rje brtsun tsong kha pa chen po yin no / zhes gsung ngo / / 'dir smras pa / dbang po rab zhi dul ba'i dpal gyis ni / / tshangs spyod kyis rgan lha yi drang srong yang / / mi bsrun byis pa ltar mdzad gzhon nu de / / 'dir ni gangs can sa yi thig ler gyur / / mkhan slob dge 'dun grangs tshang nam mkha' las / / nges 'byung gis drangs rnam dag cho ga yi / / rlung gis bar chad sprin rum bsal ba las / / bsnyen rdzogs zla ba khyod thugs mkha' la shar / / de lta'i bslab gsum khrims kyi 'dzin ma la / byang

chub sems mchog snying rje'i rtsa ba can / / rlabs chen spyod pa'i yal 'dab 'bras bus brjid / / bshes gnyen dpag bsam dbang po'ang khyod nyid lags / zhes bya ba ni / rje brtsun bla ma thams cad mkhyen pa dge 'dun grub pa dpal bzang po'i rnam thar ngo mtshar rmad byung nor bu'i phreng ba zhes bya ba las / rab tu byung ba dang bsnyen par rdzogs pa yongs su blang ba'i rim par phye ba ste gnyis pa'o / / ! de nas 'di ltar dgongs te / de yan chad nyer 'dzin chen po'i gsung dang du blangs / bstan pa dang sems can la phan gang che'i sgo nas 'gro ba'i don byas / da ni| sngar nas yid la yang dang yang du yod pa bzhin dam pa'i chos tshol ba dang / rje btsun chos kyi rgyal po tsong kha pa chen po'i drung du myur du 'gro bar bya'o snyam du dgongs te / 'dir rje rang nyid kyi gsung nas / da dbus phyogs la slob gnyer la cis kyang 'gro snyam du bsams nas de lugs kyi grabs byas pas dbu mdzad chos shes mkhan chen pa'i drung du dge bshes 'di dbus la slob gnyer la 'gro ba dga' bas bshol 'debs par zhu zhus pas / mkhan chen pa'i gsung nas / cis kyang thong gsungs nas slob gnyer la btang bas sku drin che zhing / yang dbu mdzad chos shes slob dpon blo ldan pa la / dge bshes 'di dbus phyogs la 'gro bar dga' / btang ba mi drag lags zhus pas / slob dpon pas bos nas / khyed slob gnyer la dbus la 'gro ba e yin gsung pa la / bdag @# / / dbus phyogs la slob gnyer la phyin na bsam pa yin zhus pas / khyed rang gi blo la shar ba'am / gzhan gyis bskul ba yin gsung / bdag rang 'gro snying 'dod pa lags zhus pas / 'o na cis kyang phyin pa drag gsung bas sku drin che / de nas lo nyi shu rtsa lnga pa la slob dpon rab mchog pa dang bsdebs nas dbus phyogs la phyin pa yin zhes dus phyis gsung / de nas dgung lo nyer lnga pa shing mo lug gi lo la dbus phyogs la byon te / khra 'brug tu sems dpa' chen po kun bzang pa la tshad ma dang dbu ma sogs kyi thugs sbyong mdzad / de rjes thang po cher byon / chos rje rin po che rong ston shAkya rgyal mtshan der bzhugs pa la dbyar chos zla ba phyed dang gnyis kyi bar du phar phyin gyi chos re gsan / de rjes rje btsun tsong kha pa chen po sa skyong mi'i dbang po grags pa rgyal mtshan gyis bkra shis do khar spyan drangs pa'i drung du / sems dpa' chen po kun bzang pa'i phyag phyi mdzad de byon nas / der rje rin po che la tshad ma rnam nges kyi dogs

gcod / drang nges rnam 'byed / rtsa she'i rnam bshad / bla ma lnga bcu pa'i rnam bshad / rtsa ltung gi rnam bshad sogs mang po gsan cing / rje rin po che yang thugs shin tu dgyes par byung ste / 'dul ba'i bslab khrims khyad par can spel ba'i rten 'brel bsgrig pa'i phyir du mthang gos bzhes 'phro zhig gi gnang spyin kyang mdzad / sems dpa' chen po'i drung du der yang zin thun sogs kyi thugs sbyong legs par mdzad pas bka' drin che'o zhes gsung / de nas rje btsun tsong kha pa'i gsung gis / thang po che'i bla brang pa nyi ma rgyal mtshan pa la dpal gsang ba 'dus pa'i bka' zhig zhu ba la phyin pa legs zhes bskul te der byon / rje de ba la dpal gsang ba 'dus pa mi bskyod pa dang / rdo rje 'jigs byed bcu gsum ma dang / gshed dmar bcu gsum ma dang / gshed dmar lha lnga ma sogs kyi bka' mang po gsan no / / de nas dpon slob rnams dge ldan du byon / rje shes rab seng ge gsang phu la byon / dge ldan du rje rin po che'i drung du rje bla ma 'dis / bdag gsang pur rje shes rab seng ge'i drung du phyin na bsam pa lags zhus pas / cis kyang legs gsungs nas slob dpon rab mchog la dang gnyis la spyi ru gser zho gang| rdul gzan legs po zhig gnang / ger de khong pa la phul / gzan de rje 'di pas bsnams te dgun chos la gsang phur phebs / rigs 'bring man chad la ma brten par dang po nas tshad ma'i rigs chen mdzad / thugs gsal ba dang ston pa bzang ba'i snyan pa'i grags pa yang rgya cher byung ngo / / de nas me pho spre'u'i lo la 'bras spungs kyi 'gram bting / slob dpon rab mchog pa der 'chad nyan pa cig la byon / de nas rje 'di pas ston chos sogs la dge ldan du / phyag phebs / rje rin po che la lam rim chen mo / 'khor lo bde mchog gi rtsa rgyud kyi bshad pa / sngags dbang / / sgrub dkyil gyi lung sogs sngags chos mang po gsan cing / rgyal tshab rje la tshad ma / phar phyin / byams chos @# / / phyi ma sogs kyi bshad pa mang du gsan pas pha rol tu phyin pa'i theg pa'i phyogs la bka' drin che ba yin gsung / yang gsang phur phebs te rigs lung 'grim pa sogs kyi thugs sbyong mdzad / ston dge ldan la phebs te rje rin po che dang rgyal tshab rje ste yab sras gnyis la mdo sngags kyi chos rgya cher gsan pa dang / 'dul 'dzin chen po grags pa rgyal mtshan pa la drang nges rnam 'byed tshar gcig dang / gzhan yang chos bka' ci rigs gsan / de lta bu'i tshul gyis gsang phu dge ldan

gnyis la lo gsum tsam zhig bzhugs / de nas sa mo phag gi lo rje btsun tsed kha pa chen po stod lung gi chu tshan la byon te slar 'bras spungs su phebs pa'i tshe rje 'dis kyang der byon te lam rim gyi 'khrid / nA ro chos drug / dbu ma 'jug pa / gsang ba 'dus pa'i rgyud la sogs pa mang du gsan / de nas rje btsun tsong kha pa chen po se ra chos sdings su phebs / chos rje shAkya ye shes pa la 'dul ba'i bslab khrims rnam par dag pa la brten te / dpal gsang ba 'dus pa dang bde mchog gi rtsa rgyud la 'chad nyan rkang btsugs pa'i grwa sa rnam par dag pa 'dzugs pa'i zhal bkod dang chos dpon bsko ba la sogs pa mdzad cing de'i rten 'brel bsgrig pa'i phyir du gnas der gso sbyong mdzad / rgyud kyi rgyal po gnyis kyi dbu nas chos thun re gsungs / de nas yar lam brag dkar ba la yang / bde chen rtser de lta bu'i grwa sa 'dzugs pa'i zhal bkod mdzad bzhed du 'dug pa la / bdag gi rje bla ma 'dis kyang rje shes rab seng ge dang yab sras gnyis kas se ra chos sdings su rje rin po che'i drung du byon / gso sbyong dang / rgyud kyi rgyal po gnyis gsung ba'i chos rar ched du bsams nas byon| khyad par rje shes rab seng ge'i dgongs pa la / rje btsun tsong kha pa chen po de lta bu'i rgyud kyi 'chad nyan 'dzugs pa'i rdo rje'i slob dpon zhig bdag gi bal ma 'di la re zhing / de'i bka' lung zhig gang bar zhu zhes rje btsun tsong kha pa chen po la dngos su zhus kyang 'dug / de lta na'ang rje bla ma 'di nyid 'di ltar dgongs te / spyir 'dul ba'i bslab khrims rnam par dag pa cig pyed ba la 'dul ba shes dgos par 'dug / khyad par gro sa 'di 'dul ba'i 'byung khungs lta bur 'dug pas der 'dul ba slob tu 'gor snyam du dgongs te de'i rgyu mtshan rje btsun tsong kha pa chen po la zhus pas / 'dul ba slob pa la nyams su len 'dod kyi bsam pas slob dogs pa yin / de ltar yin nang mtshar che gsungs nas chas kyi mthun rkyen du rin po che zho gang gnang / de'i cha shas shig la lha sa nas rtsam pa bsgrubs te sgo la la byon / lam du ma theg par rdul gzan gyi snam pa gcig phog la drubs pa'i nang du rtsam pa thogs cig bzhag / der rdol phyag bris mdzad de / 'di su dang phrad pas longs spyad kyang nyes pa med do / zhes bris pa bzhag la gro sar byon / de'i dus su rje shes rab seng ge pas dmar ston yab sras kyi drung ru / dge bshes 'di bdag gi slob @# / / ma'i dwangs

ma yin bas 'dul mdzod phul du phyin ba cig slob pa zhu zer ba'i zhu yig kyang phul / dmar ston dpal ldan rin chen pa dang rgya mtshe rin chen pa gnyis la lo gnyis kyi bar du mdo rtsa ba dang mngon pa mdzod legs par gsan / khyad par rgya mtsho rin chen pa la lung sde bzhi'i lung yang gsan la / dmar ston pa'i zhal nas / nged kyi slob ma gtsang phyogs khyed dang dka' bcu pa gzhon nu rgyal mcho gnyis las 'dul ba la mkhas pa med pas khyed kyis kyang bstan pa la phan pa'i 'chad nyan legs por mdzod / ngas kyang lo bcu drug nas da lta'i bar du 'chad nyan ma chag par byas pa 'di bstan pa 'ba' zhig la bsams pa yin no / zhes gsungs / der bzhugs pa'i ring la / tshe gcig rje btsun tsong kha pa chen po gzhan don la gshegs zer ba'i skad cha gsan ba la rje 'di'i thugs dgongs la / spyod pa la gshegs pa yin te 'ong / khong la mya ngan las 'da' ba'i skabs ni / med las che snyam pa cig byung gsung ste / 'di la gnad kyi dgongs rgyu chen po zhig yod do / / de nas slar yang gsang phur phyags phebs / sngar gyi thugs sbyong gi 'phro rnams legs par mdzad / gling stod du mthong smon pa zhes pa'i gra tshang zhig gi 'chad nyan pa rje shes rab seng ges mdzad kyin yod pa'i gdan sar rje 'di pa dang shar dwags po'i paN+Di ta bkra shis rnam rgyal ba gnyis bsko bzhag mdzad de lo kha yar 'chad nyan kyang mdzad / de dus gsang phu'i brag phug cig tu thugs dam mdzad pa'i mnal lam du byang shar phyogs nas thub dbang gi sku shin tu che ba cig gzigs pa'i mdzod spu nas zla ba nya gang ba cig chad de rje rang nyid la thim pa rmis / de rje shes rab seng ge la zhus pas / sangs rgyas kyi phrin las 'jug cing tshe ring po 'ong ba'i ltas yin / nged kyi rmi lam du'ang khyed mgo skya yer yer 'chad nyan byed kyin 'dug pa rmis gsung / yang de dus mnal lam la nam mkha' nas oM wA gI shwa ri muM zer ba cig la ny+dza'i rnam par nar te byung ba rje nyid kyi lce thog tu babs pa dang / gna 'tshengs / nga 'tshengs / zer ba lan gsum brjod pa dus mnyam pa cig byung gsung / de nas me pho rta lo la gtsang phyogs la phyags phebs te / de skor la dbus phyogs su lo bcu gnyis bzhugs zhes gsung / de dus rje shes rab seng ge dang yab sras phyogs mthun du gtsang la byon / byang chen du grwa pa bdun cu tsam la 'chad nyan mdzad / rigs lung kyang shin tu 'phel bar byung / de nas grwa tshogs kyang je che la song

ste snar thang / byang chen / rta nag ri khud rnams la rim gyis chos bar la byon te / lo lnga drug gi ring la 'chad nyan 'phel bar byung / de dus lcags pho khyi lo la snar thang du 'jug pa'i rnam bshad dgongs pa rab tu gsal ba'i me long gi rtsom pa yang mdzad / slar yang gsang phu'i 'chad nyan la gdan 'dren byung yang ma phebs / yang de dus rgyal tshab rje dang mkhas grub rje yab sras gnyis gnas rnyid du phebs / de'i drung du rje shes rab seng ge dang yab sras @# / / gnyis kyis kyang byon te rgyal tshab rje la spyir chos mang po dang / khyad par du mngon ba kun las btus kyi TIka de gsan rim gyis rje 'di pas phyag bris mdzad de gzhan la yang gsungs la / mkhas grub rje la yang rje 'di pas chos kyi '+p+rel yod tsam zhig kyang de dus mdzad pa yin no / / de nas dwags po dpon slob thogs cig snar thang du slebs te / dpon slob thams cad phyogs gcig tu bsgril te la stod la chos par la 'gro dgos zer ba la / rang re rnams sngon la byon / nged dpon slob rnams rjes la 'od gsungs te / lcags mo phag la rje shes rab seng ge dang yab sras phyogs mthun la stod la chos bar la byon / yar lam gcen lung dang chu 'dus sogs su byang sems shAkya dpal bas sbyin bdag mdzad de chos par mdzad / khyad par chu 'dus stag rtse'i chos par dus rje bla ma 'di'i sras kyi thu bo sems dpa' chen po 'dul 'dzin blo gros sbas pa la bar chad kyi mtshan ma cung zad tsam gyis rkyen byas te spyan ya gcig thim pa de byung / de la rje bla ma 'dis lha mo dmag zor la gtor ma phul te yus gsol bas / de'i nub mo mnal lam du bud med rgyan gyis brgyan pa cig na re / khyod kyi slob ma'i mig tshab yod pa'i skal ldan gyi slob ma gcig sang nyin 'ong ba yod do gsung ba cig rmis / de'i nangs par skal ldan gyi slob ma gcig byung ba des nga'i bstan pa la phan thogs che ba cig byung gsung / yang der mnal lam du rje btsun ma sgrol ma'i sku 'od dang 'od zer gyi phung po'i dbus na bzhugs pa cig byung ba'i zhabs la 'jus te / bsod nams 'di yis tshe rabs kun tu bdag / ces pa'i tshigs bcad 'di byas par rmis / zhes gsung / de nas rje shes rab seng ge phyir log ste / rje 'di pa dpon slob rnams kyis la stod lho la chos bar la byon / yul 'khor chos sdings / shel dkar / lha nyi mong rnams su chos par mdzad / khyad par chos sdings su g.yul rgyal ba yon 'byung zhes pa gdan drangs te khong

la dbyangs 'char gyi rgyud cha lag dang bcas pa'i bshad pa / lag len gyis ris sogs zhus te legs par spyangs / de'i dus rje 'di pas mdzad pa'i de skor gyi yig ca yang mang po yod do / / shel dkar du chos par dus kun mkhyen chos blo ba dpon slob thogs cig chos bar la byon pa dang mjal te / phan tshun thugs phebs pa'i chos kyi 'bel gtam mang po mdzad pas gnyis ka thugs tshim par byung / der bdag gi yongs 'dzin dam pa mkhas pa'i dbang po dpal ldan chos skyong zhes pa / rje bla ma 'di la sangs rgyas dngos kyi 'du shes mdzad cing / chos spyi dang / khyad par mngon pa mdzod tshar nyi shu rtsa gcig gsan pa des kyang phyags phyir slebs so / / yang de dus paN chen phyogs las rnam par rgyal ba'i slob ma mkhas grub dpal ldan sangs rgyas pa zhes pa dang / rje 'di pa shel dkar tshogs su bgro gleng la bzhengs / gnyis ka thams cad kyi yin smon pa'i gnas su byed @# / / pa byung / des rkyen byas nas paN chen phyogs las rnam rgyal ba mjal nas chos zhu ba'i 'dun pa drag po zhig byung ste / dpon slob rnams kyis padma chos sdings la byon / yar lam gla 'khor du pha dam pa'i sku gdung ka ru la mjal / spyir de la mthong tshul sna tshogs shig yod pa la / rje 'di pas dam pa rang gi skur dngos su gzigs pa yin zer ba'i lo rgyus dkon gnyer gyis brjod pa da lta'i bar du yod pa la / dus phyis bdag gis kyang gla 'khor du phyin / sku gdung dang mjal dus dkon gnyer gyis sngar gyi mthong tshul rnams rjod kyin 'dug / de nas 'dir slebs dus rje'i drung du rgyu mtshan phul bas / bdag gis dam pa rang gi skur mthong gsung ba dngos su thos / de nas padma chos sdings su byon te / paN chen dang mjal / zhag shas der bzhugs / chos mang du zhus / khyad par sgrol ma nyer gcig ma / sgrol ma lha bcu bdun ma sogs kyi dbang dang / rje btsun ma dkar sngo gnyis dang / dbyangs can ma / gdugs dkar sogs kyi rjes gnang mang du zhus / paN chen gyis dri ba mang po mdzad pa rnams la lan phul ba rnams la'ang thugs shin tu dgyes par byung nas / da phyin chang thams cad mkhyen pa dge 'dun grub gyis zhes pa'i mnga' gsol yang mdzad do / / de nas slar yang shel dkar du phebs te chos bar mdzad / de dus nub gcig gi mnal lam du rgyal tshab rje byon nas / rje btsun ma la gsol gdab kyi rjes su / bcom ldan 'das ma mchod byas pas / zhes sogs sh+lo ka 'di lan gsum re gyis gsung ba rmis / de la brtags na

de dus rgyal tshab rje gzhan don la gshegs par 'dug pas / nga po ta la nas bde ba can du 'gro / khyed kyang de ltar mdzod ces par go nas / tshigs bcad tshogs su ma chag par btsugs gsung / de nas chu pho byi ba'i lo nag pa zla ba'i tshes bzhi la tshad ma rnam 'grel gyi TIka 'di'i rtsom pa yang mdzad do / / de nas rim gyis sa skyar phebs / gur gyi mgon po la mjal bar bzhed de / dkon gnyer la mjal ka zhus pas khong na re / ngas mgon po la zhu yi zer te song / ci yin nam snyam / re zhig nas byung ste / snar thang du 'phrad pa'i mi zhig yod pa de la shog gsung gin 'dug zer| rje'i gsung nas / snar thang nyer 'dzin chen po la gur gyi bka' zhig thob pa de la dgongs pa 'dra gsung / de nas rgyang 'bum mo che skor la chos thog gcig bzhugs te chos bar mdzad / de skor gyi grwa tshang kha yar dang rigs lung sogs phyogs mthun mdzad de bstan pa'i bya ba rgyas par mdzad do / / de'i tshe khong rnams kyis gnas khang mi yong zer ba la / mnal lam du a ne rgyang ma yin zer ba'i bud med cig byung nas / 'bum pa'i sgor 'di nga rang dbang bas gnas khang yong zer cing / sang nyin bud med cig la babs nas / 'bum pa'i skor 'di da rang dbang bas gnas khang yong gi a / gzhan yang / mi chen gyis rtsam pa sbom po ster gyi a / gzhan yang / rtsod pa rgyal gyi @# / / a zer to / / de nas gnas khang yang byung zhing / byang sems sa mtsho mas phogs bzang po phul te chos kyang 'phel bar byung / de dus rje 'di bas mchod rten gyi drung du thugs dam la bzhugs pas / rten 'byung mtha' bral gyi don la nges pa chas cher rnyed de / de nas bzungs te snying rje gsum gyi don la rtse gcig tu 'jog pas dus 'da' ba cig yod ces dam pa dag gsung ngo / / de nas chu mo glang gi lo slar yang snar thang du byon / rtsa she'i rnam bshad rin po che'i phreng ba'i rtsom pa mdzad de 'chad nyan gyi sgo nas gtan la phab / de rjes ri khud du phebs / de'i tshe rje shes rab seng ge sngar rje bla ma 'di pa la stod la chos bar la byon pa'i skyel mar chu 'dus par byon / de nas phyir byon te dge ldan du rgyal tshab rje la dus 'khor gsan pa la phebs bzhed yin pa la / rta nag tu dge sbyong dkar po bas spyan drangs te ri khud chos sde phul / zhal bdag mdzad nas lo shas bzhugs / de dus su shangs pa kun mkhyen chen po dang de'i gdan

sa pa sems dpa' chen po tshul khrims dpal bzang pa gnyis la chos bka' mang du gsan / gsang ba 'dus pa'i rgyud kyi 'chad nyan yang 'phel bar mdzad / de thad du rje bla ma 'di yang phebs te de dus yab sras bka' bgros mdzad / rje shes rab seng ge dge ldan du mkhas grub rje la dus kyi 'khor lo gsan pa la byon / rje 'di pa ri khud kyi gdan sar bsko ba sogs kyi zhal ta drung chen dge sbyong ba dang yon mchod zhal 'dzom pa la gnang ste dbus phyogs la phebs / rje 'di pas ri khud chos sde'i zhal bdag mdzad / drung chen dge sbyong bas sbyin bdag mdzad de rten 'brel khyad par can bsgrig pa'i phyir du rje btsun byams pa'i sku khyad par can cig bzhengs / gtsug lag khang gi sgo sgyur pa dang rdo gcal 'dings pa sogs kyi sgo nas chos sde la phan pa che bar mdzad / khyad par du dus chen la smon lam chen mo btsugs te da bar ma chag par mdzad / de dus su rta nag na chos rje A nan+da pa bzhugs pa la dpal mgon chen po gdong bzhi ba'i bka' lung gsan / de'i rgyu mtshan yang mgon po 'di sngar yang mnal lam du byon nas yus yus byed pa cig lan mang du yod cing / khyad par de dus su tho rangs shig nam mkha' nas sgra zhig la / dang po skyes tsam nas bzungs te srung skyob byed pa cig yin te / da dung gtor ma ma byin / da dung yang khyod lta bu'i bstan 'dzin la nga lta bu'i chos skyong gis srung skyob byed pa dga' mo yin te zer ba cig byung bas zhus pa yin gsung / sngar rje shes rab seng ge'i gsung nas / dge 'dun grub / chos skyong ma mang / mangs na che'i bar chad du 'gyur / khyad par mgon po zhal dang dam can chos rgyal gnyis mi mthun pa yin gsung ba cig yod pa la / rje 'di pas dang po la stod la phebs dus / lho smad kyi grang so phyogs su char 'bebs shig la byon dus yul pa de rnams kyis khong dpon slob kyis rang re'i gzhi bdag la gnod pa skyel gyin 'dug zer nas 'phrog 'joms byas pas / de'i nub mo rmi lam du dpal @# / / mgon chen po byon nas / nga'i grogs la chos rgyal thong / nged gnyis kyis yul mi rnams la gnod pa skyel gsung ba cig byung bas khong gnyis mthun pa yin zhes gsung ngo / / ri khud du bzhugs dus nub cig mnal lam la mi zhig gis / gdung rus yin zer pa sder ma gang phul byung ba dang de 'bu ru song ba rmis / de la brten nas rta nag phu'i rdo rje gdan na bla ma don yod pa bya ba mngon shes dang ldan pa cig yod

pa de la / rje 'di bas sku skye snga phyi sogs kyi lung bstan zhu ba la btang bas khong gi zhal nas / sku skye snga ma la bal por paN chen cig tu 'khrungs / sku tshe 'di la sgrub pa byas na grub pa 'thob / skye ba phyi ma la dga' ldan du 'khrung / sku tshe bdun cu thub / ri khud du bshad nyan mdzad na drug cu las mi thub / gnas nges med du bshad nyan mdzad na sku tshe ring bar 'ong / phyi ma la rgya nag tu phrin las 'byung zhes gsung ba dang / gzhan yang da lta shar phyogs su byon na bla ma khyad par can cig dang mjal / ma byon ni ma mjal / yi dam 'jam dbyangs zhi khrod dang 'brel che / chos skyong phyag drug pa dang 'brel che / sku tshe sring thabs rta mgrin lcags ral can la bsnyen pa bskyal na bzang zhes pa'i lung bstan byung ba la brten / rta nag sgrol ma ba'i bla ma 'jam dbyangs bsam grub rdo rje bya ba la rta mgrin lcags ral can gyi rjes gnang dang / rdo rje phur ba'i bka' gsan te rta mgrin gyi bsnyen sgrub kyang mdzad / gzhan yang snga mo ri bo dge ldan du bzhugs dus mnal lam la rdzing bu zhig gi dkyil du sna tshogs padma'i sdong po'i steng du rgyal ba shAkya thub pa la 'phags pa'i gnas brtan bcu drug gis bskor nas bzhugs pa chos spyod kyi sgra lhang lhang sgrog pa'i tshal du rdzing bu'i mtha' nas / dngos grub stsol zhes zhus pas mchog gi dngos grub gnang ba'i snang ba cig byung / gnas skabs kyi dngos grub la blo rtse gtad nas / da dung yang dngos grub stsol zhes zhus pas / gtsang gi rgyags lhag khams su 'khyer bar shog / ces gsung ba cig byung / mnal sad pa na sku tshe'i 'jug la khams su phrin las 'ong ba e yin snyam pa cig byung na'ang / phyis brtags na bla ma don yod pa'i lung bstan lhar skye ba phyi mal khams su skyes nas phrin las rgya chen cig 'ong ba yin las che / zhes rje rang nyid gsung ngo / / de nas yang snar thang phyogs la phebs / byang chen sogs su chos bar mdzad / de nas bo dong la byon / dpal ldan dmag zor lha mo 'di sku skye mang po nas kyi chos skyong yin pa la sngar rjes gnang zhu ba sogs ma mdzad pas / de zhu ba la de dus bo dong na rgyal sras din po che'i dngos slob rin po che chos bzang dpal ba zhes pa bzhugs pas der byon / lha mo'i rjes gnang dgos zhus pas khong gi zhal nas / mdang rmi lam bzang / lho phyogs 'di nas rlung nag 'tshub ma'i dkyil nas dge slong zhig po dong gi sgo rtsar slebs byung ba la 'di nas bud

med rgyan can cig song ste / bstan 'dzin chen po la bsu ba bya @# / / zer nas byung ba rmis / da res rang 'brug mo hor gyis 'khyer ba 'dra / ha ha gsung zhing / lha mo 'di'i bka' lung man ngag dang bcas pa rdzogs par gnang / gzhan yang khong pa la rgyal sras rin po che'i bka' 'bum gyi lung sogs chos mang rab gsan no / / de nas byang chen du phebs te skabs shig tu bdag gi bsam pa la 'chad nyan 'di ji lta bu zhig 'ong snyam yod pa la / nub cig rmi lam na sngar ri bo dge ldan du bzhugs dus zhal 'dris yod pa'i dge slong chos mthun cig yod pa de byung nas / khyed kyi don de ngas rmi lam du brtag gis gsungs nas gnyid log pa'i tshul mdzad / de nas gnyid sad de lag pa'i phyag rgya zhig mdzad nas / yun tshogs grol thob cig 'ong pa'i rigs su ni yod / bden| zhes dang / skrag mi dgos blo 'dun dkon mchog la gtod la blo ltos chos / zhes shugs drag tu zer ba cig rmis pas da ni / nga rang blo dkon mchog la gtad la bshad nyan byed par thag gcad snyam pa thugs la 'khrungs gsung ngo / / de'i tshe 'di ltar dgongs te / byang chen 'dir chos par 'dra dang / skabs su thugs dam byed pa'i khang pa cig dgos par 'dug snyam du dgongs te / de'i mthun rkyen shing cha sogs bstan pa'i sbyin bdag chen mo shAkya dpal pa la bka' lung gnang zhing / khong gis kyang gang dgos phul te sa gzhi der byas na gdul bya phrin las rgya cher 'ong ba'i mtshan ltas sogs kyang yod pas theg chen pho drang zhes pa'i gzims khang chen po me pho 'brug gi lo la btab / de dus byang chen na sgrub chen bsod nams blo gros pa zhes pa bzhugs pa la khong rang gi bka' 'bum gyi lung dang / gzhan yang shangs pa'i chos skor ci rigs pa rnams gsan / yang de'i tshe dpon ston thub pa dpal zhes pa'i sgrub chen cig la mgon po bzhi sbrag gi bka' dang gzhan yang bka' lung ci rigs gsan cing mgon po phyag drug pa'i bka' yang gsan nam snyam mo / / de nas sngar bkra shis do khar rje btsun tsong kha pa chen pos tshad ma rnam nges kyi dgos gcod gsan pa'i zin ris rnams dang / dge ldan du rgyal tshab rje la rnam 'grel gsan pa'i gsung rgyun rnams la gzhi byas te tshad ma'i bstan bcos chen po rigs pa'i rgyan ces bya ba me mo sbrul gyi lo'i zla ba bcu pa la rdzogs par mdzad / de phyin chad rje rang nyid kyis kyang 'di nyid kyi steng nas legs par gsung zhing / da'i bar du phrin las kyang rgyas par byung / de nas rta nag ri khung du

phebs / shangs pa kun mkhyen chen po'i dpon po chos rje blo bzang pa ri khud chos sde'i gdan sar bsko gzhag mdzad de chos bar la bzhugs dus ta'i si tu chen pos snar thang mkhan po la ng+dan 'dren gyi chibs dri 'di tsam la slebs pa yod zer ba'i pho nya ba byung bas rkyen byas / de'i tshe rje 'di'i dgongs pa la snar thang nyer 'dzin chen po de snga mo nas 'di lta bu zhig la dgongs pa gtad par 'dug na'ang / de bas da dung re zhig gnas nges med du bshad nyan dang rang gi thos @# / / bsam gong 'phel byas na dga' ba 'dug / khyad par mkhas grub rje la sngar chos 'brel yod tsam zhig las ma byung / da dus 'khor gyi chos skor yongs su rdzogs pa cig zhu ba la yang da lan 'gro snyam du dgongs te| chos bar gyi dad nas gsang thabs su mdzad nas byon / ri bo dge 'phel du phebs / de'i tshe ri bo dge ldan du mkhas grub thams cad mkhyen pa gzhan don la gshegs zer ba'i skad ca gsan nas / da ni re zhig phyin kyang don ma grub po snyam du dgongs te dge 'phel du zla ba gcig tsam sku mtshams mdzad de bzhugs pa'i nub gcig mnal lam na da lta bkra shis lhun po'i rgyab ri 'di'i rnam ba can gyi ri rtse na rje tsong kha pa bzhugs / rked pa tsam na sems dpa' chen po 'dul 'dzin bzhugs / de'i smad tsam na rje rang nyid bzhugs 'dug / de nas sems dpa' chen po'i zhal nas / rje bla ma / 'di la yar rna ba gtod la gson dang / rje tsong kha pa chen po rang re pa la lung bstan mang po mdzad kyin 'dug zer ba la rje 'di pas legs par gsan pas gsung gi sgra dbyangs mang po zhig sgrog pa phal cher ma go / gsung gi cha shas shig la / dge 'dun grub ces pos pa la brten nas / sa phyogs 'dir tshad ma rnam 'grel gyi bstan pa rgyas par 'gyur ba cig 'ong ba yin / zhes gsung ba cig gsal bar tshor bas lus kyi ba spu g.yo ba cig byung / ci la lta ba yin nam / skye ba phyi ma rje dang mjal ba khong snga ba cig 'ong ba yin nam snyam pa cig byung / yang rmi lam de ka'i 'phro la ta'i si tu chen po de gos 'gang dkar po zhig gyon / zho khog cig lag du khyer nas ri de'i rtser rje btsun tsong kha pa la mjal gyin 'dug pa rmis / de ni / khong gis tshe 'dir rje dang mjal dam bca' phul byas pa'i lo rgyus 'dug pa ltar dga' ba yin nam snyam zhing gong gi rmi lam de yang dgon pa 'debs pa'i gnas lung bstan pa 'dra snyam ste / re zhig la 'di yin snyam

pa'i nges pa ma rnyed par yid la bzhag ste gang yin brtag pa la zhugs so / / de nas sa pho rta'i lo la dge 'phel nas rje rang nyid kyi bstan 'dzin bdag gi yongs 'dzin chen po dri med bshes gnyen pa phyag phyir khrid de slar yang dbus phyogs la byon / mar lam snye mo rgyal byed tshal du phebs dus sku lus la 'khru ba'i snyung gzhi zhig byung ba la zhal zon dam par mdzad pas je bsnyung la song ba'i nub cig mnal lam du mkha' 'gro ma rus rgyan dang dbu rgyan gsol ba / phyag g.yas na Da ma ru bsnams pa cig Da ma ru'i sgra dang bstun nas / rang gi snying khar zla ba'i dkyil 'khor shar shar byas pa / zhes yang yang gsung ba cig rmis pas / nad 'di tsha ba'i nad min / grang ba'i nad yin zer bar 'dug / kha glod snyam du tsha ba'i zas bsten pas phan song / zhes gsung zhing / skabs der snye mo sku zhang chos rje la 'chi bdag 'joms pa'i dbang zhig kyang zhus gsung ngo / / de nas dge ldan du phyag phebs / byang rtse ba chos rje nam mkha' dpal pa la bcom ldan @# / / 'das 'khor lo chen po byin rlabs rgyud kyi dbang lung man ngag sogs dang / tshe dpag med lha dgu'i dbang yang gsan cing / khong gis mdzad pa'i de'i sgrub dkyil zhig 'dug pa'i yig mkhan yang mdzad do| |gzhan yang sngags kyi bka' lung mang po gsan cing / thun mong ba byang chub lam gyi rim pa'i 'khrid rje tsong kha pa nas brgyud pa'i blo sbyong snyan brgyud chen mo sogs zab cing rgya che ba'i chos mang po gsan / dpon slob phan tshun thugs shin tu phebs par byung / yang dge ldan du ri rtse zhig tu rmi lam sgugs pas / pho bdud bra brdung chems se chems / zer ba cig byung bas dge ldan du bsdad na cung mi dga' ba yin pa 'dra zhes kyang gsung ngo / / de nas dbyar de 'chad khar byon / lha zur khang pa bsod nams lhun grub pa de dus blo sbyong gi bdag por byed kyin 'dug pas khong pa la gtso bor blo sbyong dang / gzhan yang bka' gdams kyi chos skor mang du gsan / de nas ston ka rgyal bo sdings su byon / spyan snga ba rin chen 'phel la bka' gdams kyi chos skor mang du zhus te shin tu gus par mdzad / de nas e waM du byon / de na 'jam dbyangs rin chen rgyal mtshan zhes pa'i bla ma khyad par can cig yod pa de rje 'di nyid kyi sku skye snga ma nas 'brel ba can gyi bla ma yin zhing / dus kyi 'khor lo'i skor la sngar nas thugs bzhed che bar yod na'ang de bar ma grub par bla ma de nyid la dus kyi 'khor lo'i

smin byed kyi dbang rdzogs pa dang / grol byed sbyor ba yan lag drug gi 'khrid / rgyud 'grel gyi bshad pa rgyas pa / man ngag cha lag dang bcas pa rnams dang / lnga bsdus kyi ri mo tsam zhig dang po gsang phur thugs spyod gi dus mdzad cing dbyangs 'char sogs kyang snga mor la stod lhor mdzad kyang dus 'khor gyi sa bris yongs su rdzogs pa'ang 'dir mdzad / gzhan yang rgyud 'bum gyi lung dang / bka' rjes gnang sogs mang po zhus te 'di phyi gi nya gar bka' drin che ba'i bla ma gcig tu mdzad pa yin no| |de nas ri bo dge ldan du phebs te byang rtser chos rje nam mkha' dpal ba la chos bka' mang po zhu dgos yod pa rnams zhus / kong po tsa ri dang mdo smad sogs la sgrub pa la 'byon pa'i thugs rtse gtad yod na'ang de dus phyags phyi pa dbon po don rgyal zhes pas da lta gdan ma drangs na 'dir mi bzhugs pa 'dug zer gtsang phyogs la bya btang ba la brten nas gtsang phyogs nas gdan 'dren pa slebs / byang rtse ba dang 'chad kha pa gnyis kyi thugs bzhed la byang rtse ba'i gdan sa la thugs bzhed che bar yod skabs su rje btsun ma la gsol ba 'debs pa'i bka' bgros shar dus rje'i zhal nas / khong rnam gnyis thugs dam bzang pas nged rang dpon slob kyang gsol ba btab pa drag ces bka' bsgos nas / byang rtse'i steng du gtsang pa rnams dang phyogs gcig gsol ba btab pa'i tshe nyams snang la rlung zhig gis dar lcog gtsang phyogs la bskyod byung bas nged rang gtsang phyogs la 'gro ba cig 'char ba 'dug gsung / @# / / sang nyin brtag pa mdzad dus 'chad kha pa rgyal tshab byams pa ltar bzang po'i 'dug stangs mdzad / zhal nub phyogs la gzigs nas zan ril bsgril bas gtsang phyogs su 'byon pa'i brtag pa babs / de rjes rje'i zhal nas spyan snga ba la / drung nas kyi zhal gtsang phyogs la gzigs pa dang / bzhugs stangs 'dis gtsang phyogs su brtag pa 'bab par de gong du go lags shing / byams bzhugs de'ang phyis rje btsun gyi sku khyad par can cig bzhed pa'i ltas yin pa 'dug go / zhes gsung ngo / / de nas gdan 'dren pa rnams kyis zhu ba phul ba / da yab sras phyogs mthun du phebs te / gtsang phyogs su mdo sngags sprel ba'i bshad nyan mjad na bsam grub rtse pa sogs kyis sbyin bdag kyang mdzad pa yod pas cis kyang 'byon pa dgos zhes nan gyis phul ba la brten nas lcags pho sbre'u'i lo la gtsang phyogs la phebs / snar thang du byon / de skor la snar thang byang chen gnyis su phal cher bshad nyan mdzad / khyad par snar thang du 'dul ba'i gleng 'bum chen mo dang so thar gyi TI ka'i

rtsom pa mdzad / de nas bsam grub rtse nas rje dpon slob gnyis ka gdan drangs te mdo sngags kyi 'chad nyan mdzad pa'i bdag rkyen bzang po rim pa bzhin du mdzad / de nas byang chen snar thang sogs su rim par byon te bshad nyan gtso bor mdzad / de dus dgongs pa la / snga dus bod 'dir lo chen yab sras kyi ring la bshad nyan dar bar byung 'dug na'ang gzhi gsum gyi phyag len cher ma byung| da 'dul ba'i bslab khrims rnam par dag pa cig gzhir bzungs te de'i steng nas bshad nyan gtso bor byed pa cig bya dgos te / de'i rten 'brel du bslab khrims kyi bca' yig chen mo 'di chu mo phag gi zla ba drug pa'i yar tshes la dpal byang chub chen por mdzad / de nas bzungs te gzhi gsum gyi phyag len bar ma chad du yod pa yin no / / snga gong spre lo de la byang chen du bzhugs pa'i skabs shig tu rje yab sras gnyis ka la sku dog shin tu che ba'i mtshan ma byung ste / rje shes rab seng ge bsam grub rtse'i gzims khang bde gsal du bsnyung ba'i tshul bstan / sku chags kyi mtshan ma bzlog pa'i phyir du rnal 'byor gyi dbang phyug bzang po rgyal mtshan pas mgon po'i gtor chen thun mong ma yin pa mdzad pas mtshan ma ngan pa bzlog ste sku khams bzang bar byung nas rgyud kyi 'chad nyan la shin tu 'grus par mdzad / rje bla ma 'di pas byang chen du sku chags kyi mtshan ma bzlog pa'i phyir du sku mtshams zla ba dgu tsam gyi bar du dam par mdzad de dus thugs dam la shin tu 'grus par mdzad cing / khyad par rje btsun ma dkar mo'i tsha sgrub gtso bor mdzad pa yin la / 'di la rje rang gi gsung nas / spyir rje btsun ma dkar mo 'di la brten nas gtso bor tshe bsgrubs na zhar la shes rab 'phel zhing / gtso bor shes rab bsgrubs na zhar la cig shos 'phel bar gsungs pas di'i dus su rje btsun ma dkar sngo'i bstod pa 'di dag dang / bla ma yab sras kyi bstod pa rnams dang / gzhan yang 'dod lha chos @# / / skyong sogs kyi bstod pa gsol 'debs dang smon lam sogs kyi rtsom pa 'di rnams kyang byas shing / de yang byed 'dod tsam gyis yid la lam ste shar nas kha nas tshig tu 'don pa cig byung gsung / gzhan yang de dus su rje btsun ma dkar sngo gnyis dang / rdo rje 'jigs byed dpa' gcig dang / mgon po phyag drug pa sogs lha dang chos skyong mang po'i zhal gzigs / khyad par dpal mgon gdong bzhi pa byon nas / khyod paN+Di ta chen po yin pas nga'i bstod pa cig rtsoms gsungs nas bstod pa 'di mdzad do / / yang de dus tho rangs mnal la

song ma song zhig la bud med dkar mo zhig gis rin po che'i snod bdud rtsis gang ba cig drangs pa rmis / de rje shes rab seng ge la zhus pas / shin tu bzang gsung / gzhan yang sku mtshams de'i mjug la mdo sde sogs bka' 'gyur rnams la gzigs rtog mdzad pas nyin mo ji tsam gzigs pa thams cad mtshan mo thugs la 'don pa sogs thugs dam gyi bogs kyang che bar byung gsung ngo / / de nas sku mtshams grol nas bstod pa gsol 'debs rnams kyi lung mdzad dus rje btsun ma'i bstod pa rnams kyi tshe rje'i gsung nas / 'di lhar na rje btsun ma'i zhal gzigs pa 'dra mo 'dug / he he gsung / yang rje shes rab seng ge rje tsong kha pa chen po'i drung na bzhugs dus rje tsong kha pa chen pos / khyed rang gtsang phyogs su byon la rgyud kyi bshad nyan mdzod / gnod sbyin ma chen mo zhig gis sbyin bdag gi gtso bo byed / slob ma'i gtso bo skye ba mang por gshin rje'i gshed kyis rjes su bzungs pa'i rnal 'byor ba chen po zhig gis thog drangs skal ldan mang po 'byung / zhes pa'i lung bstan yod pa ltar de dus su byang sems shAkya dpal bas lhun po rtser gdan drangs te sngags kyi chos kyi 'khor lo rgya chen po bskor bar mdzad / de nas seng ge rtser byon / der rje 'di pa dang skal ldan gyi slob ma 'ga' zhig la gsang ba 'dus pa'i rim lnga'i 'khrid gnang / rgyud 'grel gyi bshad lung zhig kyang mdzad de slar yang dbus phyogs la gshegs pa la rje 'di pas tsha shod par skyel ma la phebs / bsam grub rtser byon / de nas shangs phyogs la mdzad de rje shes rab seng ge ba dge ldan la gshegs so de nas rje 'di pas shing pho byi ba'i dgun chos la shab kyi bde chen rtser phebs / byang sems shAkya dpal bas zhabs tog mdzad / de nas byang chen la phebs / de dus byang chen du mnal lam zhig la skyes mchog A nan chos rje byon nas| byed pa sems can kun don byad / / gsung ba la rje 'di pas lan du / 'ong ba sems can gcig gi don kyang mi 'ong gsungs nas bzhad pa cig rmis gsung / gnas de dang snar thang sogs su chos bar mdzad / de nas glegs bam rin po che'i lung yang sngar nas ma gsan pas gsan 'dod che ba dang / sgra ka lA pa'i sa bris yongs su rdzogs pa cig mdzad bzhed kyis kun nas bslangs te / lo de'i ston mjug la dpal sdings la byon te / lo ts+tsha ba chen po thugs @# / / rje dpal ba la sgra'i sa bris thogs shig zhus / yongs su rdzogs pa rting sor mdzad par zhus te shing mo glang lo'i dgun chos la bo dong la

byon / chos thog gcig bzhugs / chos grol mtshams cig tu bla brang ser por grags pa der tho rangs cig mgo phur nas yod tsa na bar snang la bud med dus pa'i skad lhang ba cig byung / mgo phur ba bsangs te / ci byung ba yin dris pas / nga'i ming po sangs rgyas kyi bstan pa la gces pa cig yod pa de gshegs pas du ba yin zer / de su yin byas pas / de bshad na khyod kyang mya ngan byed du 'ong bas mi smra zer / ci yin nam snyam du sems ma bde ba cig byung / yang de dus tho rangs cig sngar gyi bud med de'i skad lhang ba cig byung / mgo bo bsangs te nyan pas / de na khyod kyi dgon pa yod / / gdul bya dag kyang der 'du zhing / / kha mo 'ang khyod kyi rjes su 'brang / / khyod kyi rjes 'brang skyob par byed / ces zer / dgon pa ji lta bu zhig 'ong / dgon pa'i ming la ji skad zer byas pas / lag pa gnyis thal mo khong stong du sbyar te / dgon pa 'di lta bu zhig 'ong / dgon pa'i ming la mu khyung can zer / de mkha' 'gro'i brda skad yin no ang zer te yal song / yang de dus lha mo 'di'i zhal nas / rten 'brel khyad par can yod pas tshogs su ma Ni brgya rtsa re yang ma chad par tshugs shig gsung / yang de dus dge bshes cig la lha mo 'di spyan drangs pa byon pa la / ngas bshad sgrub gang byas na bstan pa dang sems can la phan / dgon pa gan yod / dge tshul cig kyang ga na yod zhus pas / de'i zhal nas / bshad sgrub dang khyad par 'chad nyan byas na bstan pa la phan stobs che / dgon pa cig ma gi na yod / ming la mu khyung can| de yang brda skad yin no ang / dge tshul cig pha ga na yod / snying rje rje zhig pha ga na yod do zer to / / de nas chos bar lung nag shel dkar rtser phebs pa'i steng du sa g.yo ba la sogs pa'i ltas sna tshogs byung / de nas ri bo dge ldan du rje shes rab seng ge gshegs zer ba'i skad ca 'bul mkhan slebs / mang ja gcig gi steng du thugs dgongs rdzogs pa'i bsngo ba dang / dge ldan la 'gro ba'i 'bul sdud snga ma yang de nas mdzes pa yin / de nas yang bde chen rtser phebs te dbyid chos nas ston gyi bar bzhugs / seng ge rtse nas zhabs tog bsgrubs / rje 'di pas lhun po rtser byon te / kun mkhyen chos rje la gshin rje'i gshed kyi 'khrul 'khor chen mo de zhus / de nas bde chen rtser ston chos la lo chen thugs rje dpal ba sbyan drangs te sngar

gyi ka lA pa'i sa bris kyi 'phro dang / sdeb sbyor rin chen 'byung gnas sogs tha snyad kyi gtsug lag kyang mang du gsan / khyad par ka lA pa'i gzhung don 'ga' zhig la| 'di rang 'grel pa dang bstun na 'di ltar yin pa 'dra zhes yar zhus pas khong gis thal mo sbyar te / ngo mtshar che / khyed rang snga nas mkhas par 'dug / nga la slob mi dgos par 'dug go gsungs nas shin tu dgyes @# / / par byung / gzhan yang sgrol ma yid bzhin nor bu'i rjes gnang sogs bka' yang 'ga' re gsan cing / khyad par snga nas yang yang yid la gcags pa'i glegs bam rin po che'i lung gsan dus / drung nas kyis su la gsan zhus pas khong gi zhal nas / bdag gis chos 'khor sgang pa chos rje seng ge rgyal mtshan ba la zhus / khong 'brom gyi sprul bar byed par gda' gsung zhing / gzhan yang de dus khong gi gsung nas| glegs bam rin po che nas 'byung ba ltar da ste yun mi ring bar khyed rang gi yul phyogs su bstan 'dzin gyi dge slong bgres po zhig / 'brom gyi rnam thar zhu zer 'od gis / de dus dge slong de la 'brom gyi 'du shes zhog / khyed rang spyan ras gzigs su sgoms la glegs bam rin po che legs par ston cig gsung gin 'dug pa dang mthun par kho bo skal bar ldan / glegs bam rin po che 'di 'brom las thos nas 'brom la 'chad par 'dug pas da ni / chos bdag po la 'phrod pa yin no zhes gsungs nas thugs dgyes bar byung la / 'di rnams la brtags na yang rje bla ma 'di nyid 'brom thugs rje chen po'i sprul ba yin par gdon mi za ba yin no / / gnas der bzhugs ba'i ngang nas sngar 'bul sdud byas pa'i spyad dngos rnams kyis rje shes rab seng ge'i dgongs pa rdzogs thabs la ri bo dge ldan du mang skol / 'bul ba 'gyed bcas sogs kyi rdzong star yang de nas mdzad pa yin no / / de nas me pho stag gi lo'i dgun chos la bo dong la byon te chos bar mdzad / sbyin bdag rnams kyis zhabs tog phun sum tshogs pa bsgrubs shing / khyad par lha mo dmag zor 'dis nye gnas khyad par can cig phul te srung skyob tshul bzhin du mdzad pa yin no / / de nas shab kyi brag gzhug gi rtse rgyal du phebs / khyud rtse ba nang ba dpal 'byor bas zhabs tog mdzad de chos bar mdzad / de nas rim gyis snar thang du phebs te dpon slob rnams kyis sku rim la bka' 'gyur gyi gsung sgrog mdzad pa yang de nas bzungs te lo re bzhin rgyun ma chad par mdzad pa yin no / / 'dir smras pa / rab yangs shes bya'i mkha' la rab 'phags shing /

/ yon tan 'od dkar bye bas mdzes pa can / / bstan pa'i pad tshal rab tu rgyas pa'i slad / / bshes gnyen khyod ni nyin byed dbang po lags / / mkhyen rab dkyil 'khor yongs su rdzogs gyur cing / / nyon mongs tsha gdung skyob pa'i bsil zer can / / ma rig pad 'dab zum par byed pa'i phyir / / bshes gnyen khyod ni rgyu skar bdag po bzhin / / mkha' la lus med ci zhes dris pas khyod kyi yon tan phung po rnams / / mi shong snyam du dogs par gyur nas kho bos lus ni ma bzungs lo / / nyi zla 'khor ba ci zhes dris bas khyod kyi bsod nams gzi brjid ni / / ma bzod sa la 'dug pa 'phags te mkha' la 'khor ba yin zhes grag / ces bya ba ni / rje btsun bla ma thams cad mkhyen pa dge 'dun grub pa dpal bzang po'i rnam thar ngo @# / / mtshar rmad byung nor bu'i phreng ba las / gtso bor bshad nyan gyi sgo nas rgyal ba'i bstan pal phan par mdzad pa'i rim par phye ba ste gsum pa'o / / ! / / de nas snar thang du rje 'di pas nye gnas chen po don grub grags pa la / nged la tshe 'dir rje shes rab seng ge sku drin che ba yin / de'i sku drin bsab phyir du chos phyogs nas bshad nyan byas te lag rjes cig 'jog / 'jig rten zang zing gi longs spyod phyogs nas nang rten du rten bzheng zhig byas te lag rjes dod pa cig byas na bsam bas / rten de bzhugs sa zhig snar thang gi spyi sgos gang 'thad cig tu dkar me'i rgyun gang 'byor cig dang bcas te byung na bsam pa nged rang gi 'dod mos yin pas cis kyang dgos zhus pas de la khong pa na re / nyid cag gi de 'dra la skong rdzongs stobs chen dang bcas pa dgos kyin yod / nged la 'bul rgyu med pas 'dir bzhugs sa mi 'ong gsung bas der yi chad pa cig byung / yang rten de'i bzhugs sa zhig seng ge rtser zhus nas dpal sdings sam gangs can gang 'thad du dgos zhus pa la'ang dgon khag gzhan gyis chags sdang gis bkag ste ma byung / yang snang gsal gyi ldan 'dir 'gram btsugs pa tsam byas pa la 'ang gzhan dag gis bkag stem byung ba la / da ni / ji ltar byas na 'ong snyam du dgongs pa btang bas / dang po rje btsun tsong kha pas lung bstan ba de dang / phyis bo dong du lha mo 'dis lung bstan pa'i dgon pa de yang 'di ga yin pa srid / khyad par sngar rje shes rab seng ge bsam grub rtse nas snar thang la 'byon ris kyis bkra shis lhun po'i dgon sa 'di la phyag mdzub gtad de / sa phyogs 'di na dge 'dun grub

mgo bo skya yer yer chos 'chad kyin 'dug pa cig sems snang la dus rgyun du 'od gsung ba cig yang yang yod pa la brten / sa phyogs 'di ga dgon pa'i gnas su bzang bar gzigs te 'di nyid du dgon pa 'debs par thugs thag bcad la / spyir snga mo nas bla ma lha dang bcas pas lung bstan de ltar yod phyin rje rang la nges nges yod na'ang sbas pa'i tshul du de ltar mdzad do / / de nas nang rten bzheng bar dgongs te phyag na yod pa'i rdzas rnams bsdoms pas zho bcu bzhi byung ste rtan chen po rang zhig mi 'grub pa 'dra dgongs pa la sgo ri mkhan po dang drung gsol dge ba gnyis na re / rje rin po che'i dgongs pa de bzhin yin na bsam grub rtse'i mi drag pa rnams la sde pa nas ja chang dang dro bzhes gnang nas rje rang gis dge bskul gyi bka' lung zhig gnang bzang zhus pas / da bzhin byed gsungs nas sbyin bdag dang grwa pa bu slob rnams la dge bskul rgya cher mdzad pas nyin gcig rang la dar rgyas pa rang gis gser ga 'phra mang dang / gser gyi skra cha gcig / rdo rings pas gser ga gcig / brang tshal bas gser ga gcig / rgya bar bas gser ga gcig rnams kyis thog drangs pa'i gser zangs kyi 'bul ba stobs che ba dang / nas khal stod r+wa can tsam zhig byung zhing / de nas @# / / kyang rim gyis byung ba'i spyad dngos rnams bsam grub rtser bzhag / myur du bzheng ba'i thugs 'dun btang ste / me mo yos lo'i dgun chos la gnas rnying la byon / dgun chos dang po la a mi yol du bzhugs / de na bzhugs pa'i gnas rnying mkhan chen cig gis rje 'di pa la sne'u zur pa'i sku skye ba bzhes pa yin zer ba'i lung bstan kyang yod / der rten bzheng gi lha bzo ba cig su drag snyam du dgongs te dkon mchog la gsol ba btab pas dge bshes cig mi rmi lam du / bzo bo chos skyong dar gyis byed zer ba cig byung bas / chos skyong dar bya ba ga na yod dam snyam du dgongs pa la nye gnas shag mgon na re / dpon chos skyong dar de rje bde bar gshegs pa la mos po rang zhig yod / 'di ga zab lags zhus / de nas snang phur phebs / dgun chos gnyis pa mdzad / de'i mjug la de na rje btsun byams pa'i rten ngo mtshar can cig 'dug pa de'i drung du bstan pa rgyas pa'i smon lam yang mdzad / de'i tshe bsam grub rtse / gzhis ka rin spungs pa'i phyag tu byung zer pa'i skad ca yang der byung / de nas snar thang la byon / dpyid chos mdzad / de nas bsam grub rtsor byon / dpon chos skyong dar la bka' lung

gnang / de'i che rang nyid kyi mnal lam la / dge 'dun grub kyi bsams don 'grub pa la dge 'dun gi dge skos dge 'dun bzang / zhes pa la brten nas dbyar chos kyi chos khrims la dka' bzhi 'dzin pa dge 'dun bsam grub pa bskos shing 'dis bzhed don kyang grub bo / / de nas me mo yos lo'i dbyar sos nas brtsams te bsam grub rtse'i brag dmar bla brang du rten bzheng gi mgo btsugs te lugs btang bas / thad la ma byung ba la nyad stod pa'i dka' bcu pa cig rmi lam brtag tu bcug pas / khong gi rmi lam du cha lugs mdzes pa'i bud med gsum mi rkang gi gling bu 'bud cing 'di skad lo / / skyes bu dam pa'i thugs kyi mun pa gting nas bsal / / gang dang gang du bzhugs pa der / / 'od dpag med pa'i smon lam ma / / 'gro la dgyes pa'i 'dzum ston ma / / yang dang yang du spyan 'dren no / / lugs phud rje btsun sgrol ma 'tshal / / gsang bstod gegs med 'byon pa la / / thub dbang mngal skyes kyi bstod pa 'tshal / / dpe dkar gyi rtsom pa cung zad yod / / rta mgrin nag po'i zlog pa 'tshal / / nged tsho yang spre gdong can gzungs kyi dpal dang / mkhas grub du ma bsten pa yin / yang dang yang du 'ong gin yod zer gyin 'dug / yang na kha cig na bud med smug mo gcig na re / bar chad mi 'ong / phrin las dang grogs don nged lcam dral gyis byed pa yin zer ba cig rmis lags zhus pas / de ma thag thub pa chen po la bdud dpung phye mar 'thag pa ces bya ba'i bstod pa de mdzad de lugs phud la rje btsun ma'i sku bzhengs shing / de nas ston pa'i sku rgyab mtho nyer lnga pa cig gi lugs btang bas byin rlabs kyi gzi 'od 'bar zhing ngo mtshar bar byon nas / @# / / rten de'i thugs kar rgyal ba tsong kha pa chen pos thog drangs rtsa brgyud kyi bla ma sangs rgyas byang sems kyi ring bsrel mang pos gtams pa'i dngul gyi rgyal ba 'od dpag med kyi sku / rje btsun shes rab seng ge'i dbu thod rin po che sna tshogs pas bkad pa dang bcas pa bzhugs shing / gzhan yang sku'i stod smad kyi char gzungs sngags byin rlabs can mang po bshad tshod dang mthun par bzhugs / khyad par sku'i smad kyi cha la 'dul ba'i gsung rab kyi glegs bam mang po rje btsun tsong kha pa'i mthang gos dang bcas pa rten 'brel khyad par can bsgrig pa'i phyir du bzhugs / mdor na de nas brtsams te rten gyi nang bzhugs sogs yongs su rdzogs par 'brug lo zla ba gsum pa yan la rdzogs par grub pa yin no / / de nas rten

yar phyogs la spyan 'dren nam snyam du dgongs te dar rgyas pa la khrab rmog gri gsum gyi gnang sbyin mdzad / bka' bgros mdzad pa la rdo ring pa'i dpon po na re / rje khyad rang dkon mchog la gsol ba thebs pa'i gang zag yin pas dkon mchog la gsol ba btab nas / bstan pa dang sems can la gang du bzhugs na phan pa che bar lung bstan pa cig mdzad par zhu / yar mar la khyad par ma byung na 'di phyogs la bzhugs pa cig zhu zer / dar rgyas pa'i zhu ba la / da sku 'di gang du bzhugs kyang gtsug lag khang gi zhabs tog bdag rang gis byed pa lags pas yon mchod ring du mi gtong ba zhu zer / de nas bsam grub rtser gzhi byes kyi dge 'dun mang po bsags nas rje btsun ma la gsol ba btab pas 'di phyogs la bzhugs pa lung bstan byung / de nas dgon pa'i 'gram gding bar bzhed de dngos kyi sbyin bdag dar rgyas pa dpon bsod nams dpal bzang bas mdzad nas / rab byung zhes pa me mo yos lo'i smin drug zla ba'i yar tshes bzang po la rje rang nyid sbyin bdag dang bcas pa 'dir phebs / sa brtag pa / gzhi bdag la gtor ma sbyin pa la sogs pa'i chog rgyas par mdzad de / sa'i cha 'dir gtsug lag khang / 'dir bla brang / 'di rnams su brang khang so so rnams gyis gsungs te / gtsug lag khang dri gtsang khang dbus ma dang bcas pa'i 'gram bting ste / bkra shis lhun po dpal gyi bde chen phyogs thams cad las rnam par rgyal ba'i gling btab bo / / de yang gtsang khang chen mo la ka ba drug gi sa dang / 'du khang la ka ba bzhi bcu zhe brgyad kyi sa yod cing / byams khang la ka ba bcu gnyis kyis dang| sgrol ma lha khang la ka ba bzhi'i sa dang / mgon khang la ka ba gnyis kyis rnams phyis bzhengs pa yin no / / de nas sa pho 'brug gi lo'i dgun chos la lung nag gad rdzong bya bar phyags phebs / chos zhag zhe lnga'i bar du zhabs tog bzang po bsgrubs / gsung chos rigs lung sogs 'phel bar byung / de nas khro phu'i rgyal ba byams pa'i drung du byon / dpal sdings pa dang spang rtsa ba'i mi nyag bzang po gnyis kyis sbyin bdag mdzad de zhag bcu drug @# / / gi bar du smon lam chen mo btsugs / de'i ring la rgyal ba byams pa la mchod 'bul / snyan dar / 'phan| gdugs sogs 'bul ba dang / bstod pa / bstan pa rgyas pa'i smon lam sogs thugs dam 'phel bar mdzad / der skye bo'i tshogs ji snyed 'dus pa rnams la'ang las bzang po'i 'brel pa 'jog pa sogs kyang mdzad / 'di dang snga gong nas kyang gnas 'dir smon lam

chen mo lan cig ste lan gnyis mdzad do / / de nas dpal sdings 'bum par phyags phebs te chos bar mdzad / de nas snar thang la byon / dpyid chos de'i ring la bstan pa la dgongs te sman pa'i rgyal po'i mdo chog gi par brgya phrag mang po 'debs pa dang / rten gyi nang bzhugs kyi gzungs par mang po yang rje rang nyid kyis mdzad cing gtso bor 'chad nyan rgyun ma chad par mdzad / de nas rje rang gi snar thang gi brang khang byang nas phyag dpe lha rten phyag rdzas kyi dngos po gang yod pa rnams skyel ba la grwa pa thams cad kyis bsam grub rtser nyin gcig byon / slar log ste de nas chos bar rnam sras gling gi gzhis kar phebs / dpyid chos zla gcig tsam mdzad de chos mtshams la der bzhugs nas bkra shi lhun por nyin re zhing byon te bla brang ka ba nyi shu rtsa bzhi'i sa'i 'gram 'ding ba dang / gtsug lag khang gi mkhar las sogs la shin tu 'grus par mdzad de gtsang khang gi thog dang / gtsug lag khang gi khyams stod la ka ba'i star gnyis kyi thog phub / khyad par gtsang khang la thog phub pa'i dus ka ba lho shar ma btsugs nas gyeng brgyab pa dang snyam du 'ja' tshon gcig sdong 'dzugs su ka ba la zug / 'ja' tshon gcig ka ba nas dung rtse na kha la zug pa dpon gnod sbyin gyis dngos su mthong / rgyang ma nas skye bo mang pos kyang mthong zhing / thog khel nas dbu rtse'i steng du 'ja' zug pa sogs ltas khyad par can mang po byung / de nas rten ngo mtshar can de lha khang gi dbus su gdan drangs / de'i tshe yang sa g.yo ba dang me tog gi char 'bab pa sogs nyi ma lnga'i bar du byung / de nas grwa khang thogs shig dang / sgos kyi grwa khang thogs shig gi 'gram 'ding ba sogs kyi skabs der zla ba lnga pa'i gza' skar tshes grangs 'dzom pa la phyogs nas kyi bu slob mang po spyan drangs / dpal gsang ba 'dus pa'i dkyil 'khor chen po bzhengs te / nang rten ngo mtshar can de la de'i sgo nas rab tu gnas pa dang mnga' gsol rgyas par mdzad do / / de yang dgon pa ma btab gong du phyugs rdzi mang po gnas dar phyin pa'i bu mo bzang mo zer ba cig na re / dgon pa'i srad bar la ba lang shor song zer ba la zla bo rnams kyis / khyod smyo 'dug zer ba byung / dus phyis mo na re / dgon pa mda' rgyang gang gis snyogs chad cig la / sngas pa rgyan cha bzang po btags pa cig gis dge 'dun dang skye bo mang po la chos gsung ba mthong zer to / / yang dus phyis dge bshes cig gis dgon pa'i ltag gi pha

bong gru bzhi zhig @# / / gi steng du bshar byang byas pas nub mo rmi lam du bud med cig byung nas / nga'i bla ma'i chos khri'i steng du ma sdod zer nas srung ba byung ngo zhes zer / snga gong dgon pa'i ming la yang kha cig gangs can chos 'phel zer / la la dpal 'byor lhun po zer / yang de'i dus su rje bla ma 'di gtsug lag khang 'di'i khyams 'dir gur dkar po zhig gi nang du bzhugs pa'i tho rangs cig sngar gyi bud med de'i skad bar snang la lhang ba cig byung ba la gsan pas / dgon pa'i ming la bkra shis lhun po gyis / sngar gyi mkha' 'gro'i brda skad des khrol lo ang gsung ba cig byung bas bkra shis lhun po zhes pa lha mo 'dis btags pa yin / dpal gyi sde chen phyogs thams cad las rnam par rgyal ba'i gling zhes pa rje rang gis byas pa yin gsung ngo / / yang de dus su dgon pa'i mdun gyi ne thang der rab byung zhig bsgrubs / de gnas der rab byung byed pa'i thog ma yin pas ming tshogs pa rgya mtsho 'phel du btags / rab byung sgrub pa'i dus rje zhal dgon pa phyogs la bstan te gzigs pas sngar ri bo dge 'phel du rmi lam la / rje btsun tsong kha pas lung bstan pa'i gnas de 'di yin par gor ma chag par 'dug snyam du thugs nges dang / khyad par rje yab sras gsum gyi bzhugs sa sogs la cher dpyad pas thun mong ma yin pa'i nges shes byung / de'i phyir dgon pa 'di rje btsun tsong kha pa yab sras dang lha mo 'dis lung bstan pa yin no zhes gsung / khyad par glegs bam rin po che las kyang dgon pa 'di nyid kyi lung bstan mang du gsungs shing / ches gsal bar / glang chen bzhengs dang bzhugs 'dra ba / / mthar thug bsam gtan lhun grub shog / ces dang / lta bas mi ngoms gzi brjid can / / mtshungs pa med pa'i bkra shis gnas / / bkra shis lhun po rgyas 'gyur shog 'dod dgu 'byung ba'i rin po che / / de dang mthun pa dpag bsam shing / / dgos 'dod 'byung ba'i bkra shis gnas / / bkra shis mchog rab rgyas 'gyur shog / ces sogs kyis bkra shis lhun po'i rgyab ri dang / gnas kyi dbyibs dang / de'i gang zag dang / des bsam gtan 'grub lugs dang / rten khyad par can 'byon lugs la sogs pa rnams lung bstan pa yin no zhes rje rang nyid kyi gsung las dngos su thos pa yin no / / de nas rnam sras gling du dbyar zhal bzhes mdzad pa'i zhabs tog bsam grub rtse nas bsgrubs / dgag dbye thon nas rje dpon slob kyis bkra shis lhun por phebs te / der gzhi phab ste bzhugs pa'i thog ma de nas

mdzad / de'i dus su dar rgyas nang pa dpon bsod nams dpal bzang bas dgon pa'i gzhi rten la gzhis mkhar ba'i bogs sngo chags sogs kyi yong sgo rnams phul te lo re bzhin dbyar chos la gsol phogs 'bul bar mdzad do / / de nas sa mo sprul lo'i dgun chos nas brtsams te / grwa pa rnams kyis kyang bkra shis lhun por bzhugs @# / / sa'i mthil mdzad pa yin no / / de'i tshe rje bla ma 'dis bla brang rgyal mtshan mthon po'i skam thog cig tsam la brten nas bzhugs pa'i dgun chos gnyis 'dir mdzad / de nas dpyid chos la snar thang du phebs / dpon slob nyung shas shig las ma byung yang gsung chos rigs lung sogs shin tu 'phel bar byung / de nas slar yang bkra shis lhun por phebs te bzhugs / de lta bu'i rten bzhengs mkhar las sogs kyi ngang nas kyang spyir bshad nyan rgyun ma chad par mdzad cing / khyad par lo de la grwa tshogs kyang cung zad chung ba la brten / rje bla ma 'dis gsung chos thams cad gzabs bshad dang / khyad par du tshad ma rnam 'grel lha dbang blo'i 'grel pa sogs rgya 'grel mang po dang / TIka chen rigs pa'i rgya mtsho sogs bod TI ka mang po yang gzigs nas / legs par bshad pa'i gsung gi zin bris bu sleb snga ma dag gis byas pa yang yod do / / lo de'i dbyar zhal bzhes kyang der mdzad de / gnas de'i dbyar zhal bzhes kyi thog ma yang de yin no / / de dus tho rangs shig rmi lam du rje btsun tsong kha pa byon nas / dge 'dun grub / khyod bdag gzhan brje ba'i byang chub kyi sems sgom mam gsung ba la / dpe la bltas te sgom gyin yod zhus / sgom dgos gsung ba'i don du go / de nas lcags pho rta lo'i dgun chos grol mtshams shig tu rje bla ma 'di ri bo dge ldan gyi mkhan po la gdan 'dren pa la bla ma dka' bcu pa sbyin pa dpal ba dang dge skos dpal ldan rin chen pa gnyis kyis thog drangs dpon slob thogs shig gis slebs / zhu ba phul bas / rje bla ma'i gsung nas / bdag der mi 'gro / de'i rgyu mtshan yang dgon pa 'di yang btab ma thog tu song bas rgyun brtan pa cig ma byung dogs shing| khyad par sngar byas pa thams cad kyang bstan pa spyi sgos 'ba' zhig la bsams / da dung yang rje btsun tsong kha pa chen po'i bstan pa 'ba' zhig la bsams te 'dir ka sngod pa yin gsungs te mi 'byon par thag bcad do / / de nas lcags mo lug gi lo la lha rgyal rtser phebs te dgun chos dang po mdzad / dgun chos gnyis pa la sul phur byon / dpon nam mkha' rgyal po sku mched kyis zhabs tog bsgrubs

te chos bar dang / de na rten ngo mtshar can gnyis 'dug pa de'i drung du bstan pa rgyas pa'i smon lam yang mdzad do / / de nas sde chen rtser phebs / seng ge rtse nas zhabs tog bsgrubs / chos thog gnyis kyi bar la gsung chos rigs lung sogs kyang 'phel bar byung / de nas slar yang bkra shis lhun por phebs / dbyar zhal bzhes mdzad / chu pho spre'u'i dgun chos la rgyab khrar phebs / dar rgyas pas zhabs tog bsgrubs / dgun chos gnyis pa la yang dpal sdings la byon / der chos thog gnyis bzhugs / brag gzhug pa dang / dge bshes bsod nams 'phel sku mched kyis zhabs tog bsgrubs / dpal sdings kyi gtsug lag khang der bstan pa rgyas pa'i smon lam yang mdzad do / / de nas snar thang du phebs te chos thog gcig mdzad / slar yang @# / / bkra shis lhun por phebs te dbyar zhal bzhes mdzad / de'i lo dge 'dun gyi spyi bsod chen mo 'di yang btsugs pa yin no / / chu mo bya lo'i dgun chos la thag gi gdong dkar du phebs / 'di pas da lan dang / der ma zad rim par zhabs tog tshul bzhin du bsgrubs te sbyin bdag gi gtso bo zhig mdzad / de nas 'dir phebs / snar thang mkhan po bsod nams mchog grub pa gdan sa thel du gshegs pa'i dgongs pa rdzogs thabs dar rgyas nas dgon pa 'dir legs par bsgrubs so / / de nas bzungs te lo sprel gyi bar du bshad nyan rgyun ma chad pa'i ngang nas spyi dgos kyi mkhar las sogs kyang legs par mdzad do / / de nas shing pho khyi lo'i dgun chos la rta nag ri khud du phebs / lha rgyal rtse pas zhabs tog bsgrubs te dgun chos dang po mdzad / de nas dgun chos gnyis pa la lung nag gad rdzong du phebs / zhabs tog tshul bzhin du bsgrubs te chos bar mdzad / de nas yang lha rgyal rtser phebs te chos bar mdzad / slar yang snar thang du phebs te chos thog gcig mdzad nas bkra shis lhun por phebs te nga bar zhal bzhes mdzad do / / de nas shing mo phag gi dgun chos la rta nag ri khud du phebs te dgun chos mdzad / slar yang bkra shis lhun por phebs / bshad nyan tshul bzhin du mdzad do / / me pho byi ba'i dgun chos la gdong dkar bas thag rdzong nub tu spyan drangs te zhabs tog tshul bzhin du mdzad / slar yang 'dir phebs te bzhugs / yang me mo glang lo'i dgun chos la gdong dkar du spyan drangs te zhabs tog tshul bzhin du bsgrubs / de dus rje 'di nyid kyi tshems gcig brul ba gdong dkar ba nang pa dpal 'byor ba la gnang ba la / khong gis gsol ba btab pas dus phyis rje btsun ma'i sku mtshar

zhing dod pa cig ring bsrel gsum gyi dbu rgyan dang bcas pa byon pa kun gyi mthun snang du grub pa yin no / / de dus mnal lam du rje shes rab seng ge yin zhes zer ba cig la rje btsun tsong kha pa'i rnam pa can cig gis / chos kyi mthar thug sems skyed yin / / lta ba'i mthar thug stong nyid yin / / rgyud kyi mthar thug gsang 'dus yin / / gsungs nas ral gri gnyis gtad song ba rmis gsung ngo / / de nas yang 'dir phebs / gtsug lag khang gi thog 'bigs pa'i thugs 'dun btang pa'i tshe rje 'di pa'i mnal lam du mi dkar po zhig na re / nga khyod kyi pho lha yin / spyan ras gzigs kyi gtsug lag khang bzheng ba la shing 'bul du 'ongs pa yin zer te shing mang po 'dir slebs pa rmis / gzhi bdag bzang ra 'di yin pa 'dra gsung / yang kha cig gi rmi lam du 'brog pa'i khye'u dkar po zhwa rtse ring g.yon pa 'ga' zhig gis g.yag mang po la shing bkal te / spyan ras gzigs la 'bul lo zhes zer te 'dir slobs pa rmis zhes zer zhing / don la yang rje rang nyid kyi gdung chos su gtogs pa'i 'brog pa rnams kyis lho'i la mo nas shing rnams g.yag la bkal te bskyal la / shing thogs shig gnas rnying / @# / / dpal 'khor lo sde chen sogs nas chu la drangs te 'dir slebs / de nas shing bzo ba'i dpon mkhas pa gnyis kyis thog drangs bzo bo mang pos bzo btsugs te de'i ring la bzo bo rnams kyi nyams snang la nyin mo mi dang mtshan mo mi ma yin gyis las byed pa'i snang ba dang / rmi lam rmi ba sogs mang du byung zhing / de nas legs bar rtsom pa byas pas myur du thog 'bigs legs par grub cing / de lo dbyar de gzims khang rgyal mtshan mthon po'i ka drug ma'i gnas brtan lha khang gi ri mo 'di yang grub pa yin la / de'i tshe rje'i zhal nas dpon mo che bsam gtan pa la / lha mo 'di'i sku sgo rgyab 'dir 'bri ba'i lugs yin na'ang / lho shar gyi zur 'di na hrab hrib dang / shab shib mang po zer cing / nga 'dir sdod zer gyin 'dug pas 'dir bris gsungs nas / zhal nub gzigs la mdun du gtor ma dang bcas pa bzhugs so / / de nas sa pho stag lo'i dgun chos la seng ge rtser phebs / bdag mo rdo rje tshe ring mas zhabs tog bzang po bsgrubs / gsung chos kyang 'phel bar byung / de dus grwa pa 'ga' zhig la na tsha 'dra byung ba la rje'i zhal nas / 'di'i dgon pa'i lha mo 'di'i g.yo zhig yin tshod du 'dug / 'di mgon po phyag bzhi pa'i yum e ka dzA Ti yin / nged

rang gi lha mo 'di dang yang gcig par 'dug / mgon po phyag bzhi pa 'di bdag la sku'i snang ba yang dang yang du ston pa cig yod pas 'di la gsol mchod byas na phan pa che bar 'ong ngo gsung / de nas dgun chos gnyis pa la bo dong la phebs / dge bshes nas bzang ba sku mched kyis zhabs tog bsgrubs / de dus su sa skya pa chos rje seng rgyal ba zhes pa de na bzhugs kyin 'dug pa la rje 'di nyid kyis sa skya pa'i dmar po skor gsum gyi man ngag khyad par can dang / rta mgrin yang gsang gi bka' dang / de'i bka' sdod beg tse lcam dral gyi rjes gnang man ngag dang bcas pa rnams zhus shing / rje 'di pas kyang khong pa la khros ma nag mo'i bka' yang gnang ba yin no / / de'i tshe gong gi bka' lung 'di rnams kyi yig ca yang chang bar bsgrub te phyis bag tse lcam dral la dgon pa 'di'i phyi nang gi gnyer gtad kyang legs par bcol ba yin no / / de nas lha rgyal rtser phebs te chos bar mdzad / de dus bdag gi bla ma sems dpa' chen po blo gros spas pa de'i nye skor gyi khru ma dga' ldan zhes pa'i dben gnas shig na thugs dam la bzhugs pa des / rje bla ma 'di'i drung du mjal ba la byon te gsung rab kyi 'bel gtam spyi dang / khyad par rgyal ba'i bstan pa la dgongs pa'i bshad sgrub tshul bzhin du mdzad par dpon slob mthun grub tu thugs dam 'cha' ba sogs mdzad do / / de nas snar thang la byon / byang chen gyi theg chen pho brang du rin po che kun dga' dpal ldan pa spyan drangs te shangs pa'i ne gu'i chos skor tshang ma / mgon po yid bzhin nor bu'i rjes gnang dang bcas pa rnams zhus / de nas snar thang du byon te snar thang mkhan po grags pa @# / / don grub pa la rgyal po chen po rnam thos sras kyi bka' zhus shing / dus phyis khong pa la byang sa'i lung zhig zhu rtsis yin na'ang ma grub / de nas 'dir phebs / bir thogs rgyal po dpon mo che sman thang pa dpon slob kyis btsug lag khang gi ldebs chen gnyis la / rgyal ba rdo rje 'chang la grub chen brgyad cus bskor ba dang / thub pa chen po la 'phags pa'i gnas brtan bcu drug gis bskor ba'i zhing khams gnyis kyi ri mo rdzogs pa dang / mdzad bcu'i zhing bkod chen mo'i skya ris rnams mdzad cing / khyad par rgyal ba rdo rje 'chang chos 'chad du mdzad pa yang rten 'brel khyad par can gyi phyir mdzad do / / de'i tshe nub cig mnal lam la rnam sras gling gi 'khris kyi ri 'di'i steng na yi dam rdo rje 'jigs byed zhal phyag yongs

su rdzogs pa'i phyag mtshan thams cad la phod kha re bsnams pa gzigs shing / 'di phyis brtags na dgon pa'i nye skor du dus zings chen po 'ong ba'i ltas yin pa 'dra gsung / de nas zhing bkod gzhan rnams kyang lha btsun bstan pa'i rgyal mtshan dang / bshes gnyen sangs rgyas bzang po dang / dpon mo che bsam gtan pa sogs ri mo ba so so rnams kyis rim pa bzhin du mdzad pa yin no / / yang skabs shig tu rje'i dgongs pa la / rje shes rab seng ge de'i bka' drin bsab phyir du sngar gyi rten bzhengs dgon pa dang bcas pa'ang yin mod / da dung sngags la brten pa'i sku drin bsab phyir du dpal gsang ba 'dus pa'i gser sku lha grangs tshang ma zhing bzheng pa dang / dgon pa 'dir yang rgyud kyi 'chad nyan rkang btsugs shig kyang 'dzugs par bzhed de / bdag gi bla ma mkhas grub chen po bzang po bkra shis la 'dir rgyud kyi bshad nyan cig ces kyang mdzod gsungs te / de'i rten 'brel du dpal ldan bla ma'i dbang bum yin zer ba'i bum pa bzang po zhig gi gnang sbyin kyang mdzad / gzhan yang dka' bcu pa dpal ldan bzang po zhes pa la brgyags rten rin po che gnang ste / rgyud 'chad thub pa cig gyis shig gsungs te dbus phyogs la brdzangs / tha na bdag lta bu la yang de mthun gyi bka' lung gnang na'ang gdul bya'i stabs kyis thugs bzhed bzhin gyi mdzad pa ma grub / 'on kyang re zhig la gsang ba 'dus pa rigs lnga'i sku dang / bdag cag gi tshe sgrub la dmigs pa'i rje btsun ma dkar mo'i sku cig bzheng bar bzhed de / thog mar rigs lnga bzhed ba'i rgyu dang yon rdzongs dbus phyogs la brdzangs te sprul pa'i bzo bo sle'u chung ba la phul nas legs par bzhengs pa'ang 'dir slebs / de nas stag rtse pa'i lha bzo ba mkhas pa cig gis thog mar rje btsun ma dkar mo'i bzo tshad kyi sman sku zhig phul / de nas khong gis rje btsun ma'i gser sku mda' tshad tsam mtshar zhing byin rlabs che ba cig bzhengs te phul ba la khong yon rdzongs sogs kyis mnyes par mdzad do / / yang skabs shig tu gtsang khang dbus ma 'dir rten bzheng thogs shig mdzad pa la / nyang stod gnas gsar @# / / ba'i lha bzo ba dpon slob 'ga' zhig gis bstan pa'i gtso bo'i ldem gnyis gan+d+ho la dang bcas pa / g.yas g.yon du rgyal ba tshe dpag med dang sman pa'i rgyal po / shar nub tu nye ba'i sras chen brgyad kyi sman sku rnams sku tshad che zhing mtshar chags dang ldan la byin rlabs kyi gzi 'od 'bar ba bzhengs so / / sa mo yos lo'i dgun chos la gnas rnying la byon / snang phu bas zhabs tog bsgrubs / gsung chos rigs lung

sogs 'phel bar byung zhing / de'i tshe de skor gyi ban skya'i tshogs dpag tu med pa la bka' gdams glegs bam rin po che'i lung gnang zhing / dge ba'i sa bon 'jog par mdzad la / rje btsun gyi sku khyad par can 'di bzheng pa'i 'bul sdud snga ma yang de nas mdzad do / / de nas 'dir phebs te lo de'i dbyar bde ba can pa gnas brtan chos bzang zhes pas bzhugs khri'i steng gi 'bol dang / dge 'dun gyi gral gdan gyi 'bol yug thogs shig phul / de nas bzungs te yun ring gi bar dge skos re res 'bul yug re phul bas brgya lhag tsam zhig byung zhing / de'i gnad kyis dge 'dun gyi gral gdan rang re'i 'di bas bzang ba ga na'ang med cing / 'di ni / bsod nams kyi tshogs kyang shin tu che bar 'dug go / de nas rje bla ma 'di'i dgongs pa la / snga mo nas mkhas grub thams cad mkhyen pa mnal lam du byon te / rje btsun byams pa'i sku zhig bzhengs na bstan pa dang sems can la phan pa rgya chen por 'gyur ba'i lung bstan cig yong pa dang / gzhan yang rang gi slob ma nyams rtogs can 'ga' zhig gi nyams dang rmi lam la / rje btsun gyi sku bzhengs na phan thogs rgya chen po 'ong zer ba mang po yod pa sogs la brten nas / sngar gsang ba 'dus pa'i lha'i sku chang mar bzheng pa'i 'dun pa yod pa'i rigs lnga ma gtogs lhag ma rnams bzheng dgos yod na'ang gser sku ni / cung mi 'grub pa 'dra / lder sku che rab cig bzheng e thub / 'on kyang dkon mchog la thugs rje yod pas gsol ba btab na gser sku yang bzheng thub snyam du dgongs te / gnas rnying du 'bul sdud snga ma mdzad dus thog ma rang la gser gyi tog cig byung bas / rten 'brel shin tu legs gsungs nas thugs mnyes so / / da ni / phyogs thams cad du dge bskul gyi 'bul sdud rgya cher byas te / rje btsun byams pa'i sku sku tshad che ba cig bzheng bar bya'o snyam du dgongs te / bdag cag grogs mched lnga la zhal ta nan gyis gnang ste thog mar lho byang gnyis la 'bul sdud la brdzangs / de dus ne ring rin po che pas rin po che zho drug cu re lnga'i 'bul bas thog drangs so so tha dad nas 'bul ba rgya che bar byung zhing / de dag gi skabs su lha dang chos skyong gis srung skyob tshul bzhin du byas pa sogs ngo mtshar ba'i ltas mang po dang bcas te ston btsas ma'i dus nyes skyon med par 'dir slebs / de dus ta'i si tu rnam rgyal grags pas rje btsun gyi sku bzheng ba la lang 'bul ba stobs che ba mdzad cing / rje 'di pa la gsung rab kyi dri ba

thun mong ba thogs shig yod pa la lan skabs @# / / bab la bsring gsung ba yang yod do / / de'i tshe bdag grogs mched rnams kyi nang nas dge bshes blo bzang zhes pa byang chub sems dpa'i brtul zhugs la gnas pa cig yod pa de grogs mched gnyis mnga' ris stod la 'bul sdud la brdzangs / de'i tshe kho nga rnams la mnga' ris rgyal po jo bo grags 'bum lde zhes bya bas srang mang po ri ba'i g.yu mo ches thog drangs 'bul ba mang po dang / gzhan yang de phyogs kyi bu slob sbyin bdag rnams kyis dad 'bul bsam gyis mi khyab ba dang bcas te / lcags mo sbrul lo'i ston dus nyes skyon med par 'dir slebs / de'i tshe yar ngo'i tshes brgyad cig la rje'i zhal nas lha btsun bstan pa'i rgyal mtshan la / rje btsun gyi sku tshad ji tsam 'ong gi brtag pa cig byed dgos pa 'dug pas / gyeng logs shig la phyag mtho drug gi tshad mdzad nas / 'di la dbes pa'i zhal cig bris gsung / khong gis bris pas tshad 'phyugs nas / mtho dgu tsam du song ba dang rje'i zhal nas / bla ma zhang gis lha chen dpal 'bar bzhengs dus nye gnas kyis srog shing chad 'phyugs pa'i rten 'brel gyis sku shin tu che ba cig byung zer / 'o skol la yang sku chen po zhig 'ong ba yin yod gsung / de nas zhal bris nas mchod pa phul / gsol ba btab pas de'i nub mo lha ri rtse nas ser snam gyi gsol bems legs pa cig 'bul ba la btang byung bas / rten 'brel shin tu legs zhes gsung / de'i tho rangs mnal lam du| sum brgya drug cu thob zer ba'i sgra lhang pa cig byung gsung / de'i nyin par rtse zhol ba'i mo reng mo zhig gis rje'i drung du gser zho do / / zangs shu gcig / nas khal sum cu / snam bu bubs gcig rnams phul bas dgyes te / rang re'i rten bzheng 'di la bar chad med cing / longs spyod dang 'gro don yang chen po 'ong ba 'dug gsungs nas shin tu dgyes par gyur to / / lo de'i dpyid mgon khang 'di'i nang du rten bzhengs pa la / bdag gi bla ma rnal 'byor gyi dbang phyug bzang po rgyal mtshan pas zhal bkod sbyin bdag sogs kyi bdag rkyen mdzad de / yi dam mgon po dkar nag 'khor dang bcas pa'i sku rnams byin rlabs dang gzi brjid che bar bzhengs / lha mo'i sku 'di rjes la bzhengs so / / de'i ston fbdag gis kyang rje rin po che 'di'i sku drung du bsdad de phyag dpe 'bri ba sogs kyi sgo nas mnyes par byas te / rje rang gi sku skye snga phyi'i mdzad pa rnams zhib tu zhus / de nas lcags pho 'brug gi lo la dgon pa 'dir bzhugs te / phyis

rje rang gi bstan 'dzin chen po dge ba'i bshes gnyen sangs rgyas dpal rin pa dbus phyogs la 'bul sdud la rdzong ba dang / 'di skor gyi bu slob spyi sgos rnams la'ang 'bul sdud rgya cher mdzad pa de thams cad la yang rang gzhan thams cad rje btsun gyi zhabs drung du skyes te / theg pa chen po'i chos kyi dpal la longs spyod pa'i rten 'brel khyad par can bsgrig pa'i phyir du rje btsun gyi sku 'di bzheng pa yin pas / zhes pa'i bka' lung phyogs thams cad du gnang zhing / thugs @# / / la yang de 'ba' zhig dgongs pa'i sgo nas mdzad pa la / da lha bzo ba ji lta bu drag snyam du dgongs pa'i tshe slob dpon rnams bsags nas bzo bo su drag gi bka' bgros mdzad pas kha cig ni / sle'u chung pa drag zer| kha cig ni / byang pa'i dpon bkra shis rin chen pa drag zer / phal cher zhal mthun par bal po rang drag / lha chen 'di tsam bzheng pa la bal po mkhas shing rgyu yang gron chung zer / gnas brtan don rgyal pa na re / gros sna shes rab can gyis thon / / gros thag bsod nams can gyis chod zer ba yin / rje rang gi dgongs pa la gang shar ba cig mdzad par zhu / byung tsam byung na bal po mdzad na dga' ba yin zhus pas rje'i dgongs pa la / bal po byas na yon rdzongs rnams la gser dngul dang gos dar rkyang dgos par 'dug dgongs nas de nub thag ma chod par / da dkon mchog la gsol ba btab nas byed gsungs nas de nub 'then / de rting slob dpon rnams spyan drangs nas zan ril byas te / rje btsun ma la gsol ba btab pas / bzo po bkra shis rin chen cung zad ngo mtho yang bar chad che bar lung bstan / de nub yon chab kyi steng du dkar me'i dud pas zhag chags pa bzhin byas nas / mai tre zer pa'i yi ge lany+dza'i rnam par shin tu gsal ba cig byung bas thams cad ngo mtshar bar gyur te / de'i nub mo thugs dam pa cig gi rmi lam du bud med rgyan can mang po tshogs pa'i dbus na bud med smug mo mda' dar sho spung cim khyer ba cig na re / bstan pa'i snying po de la 'di skad smros blo dman rnams ni 'dod yon sred pas bcing / / sems dpa' rnams kyi spyod tshul dpag mi nus / / lus srog longs spyod g.yo med byang chub bsngo / / sum brgya drug cu mi pham mgon po'i tshad / / rgyal sras spobs pa zhan du ma 'jug cig / he he| zer ba cig dang / mgon po yid bzhin nor bu la gsol ba thob / mi gsar gyi kha nas gtam yong ba yin / lha bzo ba bod kyis byas na

shi chad nye / stod phyogs kyi 'bul sdud pa rnams 'dun thog tu 'bab zer ba cig byung / de'i nyin bar ston chen lha bcan lha mo bya zhig mdzad pas / lha bzo ba bod kyis byas na bar chad che / bal pos byas na dpa' bos dpa' bo 'khrid pa yin pas bzang zer ba byung / de'i tshe lhun po rtser rten bzheng la bal po thogs shig 'dug pa la zhal ta gnang bas khong rnams 'dod pa ches pas ma 'grig / de nas sngar brtag pa babs pa dang mthun par lha bzo ba la stod byang nas 'bod par thag bcad / lo de'i dpyid ta'i si tu ba'i dris lan rnams bdag cag rnams la gsung chos su gnang ste rtsom pa mdzad de 'bul ba dang lha bzo ba 'bod pa phyogs mthun du bdag gis lo de'i ston gzhug byang la phyin / mus pa sogs la 'bul sdud byas / dgun chos la ngam ring du phyin te dris lan phul / ta'i si tu bas kyang dgyes pa chen po mdzad / lha bzo ba ni / thang stong rgyal por grags pas gegs byas te bkag / de nas ngam ring smon lam grol nas 'dir slebs dus lcags mo sbrul gyi dpyid chos la dge bshes @# / / bsod nams 'phel gyis zhabs tog bsgrubs te gsung chos 'phel bar 'dug / de dus bdag gis byang nas grwa pa cig phul ba la / rje rang gi gsung dang mthun par bstan pa la phan thog pa cag byung ngo / / de nas dbyar chos la bdag gi bla ma mkhas grub chen po shes rab rgyal mtshan pas zhub po mdzad nas / gleg bam rin po che zhi ba tu gsungs te mang po dad pa'i sa la bkod / de dus rje rang gi bstan 'dzin chen po mkhas pa stobs ldan 'od zer pas rje la gleg bam 'di la chos min zhu mkhan 'dug pas ji ltar lags zhus pas / chos yin min cha med / sems la shin tu phan gsung ngo / / lo de'i dbyar gzhug nas byams khang gi mkhar las kyang mdzad / de nas sbrul lo'i ston gnas rnying nas zangs mgar ba bos te / zangs mgar ba kha cig gis glang phur zangs le ba 'chos pa sogs kyi mgo brtsams / de nas da bzo bo su drug gam zer ba la rje'i zhal nas / dga' ldan nas bi shwa ka rma 'ong ba yin gsungs nas bzhad kyin 'dug / de nas zla ba gcig tsam na snar thang pa dpon po byang rin zhes pas rten gyi bzo phud la rje btsun gyi sku 'di'i lugs btang ste ngo mtshar bar byon / de nas khong gi zhal bkod dang 'brong rtse pa'i zangs mgar bas brdungs byas pas 'ong zer nas khong gnyis kyis byed par thag chod pa la grwa pa rnams ma dgyes shing / khyad par zangs mgar ba'i rmi

lam du bud med cig gis skabs leb kyi mgo nas bsgril ba rmis zer nas the tshom du yod pa la de'i tshe sprul pa'i bzo bo rnams spyan ras gzigs dang sgrol mas rgyud bskul / dpal ldan lha mos lam srungs mdzad nas chu 'dus su slebs / de nas drung chos rgyal bas lha bzo pa rnams khrid nas 'dir fslebs / rje'i drung du rgyu mtshan phul bas rje'i gsung nas / shin tu legs / mi gsar gyi kha nas gtam byung / sla nga tsha dus kyi skam pa bya ba yin gsung / de nas sang nyin bzo bo rnams la zangs leb rnams bstan pas khong rnams na re| da ni rgyu yang ldangs shing / zangs leb rnams kyang legs po 'ong zer nas dbu'i tshugs drangs te bzo tshugs so / / bzo bo na re / bdag gis nyin mo bzo lag pas byed / mtshan mo yid kyis bzo byed pas mgyogs la legs pa 'ong zer / rje'i gsung nas / tshugs dpon po byang rin gyi 'di la drag gam / yang na dkon mchog la gsol ba btab na gsungs pas bzo bo na re / dkon mchog rin po che pha rang yin mod / nga la bzo phas bslabs pa yin gyi dkon mchog gis bslabs pa med zer te khong rang gi steng du bzhag / rje'i gsung nas / dpon mo che / 'u cag sngon la dbu de che ba cig byas pas de nas mi 'grub kha med yin / da lha ni / rgyu yang chen po rang mi gda' gsungs pas bzo bo na re / de ka byed / legs po 'ong / rin po che pa chu mig bzang po dang 'dra / 'phral la med kyang 'phral la skyes te 'ong zer / de nas bod kyi bzo bos ji lta ba bzhin ma byung bas bal po rnams rlom pa cung zad skyes te g.yel @# / / du song ba dang / dpon mo che'i rmi lam la rgyal chen lha khang na mi nag po chen po zhig lag pa g.yon pa sdigs mdzub byas te bzo bo rnams la btsugs nas bsdigs pa'i tshul byed kyin 'dug pa rmis pas dpon mo che / a ma zer / ci byung dris pas / 'di bzhin byung zer / skrag nas phyin chang skad cig kyang ma yengs par bzo byas pas thog mar dbu legs par grub / de la rab gnas mdzad de gsol ba btab pas mdzod spu la me tog gcig chags shing| khyad par snyan rgyan g.yas kyi 'bur dbus ma la rgyal btsong kha pa'i sku yin yang zer / kha cig rje rang nyid kyi sku yin yang zer / mdor na bla ma'i sku rang byon shin tu mtshar ba cig skye bo thams cad kyi mthun grub tu byon / gzhan yang de'i tshe chos skyong gi gtor sgrub 'dzugs pa sogs kyi rim gro 'dzugs pa dang bcas te bal po rnams

kyis bzo legs par brtsams / de'i tshe sku rim pa rnams dang bzo bo rnams kyi nyams snang la nyin mo mi dang mtshan mo mi ma yin gyis bzo sgrub pa'i snang ba rgyun mi 'chad cing / de ltar bsgrubs pas ring por ma thogs par khru nyi shu rtsa lnga'i sku tshad dang ldan pa'i rje btsun gyi sku ngo mtshar can de chu mo lug gi lo la grub ste / rtan gyi nang bzhugs la yang dam pa dmar po'i ring bsrel sogs sangs rgyas byang sems kyi sku gdung ring bsrel dang ldan zhing / rgyu rin po che las grub pa'i lugs sku mang po bzhugs shing / gzhan sku'i stod smad kyi cha la bshad tshod dang mthun pa'i gzungs sngags mang po dang / gsung rab po ti mang po bzhugs / gzhan yang sman sna / 'bru sna / zas sna / gos dar kyi sna mang po sogs mtshang ba med par bzhugs / gzhan yang rten gyi nang bzhugs khyad par can cig gzhan su la yang rgyus med par rje rang nyid kyis mtshan mo byon te / rten gyi thugs kar bzhugs su gsol nas gsol ba gdab pa dang smon lam mang po yang mdzad ces grags so / / de lta bu'i rten ngo mtshar can de'i rab tu gnas pa lug lo zla ba lnga pa'i yar tshes bzang po la dpal gsang ba 'dus pa'i dkyil 'khor bzhengs te / de'i sgo nas rab gu gnas pa rgyas par mdzad / de'i dus nam mkha' la 'ja' tshon gyi gur dang / me tog gi char 'bab pa sogs ngo mtshar ba'i lhas dpag tu med pa dang khyad par rje rang nyid kyis de nub rje btsun gyi zhabs drung du bzhugs te gsol ba rtse gcig tu btab pas rje btsun byams pa snam sbyar rdo tshos ma gyon pa'i dge slong gi rnam pa can cig sku de nyid la yang dang yang du thim pa'i snang ba byung zhing / de'i tho rangs de lta bu'i dge slong zhig gis / khyod kyis bstan pa dang sems can la phan pa rgya chen po de grub zin pas dga' ba sgoms shig ces pa'i lung bstan kyang byung la / de ni| sngar mkhas grub thams cad mkhyen pa'i lung bstan dang / bdag gi bla ma mkhas grub chen po'i mnal lam yang tshad mar grub pa yin no / / gzhan yang de'i dus su dgra bcom pa 'char kha zhes pa'i rje rang gi slob ma zhig gi gzigs snang la nyi ma gnyis shar byung ba'i snga ma de da lta'i @# / / nyi ma 'di dang / phyi ma de 'di bas che ba cig byung ba de'i 'od zer gyis gtsug lag khang gi nang khyab byung / gzhan ni ma go / nga rang 'khrul ba yin par 'dug snyam du dgongs nas gzhan la ye ma bshad ces gsung ngo / / byams pa lha khang gi sgo 'di yang

/ nyan zhes pa'i yul nas klu mo bkra shis skyid ces pa'i rje rang gi dge bsnyen ma zhig gis phul bar grags shing / rje btsun gyi ldem gnyis phyis rje rang nyid kyis bzhengs pa yin no| |de nas shing pho spre'u'i lo la mdzad pa kun las gsung gi mdzad pa mchog tu dgongs nas / phyogs kyi yig mkhan mang po bsdus te thugs dam bka' 'gyur gyi gsung rab rnams bzhengs shing / gtsug lag khang gi rgya mdzad chen mo'i ri mo mdzad dgos rnams kyang dpon mo che sman thar pas legs par mdzad pa yin no / / lo de'i dpyid ka bdag gis byang chen du chos bar zhig la phyin dus sngar nas kyi gzhi nad drag po zhig yod pa de rkyen dbang gis langs te shi la thug pa'i tshe rten 'brel bsgrig pa'i phyir du legs bshad gser phreng po ti gcig rje'i drung du phul te gdams pa cig zhu ba la btang bas de'i lan du / da lan mi 'chi / gal ten 'di ltar gyis gsung ba'i zhal gyi gdams pa phebs pa tsam gyis blo bde bar byung / de'i tshe bdag gi bsam pa la dang po spre'u'i lo la rje 'di nyid kyis byang gnas 'dir thugs dam mdzad pas bar chad kyi mtshan ma bzlog pa yin par 'dug / nga rang yang gnas 'dir mtshams dam pa cig byed do snyam nas lo de'i zla ba bdun pa nas brtsams te dge sbyor la shin tu 'grus par byas so / / de nas bdag gis byang chen du zla ba bcu mtshams dam par byas pas bar chad bzlog pa'i mtshan ma yang ci rigs byung ste dbus phyogs la 'gro 'dod pa dang / sems dpa' chen po blo gros sbas pa la chos cig zhu 'dod sngar nas yod pa rnams kyi gnang ba zhu ba la lo de'i sog 'dir 'ongs / rje rin po che'i drung du de'i rgyu mtshan phul bas rje'i zhal nas / dbus phyogs la 'gro don med| bstan pa spyi sgos la bsams te da dung 'dir ka 'chad nyan byas na jo bo rin po che dang rje btsun tsong kha pa yang 'di phyogs na ka bzhugs / yang thugs dam sgrub pa byed na yang 'dir ka sdod / nged kyang dgon pa 'di'i thod la sgrub sde zhig 'dzugs 'dod yod pas der dpon slob gnyis kyi zhabs tog byed / da lan drung 'dul ba pa la chos nyan du 'gro na khong la lha mo 'di'i bka' zhig dang / byang chub lam rim gyi 'khrid / lta ba'i 'khrid / khyad par 'dus pa'i rim lnga'i dmar khrid cig rnams zhus te myur bar 'dir byon / bdag gis kyang de rnams legs par thob ste / da na so rgas nas brjed 'dug / dang po dpe cha mang po zin pa cig yod de / da tshig re re la'ang dka' las che bar 'dug / don la 'chi ba
