brtag pa / ! man ngag rgya mtsho'i gling la dbang sgyur ba'i / / ded dpon bla ma'i zhabs la gus btud nas / / gnas skabs mthar thug tshe 'di'i dgos 'dod kun / / dngos sam rmi lam brtag pa'i zhal gdams bri / / lha mo shra ma Na'i sgo nas rmi lam brtag pa la gnyis las / dang po ni / 'gal rkyen bsal / mthun rkyen bsgrubs nas / yar ngo'i dus bzang po la / gnas dben par gtsang ma byas nas / sa'i dkyil 'khor grub bzhi dri bzang gis byugs pa'i steng du bum pa bcud dang chu gtsang gis bkang / bal dkar sogs kyis mgul pa brgyan cing / shug rlon sogs ljon shing gtsang mas kha brgyan / gos dar sngon po'i rigs kyi gur phub cing / mchod rdzas gtsang mas bskor / dkon mchog gi rten ci 'byor bshams / rnam rtog gi spro bsdu bcad cing / lus ngag gi mtshams dam po bya / rab cho ga ma tshar bar du smyung gnas bya zhing / thams kyang phyi dro'i kha zas dang / sha chad sgog gsum / khyad par zwa tshod spang / 'grul dang grib can gyi zas dang grib la 'dzem / dkon mchog gi drung du / dus gsum la stobs bzhi'i bshags pa rtag tu bya ste / de dag ni gnad che'o / / gnyis pa sgrub thabs ni / skyabs 'gro sems skyed tshad med bzhi sngon du btang / swa b+ha was stong par sbyang / de'i dang las / bum pa rin po che sna bzhi las grub pa'i ri rab steng thams cad paiDU r+ya'i sa gzhis khyab pa / kha rgyan dgos 'dod 'byung ba'i dpag bsam shing gi sdong po / yal ga / lo ma / me tog / '+p+ras bu sna tshogs pas brgyan pa / gur steng 'og gi nam mkha' sngon por bsgom / ri rab kyi steng du lha mo shra ma Na sku mdog sngon mo zhal gcig phyag gnyis ma / g.yas pas rda yab bam / me long / g.yon pa dpag bsam shing gi yal ga 'dzin pa / @# / / zhabs gnyis brkyangs nas ri rab la brkyangs 'dug gi tshul du bzhugs ba / dpag bsam gyi shing gi sdong po la rgyab brten pa / rked pa phra ba / nu ma 'bur ba / zhal 'dzum pa dang bcas pas rang la gzigs pa / dar sna tshogs pa'i stod g.yogs dang smad g.yogs can / rat+na dang me tog sna tshogs pa'i rgyan gyis spras te mdzes shing yid du 'od ba / dus gsum gyi shes byam lus par mkhyen pas bdag la lung thams cad mngon sum du ston par bsgom / de nas dar skud la brgyus pa'i me tog gam nas gtsang ma 'bru bdun thal mo sbyar ba'i bar du bzungs nas / dad gus rtse gcig pas / mkhyen rab kyi dbang phyug shra ma Na bdag ming 'di zhes bya

ba tshe phyi ma gang du skye ba'i gnas de mi slu bar da lta nyid du bstan du gsol / zhes pa gsum nas nyer gcig gi bar gsol ba btab nas lha mo'i phyag tu phul bar bsams te / mgul chings kyi bar du gtums / kha rgyan la btags nas 'dod don gang yin de gsol ba gdab pa'i yid rtse gcig pas / oM shra ma Na pi shA tsi ni pi mun+d+he swA hA / zhes pa bzlas te / 'di khri tsho bcu gnyis bsnyen pa byas na / sa 'og gi gter kyang dngos su mthong bar 'gyur gsung ngo| |thun mtshams su gong bzhin gsol ba btab cing me tog gtor ro / / de nas srod kyi dus su lhag par 'bad cing / mgo po byang / rkang pa lho / kha nub / rgyab shar du bstan te / mgo po lha mo'i pad du bzhag par mos shing / sems gzhan du ma yengs par brtag bya 'ba' zhig yid la byed sngas shub bus bzlas shing / nyal ba man ngag dam pa'o / / de yang nub cig la don gcig las mi 'od bar gsung pas / dang po gal che ba gcig kho na yid la bya zhing brtag / de grub nas gzhan la 'don pa bsgyur zhing brtag go / 'dis rang gzhan kun gyi skye ba snga phyi / tshe ring thung / don bzang dan / gang phan gang gnod sogs byang chub ma thob bar gyi mngon mtho nges legs sogs kun brtag tu btub bo / / de yang / rab dngos su lung ston pa'am nyams snang la 'char / 'bring nam mkha' la sgra grag pa 'od / tha ma rmi lam du ston pa'o / / de yang dri ba dri lan gyi tshul du dang / brda byed pa sogs kyi mi gsal ba 'byung ste / dpyad dka' ba rnams dpyod shes par bya'o / / yang na mi gsal ba thams cad dor nas / yang yang bskyar na phyis gsal po yong ngo / / rmi lam man ngag gi stobs kyis bzang ngan gyis su re zhig nges kyang / dge sdig gi stobs kyis 'gyur 'od pas / bzang po byung na de las kyang bzang ba dang / ngan pa zlog pa'i thabs bstan du gsol byas la de byung ba dang / thabs de la 'bad par bya'o / / de ltar bsgrubs na / rab zhag gsum / 'bring lnga / tha ma n+b+dun la 'grub bo / / des ma grub na / grib dang sdig shas che ba'i rtags yin pas grib la 'dzem zhing mtshams bsdams / sdig bshags la @# / / nus pa 'don / lan gsum bskyar na mi 'grub mi srid gsung ngo / / byung tshad mi la bshad na mi gsal ngas / gsang ba gal che'o / / sgrol ma'i sprul pa sha ma Na'i gdams pa 'di 'dra ba med par bla ma'i gsung bzhin myong

bas grub po / / ! / / ye shes mgon po phyag drug pa'i mnga' gsol / ! hUM / phyogs bcu'i rgyal ba kun gyi sku gsung thugs / / snyigs dus ma rungs gdug pa 'dul pa'i phyir / / gang la gang 'dul khro bo'i skur ston pa / / sangs rgyas kun gyi ngo bor mnga' gsol lo / / rang bzhin rnam dag sgrib gnyis 'ching las grol / / mkha' ltar kun khyab smra bsam brjod las 'das / / brgyad khri bzhi stong dam chos ma lus pa'i / / 'byung gnas myur mdzad mgon por mnga' gsol lo / / rab 'byams zhing gi rgyal ba kun gyi yab / / sa bcu'i dbang phyug rgyal sras kun gyi gtso / / nyan thos rang rgyal 'phags tshogs kun gyi rje / / tshogs mchog zhing gi dam par mnga' gsol lo / / gdug pa 'dul phyir khros pa'i gar mdzad kyang / / dngos grub rnam gnyis 'dod dgu'i char 'bebs shing / / rtsa rgyud bla ma kun dang dbyer med pa'i / / bla ma mgon po dbyer med mnga' gsol lo / / dngos grub rtsa ba bla ma mchog rnams dang / / dbyer med chos sku'i ngo bor ro gcig kyang / / dregs pa'i stobs kyis dgra bgegs tshar gcod phyir / / mgon po bla ma dbyer med mnga' gsol lo| |ma lus rgyal ba'i bstan srungs kun gyi gtso / / khyod ni rnal 'byor yongs kyi dgra lha dang / / rig 'dzin sgrub rgyud rnams kyi srung ma dang / / bdud 'dul dmag dpon chen por mnga' gsol lo / / myur mdzad spyan ras gzigs dbang thugs rje'i gter / / dran pa tsam gyis mi mthun mtha' dag sel / / bar do'i 'jigs skyobs mkha' spyod gnas su 'khrid / / slu med skyabs kyi dam par mnga' gsol lo / / rgyal ba'i bstan dang bstan 'dzin skyong ba dang| |khyad par chos kyi rgyal po tsong kha pa'i / / bstan dang bstan 'dzin dgon gnas thams cad dang / / bdag cag dpon slob mi nor 'khor bcas rnams / / mthu ldan srung ma khyod la gnyer du gtad / / deng nas bzungs te byang chub snying po'i bar / / phyi nang 'gal rkyen thams cad khyod kyis gsol / / ma rungs dgra bgegs thams cad khyod kyis thul / / mdor na dpon slob 'khor dang bcas rnams kyi / / tshe dang bsod nams dpal 'byor rgyas pa sogs mthun rkyen bsam pa'i don rnams ma lus pa / / 'bad med lhun gyis grub pa'i 'phrin las mdzod / / bstan pa bsrung phyir mnga' gsol lo / / dgra bgegs sgrol phyir mnga' gsol lo / / dngos grub stsol phyir mnga' gsol lo / / mnga' gsol don dang ldan par mdzod / / 'di yang rje thams cad mkhyen pa'i gsung ngo / / dge'o / / / / mgon po legs ldan gyi

gtor chog bzhugs so / ! mgon po legs ldan gyi gtor chog @# / / rgyas par byed na / bdag nyid 'phags pa gdugs dkar mo can gyi rnal 'byor du ldan pas / ri rab lhun po bang rim bzhi pa / cog brgyad dang ldan pa'i steng du / dur khrod chen po brgyad na ro dang ro langs gar byed pa dang / hUM sgra sgrog pa dang / phan tshun kun tu rgyug pa dang / 'dre dang srin po dang / mkha' 'gro dang / mkha' 'gro ma ro la rtse zhing / sha khrag la rol pa dang / kaM ka dang / bya rgod dang / bya rog sna tshogs pa ro la za zhing / rgyu ma drangs te / nam mkha' la lding ba rnams dang / 'ug pa hUM sgra sgrog pa dang / sbrul ba lang gi mgo can phyogs kun tu rnam par rgyug pa dang / ro phyed tshig pa dang / gsal shing la btags pa la sogs pa du mas yongs su gang ba'i khrod na chos 'byung mthing nag gru gsum rab tu 'bar ba'i nang du / sna tshogs padma dang nyi ma'i gdan gsum bsgrigs pa'i steng du dgra bgegs bdug pa can bsgral ba'i ro kha nas khrag skyug bzhin pa'i snying khar hUM mthing nag 'bar ba re re de rnams las 'od 'phros / bdug pa can thams cad tshar bcad / rgyal ba sras dang bcas pa'i mthu nus gcig tu bsdus te / hUM la thims pas mgon po legs ldan nag po mched gsum| sku mdog mthing nag rab tu khros pa zhal mche ba rnam par gtsigs shing / ljags 'dril ba / spyan gsum gdangs shing glog ltar 'khyug pa / smin ma g.yo zhing / khro gnyer bsdus pa / phyag g.yas pa tsan+dan gyi bde chen bsnams pa / g.yon pa dgra bgegs kyi sha khrag dang / don snying gis gang ba'i thod pa bsnams nas zhal du gsol ba / dar nag gi 'jol ber sku la gsol ba / mi mgo bskam po lnga'i dbu rgyan dang| rlon pa khrag 'dzag pa lnga bcu'i 'phreng ba mgul du 'phyang ba / sbrul nag gi chun 'phyang dang / dar gyi lhab lhub dang / stag lpags kyi shams thabs can / zhabs gnyis gyad kyi dor stabs kyis 'gying zhing brjid pa / byang phyogs gnod sbyin gyi sde dpon mang po khyung dang / kaM ka dang / bya rgod dang / 'ug pa dang / khra la sogs pa'i 'dab chags su sbrul nas / nam mkha' la lding zhing / klad la 'khor nas bar snang gi gdon bgegs thams cad tshar gcod pa / lho phyogs gshin rje'i sde dpon mang po / seng ge dang / stag dang / gzig dang / dom dang / ce sbyang la sogs pa'i gcan gzan du sprul nas / sa steng dang sa 'og gi gdon bgegs thams cad gnas nas skrod cing tshar gcod pa /

sku las sprul pa'i khro bo nyi zla'i zer dang / skar chen gyi 'od ltar du 'phros pas / phyogs mtshams gyi gdug pa can thams cad tshar gcod pa / lha srin sde brgyad kyi dmag dpung sa ya / 'bum sde dbyar gyi char sprin ltar gtibs pa hUM phaT dang / b+h+yoH bzlog gi sgra skad 'brug ltar sgrog cing / mtshon cha sna tshogs thog ltar 'phen pas bstan pa'i dgra bgegs tshar gcod pa'i bdag nyid can du gsal bar bsgoms la / @# / / gtso 'khor rnams kyi spyi bor oM / mgrin par AH thugs kar hUM / de dag las 'od 'phros rgyal ba sras dang bcas pa'i sku gsung thugs kyi mthu nus dang / yon tan bsdus te yig 'bru gsum la thim / slar yang 'od zer 'phros / 'og mi ni gya gnas dang / ri rab kyi steng dang / dur khrod chen po so sha gling la sogs pa nas ye shes kyi mgon po 'khor dang bcas pa spyan drangs shing / gu gul dkar nag dang / sha chen dang / shing kun dang / dug dang / / sgog skya rnams sbyar ba'i bdug spos sreg cing / ! mthu chen mgon po nag po ni / / mched gsum 'khor dang bcas pa rnams / / mngon tshe bskal pa dang po la / / bcom ldan shAkya seng ge yi / / spyan sngar khas blangs dam bcas bzhin / / sangs rgyas bstan pa bsrung ba dang / / rnal 'byor 'phrin las bsgrub pa'i phyir / / dad pa dang ni dam tshig gis / / gnas 'dir spyan 'dren gshegs su gsol / / oM mahA kA la b+ha ga wan sa pa ri wA ra A kar+Sha ya dzaH dzaH zhes pas spyan drangs / padma ka ma la ye stwaM / sUr+ya maN+Da la hUM / zhes pas gdan la bzhugs / dzaH hUM baM hoH gnyis su med par bstim / oM shrI mahA kA la ye sa pa ri wA ra sa ma ya / sma ra sa ma ya / ma ti ka ma sa ma ya / rak+Shan+tu dang / thal mo zlum por sbyar ba mgo thams cad kyi phyag rgya bcas te / mgon po 'khor bcas kyi spyi bor dam tshig rdo rje bzhag nas dam la bzhag par bsam zhing / rdo rje 'di ni rdo rje che / / sangs rgyas kun gyi byin gyis brlabs / / gal te dam tshig 'das gyur na / / 'jig 'gyur 'di la the tshom med / / rje btsun rtsa ba dang brgyud par bcas pa'i bla ma dam pa rnams dang / rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas gdung bdun dang / phyogs bcu'i rgyal ba 'khor dang bcas pa rnams dang / 'phags ma gdugs dkar mo can / phyag rgya'i tshogs dang bcas pa rnams kyis bka' bsgos shing dam la bzhag ste / de dag gi spyan sngar srog gi snying po phul nas ji ltar

khas blangs shing| dam bcas pa bzhin du dpal mgon legs ldan nag po 'khor dang bcas pa khyed rnams kyis sangs rgyas kyi bstan pa srungs shig / dkon mchog gi dbu 'phang bstod cig / rnal 'byor pa bdag gis bcol ba'i 'phrin las myur du sgrubs shig / ces brjod par bya'o / / de nas| nas dang sran ma nag po'i phye la gzhi byas pa'i gtor ma sha khrag dang / dar nag gis brgyan pa chang dang bdud rtsis bran te / oM AH hUM hoH sa byin gyis brlabs la| oM mahA shi ra b+h+yoH mahA kA la du tri b+h+yoH mahA ka la duSh+TaM b+h+yoH i daM pa liM ta kha kha khA hi khA hi / zhes pa gsum gyis phul / 'khor rnams la a kA ros bsdos la / ar+g+haM la sogs pas mchod / srin po'i gzugs gyi gdug pa can / ces sogs dang / ! hUM bstan pa bsrung ba'i mthu stobs can / / legs ldan nag po dka' thub las / / bzlog par byed pa'i bdag po dang / / lhan cig pa la phyag 'tshal lo / / nag po chen po @# / / rdzu 'phrul can / / <ALLO.legs ldan nag po sred med bu / / phyag rgya chen po lnga rnams kyis / / phyag byas pa la bdag bstod do / / grong khyer sum brtsegs 'jig byed pa / / legs ldan nag po dur khrod na / / gnas par mos pa ma mo yi / / tshogs kyi phyag byas khyod la 'dud / / dpal mgon mched gsum lcam bral dang / / lha srin sde brgyad 'khor bcas kun / / sha khrag dmar gyis brgyan pa yi / / mchod sbyin gtor ma 'di bzhes la rnal 'byor bdag cag 'khor bcas la / / nad med tshe dang dbang phyug dang / / dpal dang grags dang skal pa bzang / / longs spyod rgya chen kun thob cing / / zhi dang rgyas la sogs pa yi / / las kyi dngos grub bdag la stsol / / dam tshig ldan pas bdag la srungs / / dngos grub kun gyi grogs mdzod cig / dus min 'chi dang nad rnams dang / / gdon dang bgegs rnams med par mdzod / / rmi lam ngan dang mtshan ma ngan / / bya byed ngan pa med par mdzod / / 'jig rten bde zhing lo legs dang / / 'bru rnams rgyas shing chos 'phel dang / / bde legs phun sum tshogs pa dang / / yid la 'dod pa kun 'grub shog / ces bstod la 'phrin las gzhol / mgon po mched gsum gyi thugs kar pad nyi'i steng du / hUM mthing nag la rang rang gi sngags kyis bskor ba las 'phrin las rnam bzhi ji ltar 'dod pa bzhin sgrub pa'i 'od zer gyi 'phro 'du la dmigs nas / dbus su oM mahA kA la sha ri b+h+yo hUM phaT / g.yas su

oM mahA kA la ra traM b+h+yo hUM phaT / g.yon du oM mahA kA la duSh+TaM b+h+yo hUM phaT / nag po chen po spyi'i rtsa sngags / oM mahA kA la shA sa na / u pa ha ri Ni zhes sogs ci nus bzlas / thun gyi tha mar / / mchod bstod gsol ba btab nas gshegs su gsol / ! hUM dus gsum rgyal ba sras bcas kyi / / mthu stobs gcig tu bsdus pa'i sku / / legs ldan nag po dam tshig can / / gtum chen khyed la phyag 'tshal lo / / dur khrod chen po'i dkyil 'khor du / / 'jigs su rung ba bskal pa'i me / / dmar nag 'bar ba'i klong dkyil na / / bzhugs pa khyod la phyag 'tshal lo / / mthing nag zhal gcig phyag gnyis pa / / zhal gdangs mche gtsigs hUM sgra sgrog / drag po'i spyan gsum glog ltar g.yo / / rngam chen khyod la phyag 'tshal lo / / phyag g.yas tsan+dan bde chen gyis / / srid gsum gdug pa 'dul byed cing / / lha chen ma lus zil gyis gnon / / 'jom mdzad khyod la phyag 'tshal lo / / g.yon pa dgra bgegs don snying dang / / khrag gis gang pa'i thod pa bsnams / / mi dang mi min gdug pa can / / gsod byed khyed la phyag 'tshal lo / / zhabs gnyis gyad kyi dor stabs kyis / / sa gzhi ri rab khor yug dang / / rgya mtshor bcas pa'i 'jig rten kun / / g.yo byed khyed la phyag 'tshal lo / / sku la dar nag ber chen dang / / dug sbrul khros pa'i chun 'phyang dang / / dgra bgegs bsgral ba'i mgo 'phreng gis / / brjid pa khyod la phyag 'tshal lo / / @# / / rlung ltar mgyogs shing g.yo ba yi / / rdzu 'phrul zhabs kyis phyogs kun tu / / dam tshig kun rjes gcod pa yi / / myur mgyogs khyod la phyag 'tshal lo / / sgrib med phyogs bcur gzigs pa yi ye shes spyan ni rnon po yis / / 'jig rten legs nyes kun gyi stangs / / gzigs pa khyod la phyag 'tshal lo / / zhi rgyas dbang dang drag po yi / / 'phrin las kun la thogs med pas / / sangs rgyas bstan pa phyogs bcu ru / / skyong ba khyod la phyag 'tshal lo / / bstan pa 'dzin pa'i skyes bu rnams / / yid la ji ltar bsams pa bzhin / / mchog dang thun mong dngos grub kun / / ster ba khyod la phyag 'tshal lo / / rdzogs sangs rgyas kyi spyan snga ru / / ji ltar khas blangs dam bcas bzhin / / rnal 'byor bdag gis bcol ba yi / / 'phrin las myur du 'grub par mdzod / ces pas bstod la / legs ldan nag po mched gsum 'khor bcas kun / /

bstan pa bsrung dang 'gro ba'i don mdzad phyir / / dpal chen bka' sdod yid ltar mgyogs pa yi / / 'jigs pa'i gzugs can drag gtum mi bzad pa / / gdug pa 'dul mdzad nag po'i phyogs 'joms mdzad / / rnal 'byor las la 'bras bu ster mdzad pa'i / / mthu stobs byin rlabs bsam gyis mi khyab pa / / sde brgyad btsun mo sras dang g.yog bcas la / / dmar chen gtor ma dar nag cod pan can / / sha khrag chang phud bcas pa'i dam rdzas 'di / / ting 'dzin sngags dang phyag rgyas byin brlabs nas / / ri dang rgya mtshor mnyam pa dmigs te 'bul / / dar nag rgyal mtshan rkang dung thod rnga dang / / bsur chen dud pa bdud rtsi'i ro mchog dang / / stag lpags na bza' ther chen nag po dang / / 'dod yon rnam lngas khyed kyi thugs dam bskangs / / g.yag nag zhol chen sprin ltar 'thibs pa dang / / lug nag spyi dkar shel ltar 'tsher ba dang / / khyi nag snying dkar dom ltar mchong ba yis / / legs ldan 'khor dang bcas pa'i thugs dam bskangs / / bya nag gsob dang 'ug pa'i rgyal mtshan dang / / dam nyams dgra bgegs bsgral ba'i sha khrag dang / / g.yang gzhi'i bla bre rgyu ma'i lnga ldi yis / / legs ldan 'khor dang bcas pa'i thugs dam bskangs / / 'gro mgyogs yid ltar g.yo ba'i rdzu 'phrul can / / char sprin lta bu'i ze rngog kun tu g.yo / / rta nag mdzes pa'i rgyan gyis brgyan pa 'dis / / legs ldan 'khor dang bcas pa'i thugs dam bskangs / / mgon med 'gro la phan pa'i bsam sbyor dang / / thub dbang bstan pa rgyas shing gnas pa'i phyir / / bsnyen sgrub mchod gtor sgo gsum dge ba yi / / 'bad pa ci bgyis de yis thugs dam bskangs / / sgo gsum las dang nyon mongs dbang gyur pas / / so so thar dang byang sems gsang sngags kyi / / bslab gsum nyams pa'i nyes ltung ci mchis pa / / dmigs med thugs rje'i ngang nas bzod par gsol / / bag med dbang gis thub pa'i gsung rab la / / @# / / ma gus shes bzhin khyad du bsang pa dang / / rdo rje theg pa'i dam tshig bsrung mtshams las / / 'gal zhing nongs par spyad pa bzod par gsol / / theg mchog byang chub chen por sems bskyed nas 'gro la phan bde'i bsam sbyor zhan pa dang / / rang nyid zhi bde don du gnyer ba yi / / rgyal ba'i thugs kyis khrel ba bzod par gsol / / rnam dag lta ba'i rang bzhin ma shes bzhin / / blang dor spyod pa'i tshul la mi mkhas pas| |gsung rab lung gi dgongs don zab mo la / / rang bzo 'khrul pas spyad pa bzod

par gsol / / lta ba yod med phyogs su lhung ba dang / / sgom pa rnam g.yeng dbang du gyur pa dang / / spyong ba ngo lkog tshul 'chos ches pa yi / / rgyal ba'i gsung dang 'gal ba bzod par gsol / / rnam g.yeng dbang gis bsnyen sgrub g.yel ba dang / / ser sna'i dbang gis mchod gtor zhan pa dang / / rmongs pa'i dbang gis blang dor mi shes pas| |sgo gsum nyes pa'i tshogs rnams bzod par gsol / / mdor na spyi dang khyad par dam tshig las / / 'das shing 'khrul par gyur pa ci mchis pa / / nongs shing 'gyod pa'i sems kyis bshags par bgyi / / dmigs med thugs rje'i dang du bzod par gsol / / nyes ltung 'khrul pa'i rnam smin ma lus pa / / nam mkha'i sprin tshogs rlung gis gtor ba dang / / bar snang 'ja' tshon rang sar yal ba ltar / / stong gsal gdong nas dag pa'i rang bzhin du / / rnam par dag cing rgya mtsho'i rba rlabs ltar / / 'od gsal chos sku'i ngang du zhi gyur cig / ces pa 'di yang / paN chen dge 'dun grub pa dpal bzang pos mdzad pa'o / / / / ! chos rgyal yab yum gyi bskang gso bstod bskul dang bcas pa bzhugs / ! na mo b+ha ga wa te badzra b+hai rA kro d+ha rA dzA b+haiH hUM| dpal ldan bla ma rnams kyi thugs rje dang / / dpal chen rgyal ba sras bcas byin rlabs dang| |dpal mchog sangs rgyas bstan pa'i gzi brjid dang / / dpal mgon srung ma rnams kyi mthu rtsal mchog / chos dbyings rnam par dag pa'i bden pa dang / / gsang sngags phyag rgya ting 'dzin nus pa'i mthu / / rnal 'byor lhag bsam dag pa'i bden stobs kyis / / zhing khams kun gyi phyi nang gsang ba dang / / bla na med pa'i mchod sprin rgya mtsho'i tshogs / / chos rgyal 'khor bcas dgyes pa bskyed pa yi / / sgyu ma rnam par rol pa ji bzhin du / / rab 'byams zhing du mtha' med 'phel gyur nas / / thugs dam bskong zhing bzhed pa 'grub gyur cig / hUM| rin chen 'byung gnas kun nas 'khyil ba'i mtsho / / rin chen sa gzhi brten pa'i rgya mtsho dang / / rin chen bye ma 'dren pa'i chu'o dang / rin chen mchod yon rdzas kyis gtams pa dang / / dgra bgegs bsgral ba'i rak+ta'i rgya mtsho 'dis / / dam can chos rgyal chen po'i thugs dam bskang / / yum mchog tsA muN+Di yi thugs dam bskang / / srog bdag @# / / gshin rje brgyad kyi thugs dam bskang / / dbugs len ma mo brgyad kyi thugs dam bskang / / sgrol byed las mkhan rnams kyi thugs dam bskang / / las gshin pho mo rnams kyi thugs dam bskang / / bka' sdod

'khor dang bcas pa'i thugs dam bskang / / rnal 'byor nyams chags ma lus dag pa dang / / gnod byed gdug pa'i tshogs rnams tshar gcod mdzod / / mthu chen rnams kyi sprul pa'i tshogs rnams dang| |rin chen ri gling mdzes sdug padmo'i phreng / / mu chen thang chen las skyes 'dab brgyad dang / / stong chen khams kun khyab pa'i me tog dang / / gdug chen rnams kyi dbang po rnam lnga 'dis / / dam can chos rgyal chen po'i thugs dam bskang / / yum mchog tsA muN+Di yi thugs dam bskang / / srog bdag gshin rje brgyad kyi thugs dam bskang / / dbugs len ma mo brgyad kyi thugs dam bskang / / sgrol byed las mkhan rnams kyi thugs dam bskang / / las gshin pho mo rnams kyi thugs dam bskang / / bka' sdod 'khor dang bcas pa'i thugs dam bskang / / rnal 'byor nyams chags ma lus dag pa dang / / gnod byed gdug pa'i tshogs rnams tshar gcod mdzod / / rab bzang tsan+dan rang bzhin ga pur sbos / / rab mang tshogs pa lhan cig sbyar ba'i spos / / rab dkar dag pa'i spos mchog thams cad kyi / / rab 'byams khams kun gang ba'i dud sprin dang / / dgra bo'i sha rus bsregs pa'i bdug pa 'dis / / dam can chos rgyal chen po'i thugs dam bskang / / yum mchog tsA muN+Di yi thugs dam bskang / / srog bdag gshin rje brgyad kyi thugs dam bskang / / dbugs len ma mo brgyad kyi thugs dam bskang / / sgrol byed las mkhan rnams kyi thugs dam bskang / / las gshin pho mo rnams kyi thugs dam bskang / / bka' sdod 'khor dang bcas pa'i thugs dam bskang / / rnal 'byor nyams chags ma lus dag pa dang / / gnod byed gdug pa'i tshogs rnams tshar gcod mdzod / / g.yo zhing gsal ba nyi ma zla ba dang / / brtan cing gsal ba rin chen ri rnams dang / / dag cing gsal ba nor bu dbang rgyal sogs / / 'bar zhing gsal ba sgron me'i rigs rnams dang / / zhun chen ro ras sbyar ba'i mar me 'dis / / dam can chos rgyal chen po'i thugs dam bskang / / yum mchog tsA muN+Di yi thugs dam bskang / / srog bdag gshin rje brgyad kyi thugs dam bskang / / dbugs len ma mo brgyad kyi thugs dam bskang / / sgrol byed las mkhan rnams kyi thugs dam bskang / las gshin pho mo rnams kyi thugs dam bskang / / bka' sdod 'khor dang bcas pa'i thugs dam bskang / / rnal 'byor nyams chags ma lus dag pa dang / / gnod byed gdug pa'i tshogs rnams tshar gcod mdzod / / rnam mang zhing gi dri yi tshal gyi tshogs / / rnam par sbyar ba'i dri @# / / mchog ci mchis dang / / rnam dag

dri 'dzin tshim par byed pa yi / / rnam gsum dri yis bkang pa'i mchod pa dang / / dam rgyal chen po'i rgyal chen po'i thugs dam bskang / / yum mchog tsA muN+Di yi thugs dam bskang / / srog bdag gshin rje brgyad kyi thugs dam bskang / / dbugs len ma mo brgyad kyi thugs dam bskang / / sgrol byed las mkhan rnams kyi thugs dam bskang / / las gshin pho mo rnams kyi thugs dam bskang / / bka' sdod 'khor dang bcas pa'i thugs dam bskang / / rnal 'byor nyams chags ma lus dag pa dang / / gnod byed gdug pa'i tshogs rnams tshar gcod mdzod / / ro bcud rnam par dag pa lha yi zas / / ro drug ldan pa khams kyi zas rnams dang / / ro 'dzin dbang po bde ba bskyed pa yi / / ro brgya ldan pa'i zhal zas rgya chen dang / / dgra bo'i sha rus ri ltar spungs pa 'dis / / dam can chos rgyal chen po'i thugs dam bskang / / yum mchog tsA muN+Di yi thugs dam bskang / / srog bdag gshin rje brgyad kyi thugs dam bskang / / dbugs len ma mo brgyad kyi thugs dam bskang / / sgrol byed las mkhan rnams kyi thugs dam bskang / / las gshin pho mo rnams kyi thugs dam bskang / / bka' sdod 'khor dang bcas pa'i thugs dam bskang / / rnal 'byor nyams chags ma lus dag pa dang / / gnod byed gdug pa'i tshogs rnams tshar gcod mdzod / / rnga chen la sogs brjid pa'i sgra rnams dang / / rgyud mang la sogs snyan pa'i sgra yi tshogs / / zin dang ma zin la sogs sgra kun dang / / cang ti'u la sogs bskul ba'i sgra rnams dang| |dgra bo'i ngag gi lam nas bsgrags pa 'dis / / dam can chos rgyal chen po'i thugs dam bskang / / yum mchog tsA muN+Di yi thugs dam bskang / / srog bdag gshin rje brgyad kyi thugs dam bskang / / dbugs len ma mo brgyad kyi thugs dam bskang / / sgrol byed las mkhan rnams kyi thugs dam bskang / / las gshin pho mo rnams kyi thugs dam bskang / / bka' sdod 'khor dang bcas pa'i thugs dam bskang / / rnal 'byor nyams chags ma lus dag pa dang / / gnod byed gdug pa'i tshogs rnams tshar gcod mdzod / / g.yang gzhi bla bre nam mkha' mdzes byed rgyan / / mi mgo'i phreng ba bar snang 'phyang ba'i rgyan / / keng rus bkram pa sa gzhi bkang pa'i rgyan| |rin chen phreng ba dngos grub gter ba'i rgyan / / phyag rgya rnam drug dpal chen sku yi rgyan / / khur dar chen po dpa' rtags ston pa'i rgyan / / brkyangs bskums tshul du bzhugs pa rngam pa'i rgyan / / dur khrod chas kun 'jigs pa skyed pa'i rgyan / / dpag med rgyan

gyi rim pa 'di dag gis / / dam can chos rgyal chen po'i thugs dam bskang / / yum mchog tsA muN+Di yi thugs dam bskang / / srog bdag gshin rje brgyad kyi thugs @# / / dam bskang / / dbugs len ma mo brgyad kyi thugs dam bskang / / sgrol byed las mkhan rnams kyi thugs dam bskang / / las gshin pho mo rnams kyi thugs dam bskang / / bka' sdod 'khor dang bcas pa'i thugs dam bskang / / rnal 'byor nyams chags ma lus dag pa dang / / gnod byed gdug pa'i tshogs rnams tshar gcod mdzod / / thod chen mkha' ltar yangs pa'i nang nyid du / / sha lnga bdud rtsi lnga dang sbyar ba yi / / myos byed stong gi bcud kyis legs par gtams / / rlung g.yos me sbar rdzas rnams zhu zhing khol / / rdo rje gsum dang dbyer med 'dres pa las / / kha dog dri ro nus pa phul du phyin / / ting 'dzin sngags dang phyag rgyas byin gyis brlabs / / sbyang rtogs sbar ba'i zag med bdud rtsi 'dis / / dam can chos rgyal chen po'i thugs dam bskang / / yum mchog tsA muN+Di yi thugs dam bskang / / srog bdag gshin rje brgyad kyi thugs dam bskang / / dbugs len ma mo brgyad kyi thugs dam bskang / / sgrol byed las mkhan rnams kyi thugs dam bskang / / las gshin pho mo rnams kyi thugs dam bskang / / bka' sdod 'khor dang bcas pa'i thugs dam bskang / / rnal 'byor nyams chags ma lus dag pa dang / / gnod byed gdug pa'i tshogs rnams tshar gcod mdzod / / khrag zhag myos byed 'khyil ba'i rgya mtsho'i dbus / / 'bru sna sman sna rin chen sna tshogs dang / / 'bru mchog zan dang dmar chen sha rnams spungs / / dar nag gur dang mda' dar rten bcas btsugs / / mthun rdzas rten rdzas sgrub rdzas sogs dang sbyar / / dgra bo'i sha rus sogs dang gnyis su med / / tshim zhing dgyes pa'i nus pa phul du phyin / / dam rdzas dmar chen gtor ma 'di nyid kyis / / dam can chos rgyal chen po'i thugs dam bskang / / yum mchog tsA muN+Di yi thugs dam bskang / / srog ? gshin rje brgyad kyi thugs dam bskang / / dbugs len ma mo brgyad kyi thugs dam bskang / / sgrol byed las mkhan rnams kyi thugs dam bskang / / las gshin pho mo rnams kyi thugs dam bskang / / bka' sdod 'khor dang bcas pa'i thugs dam bskang / / rnal 'byor nyams chags ma lus dag pa dang / / gnod byed gdug pa'i tshogs rnams tshar gcod mdzod / / dgra bgegs gzhug par byed pa'i ling+ga'i las / / dgra bgegs 'dul bar byed pa gtor ma'i las / / dgra bgegs gzir bar byed pa thun gyi las /

/ dgra bgegs 'khrugs par byed pa 'khor lo'i las / / dgra bgegs dbye bar byed pa rdzas kyi las / / dgra bgegs lkugs par byed pa mnan pa'i las| |dgra bgegs lha dang phral ba kha sbyor las / / dgra bgegs bzlog par byed pa zor gyi las / / dgra bgegs ltas ngan gyis dkrugs man+de'i las / / dgra bgegs bsdigs shing spa bkong sbyin sreg @# / / las / / dgra bgegs 'brub par byed pa hom khung las / / dgra bgegs srog dang phral ba bsad pa'i las / / bsnyen cing sgrub dang bskul ba dmigs pa'i las / / stobs chen las kyi rim pa 'di dag gis / / dam can chos rgyal chen po'i thugs dam bskang / / yum mchog tsA muN+Di yi thugs dam bskang / / srog bdag gshin rje brgyad kyi thugs dam bskang / / dbugs len ma mo brgyad kyi thugs dam bskang / / sgrol byed las mkhan rnams kyi thugs dam bskang / / las gshin pho mo rnams kyi thugs dam bskang / / bka' sdod 'khor dang bcas pa'i thugs dam bskang / / rnal 'byor nyams chags ma lus dag pa dang / / gnod byed gdug pa'i tshogs rnams tshar gcod mdzod / / stong gsum gang ba'i sprul pa rnam par 'gyed / / khams gsum g.yo ba'i ngar sgra drag po sgrog / dus gsum sdang pa'i dgra dang bgegs kyi gshed / / sgo gsum gzir ba'i cha lugs rnam 'gyur can / / mig sman ltar nag sprin gyi shugs la 'gran / / lhun po ltar brjid mig dmar gyen la bzlog / dom nag lta bur kha gdangs mche ba gtsigs / / khro chen lta bur rus pa'i rgyan cha thogs / / nyi ma'i bu ni yan lag bzhi yis mnan / / sa srungs bu yi stobs la 'gran par byed / / gshin rje'i bu yi brjid kyis mnan gyur kyang / / ma he'i bu khyod dgra bo'i yul kun myul / / spu sdug mdzes pa'i gos bzang rnam par bgos / / nor bu'i tshogs kyi dra bas rnam par spras / / sna tshogs dar gyi rgyan gyis rnam par bkab / / stobs chen shugs dang rnam par ldan pa 'dis / / dam can chos rgyal chen po'i thugs dam bskang / / yum mchog tsA muN+Di yi thugs dam bskang / / srog bdag gshin rje brgyad kyi thugs dam bskang / / dbugs len ma mo brgyad kyi thugs dam bskang / / sgrol byed las mkhan rnams kyi thugs dam bskang / / las gshis pho mo rnams kyi thugs dam bskang / / bka' sdod 'khor dang bcas pa'i thugs dam bskang / / rnal 'byor nyams chags ma lus dag pa dang / / gnod byed gdug pa'i tshogs rnams tshar gcod mdzod / / go cha mchon cha rgyan cha'i tshogs rnams dang / / rta nag g.yag nag lug nag khyi nag dang

/ / ri bdun mtsho bdun rgyal srid sna bdun dang / / rig ma mchog ma gzugs ma mdzes ma dang / / phyi rten nang rten gsang ba'i rten rnams dang / / 'dod 'jo 'dod yon 'dod dgu 'byung ba dang / / dam rdzas tshogs rdzas 'gugs pa'i rdzas rnams dang / / lha mchod klu mchod mi yi mchod pa 'dis / / dam can chos rgyal chen po'i thugs dam bskang / / yum mchog tsA mu N+Di yi thugs dam bskang / / srog bdag gshin rje brgyad kyi thugs dam bskang / / dbugs len ma mo brgyad kyi thugs dam bskang / / sgrol byed las mkhan rams kyi thugs dam bskang / / las gshin pho mo @# / / rnams kyi thugs dam bskang / / bka' sdod 'khor dang bcas pa'i thugs dam bskang / / rnal 'byor nyams chags ma lus dag pa dang / / gnod byed gdug pa'i tshogs rnams tshar gcod mdzod / gser gling zangs gling nor bu'i gling rnams dang / / bum pa thod pa 'jon pa'i tshogs rnams dang / / dril bu gling bu shar bu'i rigs rnams dang / / khang bzang gos bzang tshal bzang tshogs rnams dang / / dar rgyan rus rgyan rin chen rgyan rnams dang / / rol mo sgeg mo la sogs mchod pa dang / / phyi mchod nang mchod gsang ba'i mchod pa dang / / 'khor gsum sgo gsum dus gsum mchod pa 'dis / / dam can chos rgyal chen po'i thugs dam bskang / / yum mchog tsA muN+Di yi thugs dam bskang / / srog bdag gshin rje brgyad kyi thugs dam bskang / / dbugs len ma mo brgyad kyi thugs dam bskang / / sgrol byed las mkhan rnams kyi thugs dam bskang / / las gshin pho mo rnams kyi thugs dam bskang / / bka' sdod 'khor dang bcas pa'i thugs dam bskang / / rnal 'byor nyams chags ma lus dag pa dang / / gnod byed gdug pa'i tshogs rnams tshar gcod mdzod / / gdong lnga ba sogs gcan gzan tshogs rnams dang / / mkha' lding la sogs 'dab bzang du ma dang / / khyu mchog la sogs ma he ra nag dang / / glang chen la sogs rkang 'gro sna tshogs dang / / zab chen la sogs dar zab sna tshogs dang 'phan gdugs la sogs mdzes rgyan sna tshogs dang / / mdor na khams gsum snod bcud kyis bsdus pa'i / / legs pa'i yon tan gang dang gang mchis pa / / mchod bya mchod byed mchod pa'i las rnams dang / / rang bzhin ma grub rten 'brel mi slu'i tshul / / snang stong gnyis su med pa'i mchod pa 'dis / / dam can chos rgyal chen po'i thugs dam bskang / / yum mchog tsA muN+Di yi thugs dam bskang / / srog bdag gshin rje brgyad kyi thugs dam bskang / dbugs len ma mo brgyad kyi thugs

dam bskang / / sgrol byed las mkhan rnams kyi thugs dam bskang / / las gshin pho mo rnams kyi thugs dam bskang / / bka' sdod 'khor dang bcas pa'i thugs dam bskang / / rnal 'byor nyams chags ma lus dag pa dang / / gnod byed gdug pa'i tshogs rnams tshar gcod mdzod / / ! bstod pa ni / hUM| 'di nas dpag tshad brgyad khri yi / / lho phyogs rim bdun sa 'og na / / gshin rje'i grong khyer chen po ste / / lcags mkhar lhun po lta bur brjid / / ro dang keng rus sa gzhi gang / / srin po'i g.yang gzhi mkha' la bres / / rgyu rlon lnga ldi 'thur du 'phyang / / mi mgo'i phreng ba'i do shal spel / / khrag dang zhag gi rba glong 'khrug / sha chen bsregs pa'i dud sprin 'khrigs / / gnam lcags mtshon cha thog ltar 'bab / / sod song rgyob rgyob 'brug sgra sgrog / gshin rje pho mo glog ltar 'khyug / sprul pa yang sprul ser chen 'bebs / / sha za sde brgyad bu yug @# / / 'tshubs / / las mkhan tshogs kyis bro chen rdung / / pho nya ma mo shugs glu len / / ma he dkar nag rlung ltar 'tshubs / / nad rims yongs kyi na bun 'thibs / / 'jigs shing bzod par dka' ba yi / / skye 'gro yongs kyi srog khang dar / / ro ras nag po'i ba dan rnams / / rlung gis bskyod pa'i rnam 'gyur gyis / / dgra la g.yab mo g.yab pa 'dra / / lcags mkhar sgro med bcu drug gis / / bskor ba'i 'jigs rung gnas mchog na| |hUM| chos dbyings spros dang bral ba'i klong dkyil nas / / chos can kun rdzob rnam par rol pa las / / chos kyi rgyal po'i sku ru bzhengs pa ni / / chos 'khor srog shing bstan pa'i srung ma khyod / / lha mchog gshin rje'i gshed kyi bka' sdod mchog / lhar bcas skye 'gro yongs kyi srog gi bdag / lha min g.yul du chas pa ji bzhin du / / lha khyod ma g.yel myur bar mthu rtsal bskyed / / ser skya'i ral pa nam mkha'i dbyings la 'phyar ser nag smi ma sma ra rab tu 'bar / / si ral ga la mi mgo'i do shal 'phyang / / ser zhing dmar ba'i nyi ma'i gdan la bzhugs / / dmar zlum spyan gsum gnod byed tshogs la bgrad / / dmar la 'khyug pa'i ljags ni rnam par 'dril / / dmar zhing rgyas pa'i ling+ga gyen la langs / / dmar nag 'khrugs pa'i me yi klong na bzhugs / / rab dkar thod bskam phreng bas dbu la brgyan / / rab 'jigs ma he'i zhal ni khro gnyer g.yo / / rab yangs shangs nas bskal pa'i rlung chen 'bud / / rab mchog bstan pa'i srung ma nag po che /

/ ma he'i gdan la brjid pa'i tshul du bzhugs / / ma rungs 'dul phyir char sbrin lta bur gnag / ma bskul par yang bla ma'i phrin las sgrub / / ma g.yel ma g.yel rgyal pa'i bstan pa srungs / / yab ti sogs gshin rje'i 'khor gyis bskor / / ya ma dU sogs ma mo'i 'khor gyis bskor / / ya las byung ba'i dbyug pa klad la 'phyar / / ya nga'i 'jigs ba sdang ba'i dgra la thongs / / r+wa gnyis rtse la dus mtha'i me chen 'bar / / snyan gnyis bskyod pas nyi zla sgrib par byed / / phyag gnyis dbus na dgra bgegs thal bar rlog / zhabs gnyis brdabs pas sa gzhi gting nas g.yo / / 'jigs byed dpa' bo chen po khyod nyid kyis / / 'jig rten gsum po 'jigs par byed 'gyur na / / 'jigs bcas gdug pa sgrag rmongs bskyed pa dang / / 'jigs shing rengs dang bskrad dang bsad par gyis / / ! bskul bya ba ni / hUM| rdo rje 'chang gis mtshan btags pa / / rdo rje dus nag ces su grags / / shAkya'i rgyal pos mtshan btags pa / / gshin rje chos kyi rgyal po ste / / gshin rje'i gshed pos mtshan btags ba| |gshin rje kA la rU pa khyod / / rnal 'byor bdag la dgra byung na / / g.yul ngo bzlog pa khyod la re / / bdag la lha med zer nas brnyas / / smod cing gnod pa du ma byed / / lha khyod mthu med zer nas smod / / bla ma @# / / rnams la skur pa 'debs / / sangs rgyas bstan la gnod par byed / / bstan 'dzin rnams la chad pas gcod / / rdo rje slob dpon snying nas smod / / rdo rje theg pa sun 'byin cing / / dge 'dun sde rnams dkrug cing 'joms / / sdom brtson yongs la brnyas par byed / / skye bo yongs la 'tshe bar byed / / rnal 'byor bdag la chad du btsugs / / srung ma khyod la do ru bsdos / / 'di 'dra'i las ngan sdig can 'di / / dam can 'khor dang bcas pa yis / / da lta nyid du bsgral bar gyis / / hUM| bcom ldan gshin rje'i gshed po'i bka' / / chos kyi rgyal po dgongs su gsol / / de ring drag po'i 'phrin las 'di / / khyod kyi las su 'os pa yin| |lha dang bcas pa'i 'jig rten na / / legs nyes chos bzhin spyod pa khyod / / gshin rje'i gshed kyi bka' 'khor na / / bka' nyan dam tshig bsrung ba khyod / / las dang rkyen gyis 'chi ba yi / / srog la dbang byed bdag po khyod / / de ring las 'di khyod la btad / / khyod kyi 'khor ni mi srun te / / tha mal sems can nyes med cing /

/ gzhan gyis bskul bar ma byas kyang / / glo bur 'phrad pa'ang 'dzin byed na / / nga yis gtad pa'i dgra bgegs 'di / / 'jam dpal gzhon nu'i bka' bzhin du / / dam tshig phyag rgya mig la bstan / / dam tshig snying po rna bar bsgrags / / rdo rje'i thi tshag snying la bzhag / dam rdzas mchod pa phul nas kyang / / dam tshig 'phrin las gnyer du btad / / las 'di sngon du bsgrub par bgyi / / khyod kyis las 'di ma bsgrubs na / / dkon mchog gsum gyi bka' yanr bcag / gshin rje'i gshed kyi dam yang dral / / rang gi tha tshig rang gis bslus dam tshig grogs po bdag cag gi / re ba'i bsam pa gting nas bcad / / de bas las 'di sgrub par gyis / / hUM / khyod kyi 'khor gyi dkyil 'khor na / / ya ma dU ti zhes bya ba / / lag na lcags kyu nag po thogs / / gang zhig bzung bar 'dod pa de / / dbyugs pa tsam gyis 'dzin par byed / / khyod kyi de ring dgra bo zungs / / gzhan yang 'khor gyi dkyil 'khor na / / kA la pA sha zhes bya ba / / lag na zhags pa nag po thogs / / gang zhig bcing bar 'dod pa de| |btab pa tsam gyis 'ching bar byed / / khyod kyis de ring dgra bo chings / / gzhan yang 'khor gyi dkyil 'khor na / / ya ma daN+Di zhes bya ba / / lag na be con nag po thogs / / gang zhig bsad par 'dod pa de / / phyar ba tsam gyis 'chi bar byed / / khyod kyis de ring dgra bo gsod / / gzhan yang 'khor gyi dkyil 'khor na / / ya ma daM Sh+T+ri zhes bya ba / / za byed mche ba 'bar ba can / / gang zhig za bar 'dod pa de / / gtsigs pa tsam gyis za bar byed / / khyod kyi de ring dgra bo zo / / gzhan yang 'khor gyi dkyil 'khor na / / kA la ra tri zhes bya dang / / gsod pa mo dang nag mo dang / / nam gru sha ka li la sogs / / bud med tshogs kyis bskor ba ni / / la la las kyi me long @# / / can / / la la nad kyi rkyal pa can / / la la mtshon gyi dru gu can / / la la bdud kyi khram shing can / / la la sho rde dkar nag can / / la la lcags kyi dre'u rta zhon / / la la bung bu ga pa zhon / / la la rlung nag 'tshubs ma zhon / / la la chu bya nag mo zhon / / la la nam gyi gung la rgyug / la la chu bo'i gzhung la rgyug / la la nyi

ma'i zer la rgyug / la la mun pa'i smag la rgyug / kun kyang gzhan srog 'phrog par byed / / bdag la sdang pa'i dgra bo 'di / / da lta nyid du tshar gcod mdzod / / gzhan yang 'khor gyi dkyil 'khor na / / yab ti dang phya sangs dang / / rmig pa ral pa tshar dgu sogs / / la la rgyal po'i tshul du gnas la la blon po'i tshul du gnas / / la la pho nya'i tshul du gnas / / kha cig dag ni sde dpon tshul / / lag na be con 'khor lo dang / / gsal shing mdung sogs mtshon cha thogs / / so so'i sde dpon mngags pa dang / / pho nya phyag brnyan bcas pa la / / 'phrin las gnyer du gtad pa ni / / dam nyams las ngan sdig can 'di / / lo dang zla bar ma bzhag par / / chos kyi rgyal po'i zhal du stobs / / rgyab rten lha dang myur du phrol / / gang du gnas par mi nus shing / / bsdigs shing spa rnams bkod pa dang / / mtshon cha'i tshogs rnams gzugs par gyis / / ma he'i tshogs kyis brdzi bar gyis / / gshin rje'i chogs rnams srog la rol / / ma mo'i tshogs rnams dbugs la rol / / ri bo'i tshogs kyis mnan par gyis / / gcan gzan tshogs kyis 'brang par gyis / / sha za'i tshogs rnams rol par gyis / / bya nag mang pos 'khyer bar gyis / / ya ba ti dang phya sangs dang / / gshin rje 'bebs ma la sogs kyis / / dgra bo'i klad pa 'khor du chug / tel pa chos kyi rgyal po dang / / gshin rje lcags kyu zhags pa mas / / dam nyams khrag tu skyug tu chug / gshin rje glang mgo rmig pa dang / / pho nya mo dang mche ba mas / / dgra bo smyo zhing 'bog tu chug / ral pa tshar dgu mig dmar dang / / gshin rje mtshan mo dus mtshan mas / / dgra bo gsod pa'i las mdzod cig / de ltar tshar bcad las byas pas / / dam nyams bsgral ba'i 'khor gsum kun / / sprul pa lta bu'i tshul du byas / / rnam par mi rtog dang nyid du / / mchog tu gnas pa nyid gyur cig / phyi nang 'gal rkyen tshogs rnams zhi ba dang / dam chos 'dzin pa'i bshad sgrub rgyas pa dang / / skye 'gro ma lus dbang du bsdu ba la / / chos kyi rgyal pos rtag tu grogs byed shog / ces chos rgyal yab yum gyi bskang gso bstod bskul dang bcas pa 'di / paN chen dge 'dun grub kyis mdzad pa'o / / bkra shis / / ! / / 'jam dpal gshin rje'i gshed kyi bka' sdod dam can chos kyi rgyal po la bstod pa bdud dpung

'joms pa zhes bya ba / @# / / dpal rdo rje 'jigs byed kyi lha tshogs la phyag 'tshal lo / / hUM kA la rU pa rab brjid drag po'i sku / / kha nas khrag 'dzag mi mgo'i 'phreng ba yi / / ga sha rab 'phyang mi bzad bdud dpung gi / nga rgyal dregs pa 'joms pa khyod la bstod / / ca co che ldan rdo rje'i glu dbyangs dang / / cha shas yongs su rdzogs pa'i gtor ma ni / / ja chang phud dang dgra bgegs bsgral ba'i sha / / nya sha khrag zhag rgya mtshos brgyan pa 'bul ta thA ga ta'i bstan la gnod byed pa'i / / tha chad dgra bgegs rdul du rlog pa dang / / da nas bzungs te rnal 'byor bdag cag gi / na rga 'chi ba'i 'jigs pa 'joms la bstod / / pa wa sangs ltar rab dkar mche ba gtsigs / / pha rol 'joms pa'i spyan rtsa glog ltar 'khyug / ba spu dus mtha'i me chen 'bar ba yis / / ma lus bgegs dpung sreg pa khyod la bstod / / tsA muN+Di sogs ma mo kun gyi bdag / tsha zer rab tu rgyas pa'i gzi brjid can / / dza zhes 'phrin las sgrub la bos pa'i tshe / / w+wa skyes lta bu'i bgegs 'joms khyod la bstod / / zhwa ltar 'byung po kun gyis spyi bos bsten / / za byed ma he khros pa'i zhal gdangs shing / / 'a 'ur dar dir sgrogs pas sa chen g.yo / / ya las skyes pa'i thod dbyug 'dzin la bstod / / r+wa dang rmig pa rno ba'i ma he dang / / la la rlung nag tshub ma zhon pa'i 'khor / / sha ka li dang gshin rje 'bebs ma sogs / / sa gsum 'byung po'i 'khor gyis skor la bstod / / ha ha drag tu bzhad pa'i dpal yon can / / ar+g+haM la sogs mchod pa bzhes nas kyang / / dpal ldan gshin rje'i gshed kyi spyan snga ru / / zhal bzhes dam bca' g.yel ba med par mdzod / / 'jam dpal gshin rje'i gshed kyi bka' sdod dam can chos kyi rgyal po la bstod pa 'di ni / gshin rje'i gshed kyi rnal 'byor pa dge 'dun grub pa dpal bzang pas dpal ri khud kyi gtsug lag khang du sbyar ba'o / / ! tsA mu N+Ti la bstod pa / ! 'jam dpal gshin rje'i gshed la phyag 'tshal lo / / b+h+yauH ma skyes mi 'gag chos dbyings klong yangs nas / / ma hA kA li srin mo khros pa'i sku / / ma rungs 'dul phyir rtse gsum thod khrag 'dzin / / ma mo chen mo tsA mu N+Di la bstod / / ma he'i gdong can gshin rje'i dga' ma khyod / / ma rungs dgra la kha gdangs mche ba gtsigs / / ma lus bdud kyi srog gcod shan pa mo / /

ma yengs bstan pa'i srung ma khyod la bstod / / ma gcig 'dod pa'i khams la dbang bsgyur ma / / ma mo mkha' 'gro sde brgyad 'khor dang bcas / / ma mo'i dal yams la sogs cho 'phrul gyis / / ma dul gdul dka' 'joms pa khyod la bstod / / ma bcos rang bzhin dag pa'i chos kyi dbyings / / ma rtogs bdud kyi cho 'phrul ci byung yang / / ma chen khyod kyi ming nas bos pa'i che / / ma g.yel myur du byon la mthu rtsal bskyed / / ma rungs rnams la rab tu khros gyur kyang / / @# / / ma ltar brtse bas bstan 'dzin skyong ba khyod / / ma sring chung ma bran mo'i tshul bzungs nas / / ma bskul bar yang mthun pa'i las kun sgrubs / / mnor lam mchog ston pa'i bla ma dang / / ma rig mun sel rgyal ba'i bstan pa la / / ma dad log par sgrub pa'i gdon dang bgegs / / ma bsgral ba rnams chos kyi dbyings su sgrol / / ma lus 'gro ba'i du rnal 'byor ngas / / mny+dzu g+ho Sha'i go 'phang dam pa de / / ma thob de srid nag mo chen mo khyod / / ma g.yel ma g.yel 'phrin las tshul bzhin sgrubs / / ma mo chen mo bstod cing bskul bas bdag / ma rig 'khrul pas bskyed pa'i 'khor ba 'di / / ma stongs bar du bstan pa 'dzin pa la / / ma hA kA lis rtag tu grogs byed shog / ma mo chen mo tsA muN+Di la bstod pa 'di ni / dge slong rdo rje 'dzin pa dge 'dun grub pa dpal bzang pos dpal byang chub chen po'i dben gnas theg chen pho brang du sbyar ba'o / / ! / / dam can chos rgyal gyi zlog pa rgyas pa / ! hUM| khyod kyi 'khor gyi dkyil 'khor na / / dgra bo'i srog len gshin rje ni / / ya ba ti dang phya sangs dang / / rmig pa ral pa tshar dgu can / / mig dmar tel pa glang mgo can / / 'jigs pa'i mtshon cha thogs pa dang / / nad bdag ma mo pho nya mo / / zhags pa ma dang dam sri ma / / gshin rje sreg ma dus mtshan ma / / bsod ma nag mo nam gu sogs / / mchod sbyin gtor ma 'di bzhes la / / bcol ba'i 'phrin las sgrub pa dang / / dam nyams sdig can dgra bgegs 'dis / / bla ma dam pa'i sku la bsngos / / dkon mchog gsum gyi dbu 'phang smad / / sangs rgyas bstan pa'i spyi dgra byas / / 'phags pa'i dge 'dun so sor phye / / skye bo yongs la gnod cing 'tshe / / srung ma khyod la sngo phod btsugs / / rnal 'byor bdag la gnod byas pas / / las kyi gshin

rje dgra la b+h+yoH / lcags kya rnon pos dgra bgegs khug / bdud kyi zhags pas dgra bgegs chings / / bdud kyi be con dgra la phyor / / mche ba 'bar bas dgra la phug / nad kyi rkyal pa dgra la byo / / mtshon gyi dru gu dgra la rkyongs / / bdud kyi khram shing dgra la thobs / / sho rde nag po dgra la khye / / rims nad drag po dgra la thongs / / glo bur ye 'brog dgra la thongs / / dus kyi 'khrug pa dgra la thongs / / thog dang ser pa dgra la thongs ltas ngan thams cad dgra la thongs / / dmu gab dgra dang bgegs la thongs / / dal yams dgra dang bgegs la thongs / / gzer thabs dgra dang bgegs la thongs / / mdze nad dgra dang bgegs la thongs / / smyo 'bog dgra dang bgegs la thongs / / bdud kyi dmag tshogs dgra la drongs / / las kyi gshin rjes dmag sna drongs / / dmag dpung bskyed la ru mtshon phyor / / bstan dgra dam nyams sdig can rnams / / las kyi @# / / rlung gis rgyab nas phul / / 'jigs pa'i mun pas mdun nas bsus / / lo dang zla bar ma bzhag par / / kha nas khrag don skyug tu chug / khong pa'i nang nas snying phyugs shig / dpral ba'i dbyings nas mig phyungs shig / ltag pa'i phyogs nas bdud chod cig / gnam gyi 'ju thag chod la shog / sa yi rten phur thon la shog / dgra rgyud rtsad nas chod la shog / dgra bo'i bla srog khug la shog / dgra bo'i sha zo zhag la 'thungs / / dgra bo'i yul khams brlag par gyis / / bka' dang dam las ma 'da' bar / / bcol ba'i 'phrin las myur du sgrubs / / dam can yab yum 'khor bcas la / / mchod cing gtor ma 'di phul bas / / rnal 'byor bdag cag 'khor bcas kyi / / rkyen ngan par chad thams cad zlog / gzhan gyi bsam ngan sbyor rtsub zlog / dri za'i gdon rnams gtor mas zlog / pho phywa ngan pa gtor mas zlog / mu stegs ngan sngags gtor mas zlog / ban bon phur kha gtor mas bzlog / chos kyi chos zor gtor mas zlog / bon gyi bon zor gtor mas zlog / sngags pa'i sngags zor gtor mas zlog / zhang zhung btso zor gtor mas zlog / rgyal po'i thog brdzis gtor mas zlog / ma mo'i dal yams gtor mas zlog / 'byung po'i rims nad gtor mas zlog / yas kyi bdud g.yos gtor mas zlog / mas kyi sri langs gtor mas zlog / 'phangs kyi snying ngan gtor mas zlog / nye ba'i byol kha gtor mas zlog / pha tshan rgya 'dre gtor mas zlog / ma bu'i byur 'dre gtor mas zlog / byis pa'i chung sri

gtor mas zlog / tshe zor nyungs zor 'phen pa zlog / 'byung po'i thod zor 'phen pa zlog / gshin rje'i 'khor lo skor ba zlog / bdud kyi khram kha ston pa zlog / ma mo'i khrag zor 'phen pa zlog / klu yis byad du bcug pa zlog / the rang tshe la rku ba zlog / mu stegs bar chad byed pa zlog / rmi ltas mtshan ltas ngan pa zlog / lo skeg zla skeg zhag skeg zlog / 'chi ltas bdung chags yod pa zlog / bdud kyi shed bzhi yod pa zlog / drag po'i pho nya 'gyed pa zlog / pho bdud mo bdud spyi bdud zlog / skyes pa'i mda' zor 'phen pa zlog / bud med dmod zor 'phen pa zlog / ltas ngan brgyad cu rtsa bzhi zlog cho 'phrul ngan pa thams cad zlog / ye 'brog sum rgya drug cu zlog / nad rims bzhi brgya rtsa bzhi zlog / cho 'phrul ngan pa thams cad zlog / mdor na bdag cag 'khor bcas kyi / / rkyen dang bar chad gtor mas zlog / mthun rkyen chos bzhin 'grub pa dang / / bstan pa dar zhing rgyas par mdzod / ces dam can chos kyi rgyal po yab yum 'khor dang bcas pa la bstod pa bskul zlog dang bcas pa 'di ni / gshin rje'i gshed kyi rnal 'byor pa dge 'dun grub pa dpal bzang pos bkra shis lhun por legs par sbyar ba'o / / ! / / dam can gsang sgrub dmar po'i bstod pa / ! hUM| chos nyid ngang las mdun gyi nam mkha' ru / @# / / sna tshogs chu skyes nam mkha'i nor bu dang / / ma he dmar po 'gyings pa'i gdan steng du / / yaM gyis mtshan pa'i yid bzhin nor bu las / / 'od 'phros sems can kun gyi dbul phongs gsal / / tshur 'dus de nyid yongs su gyur pa las / / rab brjid padma rA ga'i ri bo la / / nyi ma bye ba'i 'od kyis byugs 'dra ba'i / / chos rgyal sku mdog dmar po brjid pa'i sku / / ma he'i gdong can zhal gcig phyag gnyis kyis / / dgos 'dod mchog stsol yid bzhin nor bu dang / / 'chi med bdud rtsis gang ba'i thod pa 'dzin / / mche ba rab dkar spyan gsum dmar la zlum / / skra ser rdo rje nag pos spyi bor brgyan / / 'jigs rung thod skam lnga yi dbu rgyan dang / / khrag 'dzag brgya phreng 'phreng ba'i ga shal can / / rin chen rgyan dang rus pa'i rgyan gyis spras / / thugs kar yaM gyis mtshan pa'i nor bu las / / lcags kyu lcags sgrog zhags pa lta bu yi / / 'od zer dmar po phyogs bcur 'phros pa las / / 'jig rten kun gyi phun tshogs longs spyod rnams / / thogs pa med pa'i tshul gyis bkug nas kyang / / rlabs chen

zad pa med pa'i longs spyod kyis / / sgrub pa po yi bsam pa tshim mdzad cing / / phongs pa'i sdug bsngal mtha' dag zhi ba dang / / snyan pa'i grags pas phyogs bcur khyab pa dang / / ma lus dbang du sdud pa'i las mdzad pa'i / / dam can chos kyi rgyal po khyod la 'dud / / rje btsun 'jam pa'i dbyangs kyi spyan snga ru / / ji ltar khyod kyis zhal bzhes dam bcas bzhin / / chos bzhin sgrub par byed pa'i gang zag la / / longs spyod thams cad ngang gis 'du bar mdzod / / bdag kyang deng nas tshe rabs thams cad du / / dpal mgon dam can khyod dang mi 'bral zhing / / phyi nang 'gal rkyen kun gyis g.yo med par / / mthun rkyen thams cad chos bzhin 'grub par mdzod / / dge ba 'di yis bdag gzhan 'gro ba kun / / rje btsun 'jam pa'i dbyangs kyi zhabs kyi rdul / / 'bral med spyi bos nod pa'i bka' drin gyis / / rgyal ba'i chos tshul ma lus 'dzin par shog / ces chos rgyal gsang sgrub la bstod cing gsol ba 'debs pa 'di ni / gshin rje'i gshed kyi rnal 'byor pa dge 'dun grub pa dpal bzang pos sbyar ba'o / / ! / / dmag zor lha mo'i gtor chog mdor bsdus / ! bla ma dang dpal gshin rje'i gshed la phyag 'tshal lo / / 'dir dpal ldan re ma ti la mchod gtor 'bul bar 'dod pa'i dam tshig dang ldan pa'i sgrub pa pos ras bris la sogs pa'i rten gyi drung mdun du / nal bu'i thod par 'bru sna tshogs dang sbyar ba'i gtor ma sha khrag gis brgyan pa bshams / / bdud rtsi dang / r+k+ta dang / g.yab dar la sogs pa'i dam rdzas tshang bar byas la / gtor ma bdud rtsi lngas sbags / chu tshang gis sbyangs te / yi dam gyi lha'i nga rgyal brtan pos las thams cad pa'i sngags kyis bsangs / lag pa @# / / g.yon pa bstan te / oM zhes brjod pas gtor ma la dmigs te stong par bsam / lag pa g.yas pa bstan te / AH zhes brjod pas / stong pa'i ngang las thod pa dkar po yangs shing rgya che bar bsam / lag pa gnyis ka bstan te / hUM zhes brjod pas dgra bgegs kyi sha khrag las grub pa'i gtor ma ri rab dang rgya mtsho tsam bsam / bya khyung gi phyag rgya bstan te / ho zhes brjod pas 'dod dgu 'byung pa'i ye shes kyi bdud rtsir bsam mo / / de nas mdun na rten yod na bsangs / med na skad cig gis rang gi mdun du / stong pa'i ngang las rlung nag 'tshub ma'i gur nang / me ri rab tu 'bar ba'i khrod / khrag zhag 'khrug pa'i klong dkyil du / b+h+yauH r+k+mo b+h+yauH r+k+mo b+h+yauH b+h+yauH k+mo thun

b+h+yauH kha la rka chen mo / r+k+mo a bya ta bya thun b+h+yauH ru lu ru lu hUM b+h+yauH hUM zhes brjod pa dang / k+Sha yig yongs su gyur pa las / dpal ldan lha mo re ma ti dre rta la zhon pa sku mdog mthing nag zhal gcig phyag gnyis / zhal mche ba gtsigs pa / dmar la zlum pa'i spyan gsum sdang mig tu bgrad cing / smin ma'i dbus su khro gnyer rab tu g.yo ba dang bcas pa / dbu skra kham pa gyen du g.yengs pa la / me stag dang me lce du ma 'phro ba / phyag g.yas rdo rjes mtshan p-I ts+n+dan ni gya be con nam mkha' la 'phyar ba / g.yon pa nal thor nyungs kar dang / khrag gis gang ba thugs kar 'dzin pa mi mgo bskam po lnga yis dbu brgyan cing / rgyu rlon la brgyus pa'i mi mgo khrag 'dzag pa lnga bcu'i do shal byas pa / zhing chen gyi g.yang gzhi dang / re ldes stod g.yogs shing / stag gi pags pa'i sham thabs can / dar nag gi gos kyis lhab lhub tu g.yogs shing / skul khrag gi thig le dang / zhag gi sor ris dang / thal chen gyi tshom bu sogs kyis brgyan cing / rma bya'i gdugs 'og tu chud pa / sga'i snga ru la nad kyi rkyal pa dang / phyi sha la mtshon gyi dru gu btags pa / bdud kyi khram shing rked la gzer ba / byang dmar dang sho rde snga sha la 'phyang ba / 'khor bdud phrug gi tshogs / yungs khrag dang mtshon cha sna tshogs 'dzin pa / mig rtsa dmar zhing rab tu rngams pa'i cha lugs can dpag tu med pas bskor bar bsam / de lta bu'i dam tshig pa bskyed pa'i thugs kar k+Sha yig mthing nag bsgom zhing / de dang rang gi thugs ka'i hUM las 'od 'phros pas| byang shar mu le'i ding nas dpal ldan lha mo 'khor bcas spyan drangs par bsam zhing / tshil chen dang / gu gul dang / cong zhi rnams bsregs pa'i bdug spos yod na bsreg / g.yab dar dang ma mo spyi'i dam rgya| mgo thod kyi phyag rgya bcas la mdzub mo gnyis g.yab cing / b+h+yauH chos 'khor yongs kyi srung ma re ma ti / / sngon tshe rgyal ba'i spyan sngar dam bcas bzhin / / bstan pa srung dang sgrub la phan gdags phyir / / @# / / byang shar mtshams nas spyan 'dren gshegs su gsol / / r+k+mo sogs kyi rjes la / T+k+ki dzaH hUM / zhes pa lan gsum gyis spyan drangs nas / mdun gyi dam tshig pa la bstims / b+h+yauH nag mo gdug can dregs pa can / / kun tu khyab pa'i gzugs ston ma / / nag mo'i gtso mo dre rta chibs / / 'dir byon dre rta'i gdan la bzhugs / / r+k+mo zhes sogs kyi rjes la / dzaH hUM

baM hoH zhes brjod pas bzhugs su gsol / de nas rang yi dam gyi nga rgyal gyis / b+h+yauH za byed nag mo mche ba can / / rgod byed ha ha nag mo khyod / / gsod la dga' bar byed pa mo / / bdag ni brda yi phyag bgyid do / / r+k+mo sogs kyi rjes la / a ti su ho zhes brjod cing / thal mo sbyar la lha mo la 'dud pa'i tshul gyis phyag byas la / lha mos bdag la phyag gus pas 'tshal bar bsams la / pra tIts+tsha ho / zhes brjod / de nas gtso 'khor thams cad kyi mig gnyis su k+ShiM dkar po / rna ba gnyis su dzriM sngon po / snar khaM ser po / lce la raM dkar po / dpral bar kaM ljang khu / lte bar saM dkar po / spyi bor oM dkar po / mgrin par AH dmar po / thugs kar hUM sngon po bkod de / de dag byang chub sems pa sa'i snying po la sogs pa drug dang / sku gsung thugs rdo rje'i ngo bor bsams te byin gyis brlabs / yang rang gi thugs ka'i hUM las 'od zer 'phros pas dbang gi lha rigs lnga spyan drangs nas dbang bskur bar bsam zhing / oM badzra a b+hi Shiny+tsa hUM zhes brjod cing dbang bskur bas / lus thams cad gang / dri ma thams cad dag / chu lhag pa yar lung pa las spyi bor gshin rje'i gshed kyis dbu brgyan par gyur / de nas bdud rtsi gtor zhing / phra mo spom po las byung ba'i / / bdud rtsis bran pa'i dza gad 'di / / dmag zor lha mo la 'bul gyis / / bstan pa bsrung phyir bzhes su gsol / / r+k+mo zhes sogs kyi rjes la / mahA p+ny+tsa a mr-i ta kha kha khA hi khA hi / yang r+k+ta dbul zhing / chu dang ma 'dres dwangs ma'i khrag / dwangs ma yi ni khrag chen po / / dmag zor lha mo la 'bul gyis / / bstan pa bsrung phyir bzhes su gsol r+k+mo sogs kyi rjes su / ma hA r+k+ta kha kha khA hi khA hi zhes brjod / de nas 'khu ldog mi yong ba'i phyir byang sems dkar dmar rang dang lha mo gnyis ka'i lce la bzhag par bsam zhing / dngos kyi nang mchod 'thor zhing rang gi myang ba ni dam tshig sre ba'o / / de nas lha mo 'khor bcas kyi zhal nas 'od kyi sbu gu byung nas gtor ma la zug par bsam zhing / rdo rje thal mo gyen du phye la / sha khrag la sogs bdud rtsi lnga dang bcas / / 'bru sna lnga dang sbyar ba'i gtor ma 'di / / dpal ldan dmag zor lha mo la 'bul gyis / / rgyal ba'i bstan pa bsrung phyir bzhes su gsol / / r+k+mo sogs kyi rjes la ma hA ba liM ta kha kha

khA hi khA hi / gsum @# / / mam lnga'am bdun gyis 'bul / de nas nang mchod gtor zhing / dpal ldan lha mo 'khor dang bcas pa khyed kyis mchod sbyin gyi gtor ma rgya chen po 'di bzhes la / sangs rgyas kyi bstan pa srungs / dkon mchog gi dbu 'phang bstod / dge 'dun gyi bde skyongs / bstan pa spyi la gnod pa / sems can yongs la 'tshe ba / sgos rnal 'byor pa bdag gi dam pa'i chos sgrub pa la bar du gcod pa'i gdon bgegs log par 'dren pa thams cad tshar chod cig / zhi ba dang / bdag cag 'khor dang bcas pa'i tshe dang / bsod nams dang / longs spyod dang / dbang thang la sogs pa thams cad rgyas pa dang / 'gro ba thams cad dbang du 'dus shing / chos las skyes pa'i bu dang tsha bo la sogs pa thams cad rgyas pa'i 'phrin las mdzod / ces pas bka' bsgos / 'dod pa'i don la gsol ba btab cing 'phrin las bcol / de nas bzlas pa bya bar 'dod na / rang gi snying kha'i sa bon las 'od zer dkar po sngags kyi rang bzhin can 'phros te / lha mo'i thugs kar thims pas / lha mo mnyes pa'i mchod pa phul / slar 'dus te bdag la thims pas / gang 'dod pa'i dngos grub byin par bsams pa tsam gyi dmigs pa byas la / b+h+yauH rak+mo la sogs pa'i rtsa sngags ci 'grub bzlas / 'di la bod rbad bsad gsum ga chang bar bzhed do / / de nas bstod pa bya ba ni| rnga brdung ba'am dril bu gsil zhing bstod pa rgyas bsdus ci rigs pas bstod / nongs pa bzod par gsol zhing / mdun gyi lha mo'i rten yod na brtan par bzhugs pa'am / med na rang bzhin gyi gnas su gshegs su gsol| mtshan mo yin na gtor ma la dpal 'bar btsugs nas gtsang sar gtong / dge ba'i rtsa ba bsngo ba sogs cho ga spyi dang mthun par bya'o / / de lta bu'i tshul gyis mchod gtor dang bzlas pa la brtson par byas na / gnas skabs su bar chad zhi zhing mthar thug byang chub sgrub pa'i grogs su 'gyur ro / / 'di ni / re ma ti'i mchod gtor gyi man ngag bla ma gong ma'i tho yin la brten nas bris pa yin pas yin ches pa'i gnas su bya'o / / -ithi / / / / ! dmag zor lha mo'i bstod pa / ! bstod pa bsdus pa ni / dpal gyi gzugs la 'dod khams gtso mo khyod / / dre rta zhon nas dpag tshad lnga brgyar rgyug / be con nal thod dam pa'i rang rtags 'dzin / / re lde'i stod g.yogs sbal gyi gsham bu can / / lte bar nyi ma gtsug na zla rgyas ma / / khrag nad bdag mo dbyings phyug dpal 'bar ma / / lha mo re

ma til bstod par bgyi / / rnal 'byor bcol ba'i 'phrin las sgrub par mdzod / / sha chen tshogs ni ri ltar spungs / / rak+ta'i tshogs ni mtsho ltar 'khyil / / tshogs kyi longs spyod 'di bzhes la / / dam tshig nyams pa'i dgra bo la / bdud kyi dmag chog dgra la drongs / / dmag dpon rgyal mos dmag sna drongs / / ma yi nang @# / / nas ma gcig dang / / srid gi nang nas srid gcig dang / / bdud kyi yum la gshin rje'i lcam / / bcol ba'i 'phrin las 'grub par mdzod / / b+h+yauH rak+mo sogs nas che ge mo mA ra ya phaT / ces pa'o / / 'di yang rje nyid kyis snga mo'i dus su theg chen pho brang du sbyar pa'o / / / b+h+yoH sku gsum lhun grub thugs rje mthar phyin kyang / / srid gsum gdug pa 'dul phyir khros pa'i sku / / dus gsum rgyal pa'i bstan srungs chen mo la / / sgo gsum gus pa'i sgo nas phyag 'tshal lo / zhes dpal ldan lha mo dmag zor rgyal mo'i bstod pa 'di yang rje nyid kyis mdzad pa'o / / ! / / dam can chos rgyal dpal ldan lha mo beg tse lcam srid la bkra shis lhun po'i mi nor dge 'dun dang bcas pa gnyer du gtad pa'i bka' bsgo / ! oM phyogs bcu dus gsum du bzhugs pa'i bla ma yi dam / sangs rgyas byang sems dpa' bo rnal 'byor ma / dpal mgon dam pa chos skyod pa'i srung ma rnams kyi byin rlabs dang / thugs rje dang / rdzu 'phrul dang / nus mthu bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i stobs dang / bdag dge 'dun grub ba dpal bzang pos dus gsum du bsags pa'i dge ba'i rtsa ba rnams kyi mthu la brten nas / bdag rtag tu tshe rabs dran cing / gzhon nu la rab tu byung zhing tshul khrims rnam par dag pa srung pa dang / sangs rgyas kyi bstan pa dang / sems can la phan pa rgya chen po gong nas gong du bsgrubs te / sangs rgyas kyi go 'phang rin po che myur du thob par gyur cig / sangs rgyas nas sems can gyi khams dang / bsam pa dang / bag la nyal ji lta ba bzhin du thugs su chud nas skal ba dang 'tsham par chos bstan pas thams cad sangs rgyas kyis la 'god par gyur cig / tshe 'dir yang dam pa'i chos kyi bshad sgrub rgyas par byed pa'i ngang nas bde bar gshegs pa'i sku gsung thugs kyi rten khyad par can dus bzheng pa dang / dkon mchog gi drung du mchod rdzas phun sum tshogs pa dang / dge 'dun gyi bsnyen bkur sogs sgrub pa la bar chad med cing / mthun rkyen rnams ji ltar bsams pa bzhin du 'grub par gyur cig / khyad par du ye shes kyi mkha' 'gro ma dmag

zor rgyal mo re ma ti 'khor dang bcas pa dang / gnod sbyin beg tse lcam dral 'khor dang bcas pa dang / dam can chos kyi rgyal po yab yum 'khor dang bcas pa la / bkra shis lhun po'i mi nor dge 'dun dang bcas pa gnyer gtad zhus pa yin pas / nyin gsum gyi byar ma g.yel / / mtshan gsum gyi mel tshe ma g.yel bar sangs rgyas kyi bstan pa ji srid gnas kyi bar du bkra shis lhun por dam pa'i chos kyi bshad sgrub dar zhing rgyas pa dang / dge 'dun rnams thugs mthun pa dang / dpal 'byor rgyal par mdzod / / bkra shis lhun por ma byin par len pa rnams chad pas gcod pa dang / bkra shis lhun po ba la gnod cing 'tshe bar byed pa'i 'byung po @# / / mi dang mi ma yin pa rnams kyi bsam pa ngan pa dang sbyor ba rtsub pa thams cad nye bar zhi nas bsam sbyor phun sum tshogs par mdzad du gsol / zhes pa 'di yang dmag zor rgyal mo'i bris sku chen mo bzhengs pa'i dus su mdzad pa'o / / ! / / dpal mgon chen po gri gug can la bstod pa / ! na mo ma hA kA la ye / chos kyi sku las 'gyur ba mi mnga' yang / / chos kyi rgyal po'i bstan pa bsrung ba'i phyir / / chos dbyings rnam par dag pa'i pho brang nas / / chos skyong 'khor bcas gnas 'dir gshegs su gsol / / dpal ldan rdo rje 'chang gi sbyan snga ru / / gtum chen khyod kyis ji ltar zhal bzhes bzhin / / zhi rgyas dbang dang drag po'i 'phrin las la / / spyan 'dren 'khor bcas gnas 'dir gshegs su gsol / / rgyal ba kun gyi mthu stobs gcig bsdus nas / / gdugs pa 'dul phyir khro bo'i skur bstan pa / / nag po chen po bka' sdod 'khor dang bcas brtse ba'i thugs kyis gnas 'dir gshegs su gsol / / chos nyid ngang las padma nyi ma'i steng / / 'jigs pa'i gzugs can zhal gcig phyag gnyis pa / / brkyangs bskums zhabs kyis gdug pa'i lus brdzis shing / 'jigs pa rnams kyang 'jigs par mdzad la 'dud / / bskal ba 'jig me ltar mi bzad pa'i / / ye shes me dpung 'bar ba'i klong dkyil na / / dam can rgya mtshos bskor ba'i dpa' bo khyod / / gar dgu'i nyams kyis rol par mdzad la 'dud / / phyag g.yas rno zhing 'bar ba'i gri gug gis / / dgra bgegs rtsad nas gcod pa'i 'phrin las mdzad / / gdug pa'i khrag gis gang ba'i thod pa ni / / g.yon pa'i phyag gis thugs kar 'dzin la bstod / / rab brjid in+d+ra nI la'i ri bo'i rtser / / dus mtha'i me chen gyen du mched pa bzhin / / dbu skra dmar ser gyen du brdzes pa yis

/ / steng gi bgegs tshogs sreg par mdzad la 'dud / / brkyangs bskums zhabs ni cung zad brdabs pas kyang / / rgya mtsho'i gos can mtha' dag 'dar byed cing / / 'og phyogs bgegs dpung rdul du brlag mdzad pa / / dpal ldan nag po chen po'i zhabs la 'dud / / nyi zla 'bar pa'i sngang mig bgegs la gzigs / / khro gnyer rab bsdus smin ma glog ltar 'khyug / ba spu dus mtha'i me ltar 'bar ba yis / / bar gyi bgegs tshogs sreg par mdzad la 'dud / / rab 'jigs zhal gyi char sprin nag po las / / ljags kyi glog stong kun nas rab 'khyug cing / / hUM dang phaT kyi 'brug sgra cher bsgrags nas / / bdud kyi gnas rnams phye mar 'thag la 'dud / / drag po'i dbugs phreng dus mtha'i rlung tshub bzhin / / dgra po'i sha khrag mche ba'i khyogs la len / / drag po'i rkan sde bas 'jigs pa'i gad rgyangs kyis / / bdud kyi srog rnams nges par 'gog la 'dud / / 'jigs rung thod skam lnga yi dbu rgyan dang / / khrag 'dzag mi mgo'i phreng ba'i do shal can / / rus pa'i rgyan dang rin chen @# / / phreng ba dang / / sprul gdug rgyan gyis brgyan pa khyod la 'dud / / g.yas na ri bo 'gyings 'dra brjid pa'i sku / / legs ldan nag po zhal gcig phyag gnyis kyis / / tsan+dan bed chen thod khrag 'dzin mdzad pa / / dam tshig can gyi dgra lha khyod la 'dud / / g.yon na dpal ldan 'dod khams dbang phyug ma / / bong bu gwa zhon mi sdug 'jigs pa'i gzugs / / zhal gcig phyag gnyis ral gri thod khrag 'dzin / / 'phrin las myur sgrub lha mo khyod la 'dud / / rlung ltar mgyogs pa'i dre'u sdon po chibs / / dam nyams dgra la shin tu khros pa'i sku / / sgrub pa po la kun nas brtse ba'i ma / / dpal ldan lha mo re ma ti la bstod / / sha dang khrag la rol pa'i khy-i sbyang dang / / mi nag bya nag mkha' 'gro'i dbang po sogs / / 'phrin las sgrub la thogs pa mi mnga' pa'i / / sprul pa'i pho nya rnams kyang bstod par bgyi / zhes dpal mgon chen po gri gug can la bstod pa 'di nyid shAkya'i dge slong dge 'dun grub pa dpal bzang pos thag lung ba'i zhogs dgon par sbyar ba'o / / ! / / dpal mgon zhal bzhi pa'i bstod pa / ! / na mo ma hA kA la ye / ka pA la dang 'bar pa'i gri gug 'dzin / / kha dog mi bzad mun nag byugs 'dra'i lus / / ga sha la sogs khro bo'i rgyan gyis spras / / nga ro drag pos sa gsum sgrag la 'dud / / ca co kun tu sgrog

pa'i ro langs dang / / cha lugs 'jigs rung srin po rgyu ba bzhin / / ja dang dgra bo'i khrag la rnam rol zhing / / nya ba'i zla ltar nag phyogs 'joms la 'dud / / ta thA ga ta'i sbyan sngar mngon sum du / / tha chad dgra bgegs sgrol bar khas blangs bzhin / / da ni bdag la 'tshe ba'i dgra bgegs dang / / na rga'i sdug bsngal kun tu sel la 'dud / / pa wa sangs sogs dpal mgon bdud cur bcas / / pha rol bdud kyi g.yul las rnam rgyal pa'i / / ba dan gnam du sgreng ba'i mthu bo che / / ma lus bstan pa'i dmag dpon khyod la 'dud / / tsa tu ra mu kha 'bar ba'i mche ba gtsigs / / tsha tsha 'phro ba'i dus mtha'i me dbung can / / dza lang rgyas pa'i seng ge khros pa bzhin / / wa ltar nag po'i rtsa lag 'joms la 'dud / / zha pa med pa'i rdzu 'phrul rkang pa yis / / za hor la sogs yul khams kun bgrod nas / / 'a 'ur dar dir 'brug gi sgra chen dang / / ya mtshan cho 'phrul mtha' yas ston la 'dud / / r+wa rtse shin tu rno ba'i g.yag nag sogs / / la lar rnam 'phrul du mas dgra bgegs kyi / / sha dang khrag la shin tu rngam pa'i phyir / / sa steng kun tu myul ba khyod la 'dud / / ha ha drag tu rgod pa'i dur khrod nas / / a la la dang hUM hUM phaT phaT sogs / / 'jigs rung gsung gi nga ro gcig pus kyang / / bdud kyi srog rnams nges par 'phrog la 'dud / / g.yung mo gtum mo srin mo sing+g+gi la / / gcer mo'i gzugs can g.yas bgri gug g.yon / @# / / khrag ldan thod pa gtso bo'i zhal du stob / / rgyal ba'i bstan srungs chen mo bzhi la bstod / / khyod la cung zad bstod pa'i dge pa 'dis / / tshe rabs kun tu lus dang grib ma bzhin / / khyed dang skad cig tsam yang mi 'bral zhing / / g.yel ba med par srung skye ba byed par shog / dus 'di nas bzungs byang chub snying po'i bar / / bdag gis gsung rab kun la bshad pa dang / / sgrub pa snying por byed pa'i mi mthun phyogs / cung zad tsam yang 'byung bar ma gyur cig / tshe ring nad med dbang phyug phun sum tshogs / / 'khor dang longs spyod snyan pa'i grags pa sogs / / bla med byang chub bsgrub pa'i mthun rkyen kun / / 'bad rtsol med par dang gis 'grub par shog / ces pa 'di nyid shAkya'i dge slong dge 'dun grub pa dpal bzang pos / bcom ldan 'das kyis bdud btul ba'i dus chen la byang chub chen po'i dpen gnas su sbyar pa'o /

'khor pa spyi dang bye brag gi nyes dmigs bsams pas 'khor ba mtha' dag sdug bsngal gyi rang bzhin du khod du chud na / de'i tshe sdug bsngal dang 'bral 'dod kyi blo skye la / sdug bsngal de rgyu gang las byung na zag bcas kyis las dge ma dge las byung / de dug gsum las byung / de'i nang nas 'dod chags zhe sdang gnyis gtso mi che la / gti mug gtso che / de yang nye skor na ngar 'dzin lhan skyes 'di yin pas / sdug bsngal spangs pa'i thar pa thob par 'dod pas ngar 'dzin lhan skyes 'di spang dgos / de spong ba la nga rang bzhin med par gtan la phab nas bsgom dgos / da rang bzhin med par gtan la 'bebs tshul ni / nga rang bzhin gyis grub na phung po re re pa nga yin nam phung po tshogs tsam nga yin nam de gnyis las logs na yod / phung po re re ba nga min te / blo lhan skyes 'di la phung po la dmigs nas 'di nga'i phung po yin snyam du zhen pa 'dug gi / phung po nga yin snyam pa dang / nga phung po yin snyam du zhen pa mi 'dug pa'i phyir / des na phung po re re ba nga min te / nga yi ba yin pas so / / phung po tshogs tsam nga min te / nga de phung po tshogs tsam la brten nas 'dogs pa'i phyir / de skad du yang mdo las / ji ltar yan lag tshogs tsam la / / brten nas shing rtar 'dogs pa ltar / / de bzhin phung po rnams brten nas / / kun rdzob sems can zhes bya'o / zhes dang / 'jug pa las / mdo las phung po brten nas yin gsungs pa / / de phyir phung po 'dus tsam bdag ma yin / zhes gsungs / phung po las logs na yang nga med de / phung po las logs na nga snang rung ma dmigs pa'i phyir / des na phung po re re ba nga min / phung po tshogs tsam nga min / phung po las logs na nga med pas / da rang bzhin gyis med snyam du bsgom par bya'o / / mnyam gzhag tu nga rang bzhin med par bsgoms pa'i rjes thob tu @# / / nga rang bzhin gyis grub par snang yang / rang bzhin gyis med pa rmi lam lta bu sgyu ma lta bur yang dang yang du bsam / yang rjes thob kyi gnas skabs su sems can rnams kyis nga rang bzhin gyis grub par bzungs nas 'khor ba'i sdug bsngal sna tshogs myong / sems can rnams cir yang mi 'ong ba min / thog ma med pa nas ma byas de yang / yang dang yang du byas / ma byas res kyis phan btags / gnod pa las bskyabs pa'i drin can sha stag yin pas / 'di rnams sdug bsngal dang

sdug bsngal gyi rgyu bdag 'dzin dang bral na / bral bar gyur cig / bral ba de bdag gis bya'o snyam du bya'o / / yang mnyam gzhag tu chos thams cad rang bzhin gyis med par bsgoms pa'i rjes thob tu / myu gu la sogs pa'i dngos po gang snang ba thams cad la 'di rnams bden par med de / rgyu rkyen las skyes pa'i phyir snyam du yang dang yang du goms par byas na gang snang kun stong par 'char bas rten 'brel stong pa'i don du 'char pa yin / 'o na chos thams cad rang bzhin gyis med na gtan nas med snyam na rang bzhin gyis med pa la bya byed thams cad rung ba'i tshul bsams pas stong pa rten 'byung gi don du 'char ba yin la / sngar bshad pa ltar mnyam rjes gnyis su goms par byas pas stong nyid la dmigs pa'i zhi gnas skyes pa na tshogs lam dang / stong nyid la dmigs pa'i lhag mthong skyes pa na sbyor lam dang / stong nyid mngon sum du gsar du rtogs pa na mthong lam dang / stong nyid mngon sum du rgyun ldan du mthong zin goms par byed pa na sgom lam dang / de la brten nas bdag 'dzin dang / des bskyed pa'i nyon mongs dang sdug bsngal spangs pa'i tshe thar pa thob pa yin no / / lhan cig skyes pa'i bde ba chen po dang / longs spyod rdzogs pa'i sku ngo bo dbyer med pa'i mi slob pa'i zung 'jug de thob bya mthar thug yin la / de la slob pa'i zung 'jug sngon du 'gro dgos te / mi slob pa'i zung 'jug de la rang gi rigs 'dra snga ma sngon du 'gro dgos pa'i phyir / slob pa'i zung 'jug la rim pa bzhi pa'i 'od gsal sngon du 'gro dgos te / rim pa bzhi pa'i 'od gsal dang de'i bzhon par gyur pa'i rlung las slob pa'i zung 'jug gi sku sgrub dgos pas so / / rim pa bzhi pa'i 'od gsal la rim pa gsum pa'i sgyu lus sngon du 'gro dgos te / rim pa gsum pa'i lus de ril 'dzin dang rjes gzhig gis 'od gsal du bcug nas dag par byas pa las rim pa bzhi pa'i 'od gsal sgrub dgos so / / rim pa gsum pa'i sgyu lus la / sems dben sngon du 'gro dgos te / sems dpen gyi rlung sems las rim pa gsum pa'i sgyu lus skyed dgos pas so / / sems dben la srog rtsol rdo rje bzlas pa sngon du 'gro dgos te / sna rtse gsum du thig le gsum gyi srog rtsol bsgoms pa'i stobs kyis / snying khar rlung sdud pa'i sdud rim khyad bar can @# / / las sems dben skyed dgos pas so / / srog rtsol la lus dben sngon du 'gro dgos te / snying khar rlung sdud pa'i sdud rim khyad par can byed pa la sngon du lus

gnad gzhan du rlung dbu mar tshud pa'i rgyu bde stong sgom pa dang / rjes thob tu gang snang bde ba'i rnam rol du 'char ba / rang bzhin yang lha sku'i rnam rol du 'char ba la bslab dgos / de'i rgyud ma smin pa smin byed du phra mo rtog pa'i rnal 'byor sngon du 'gro dgos / de'i yang sngon du rags pa dran pa gcig pa'i rnal 'byor sngon du 'gro dgos / rim gnyis sgom pa'i snod du rung ba la / dbang bskur ba'i dus su khas blangs pa'i dam tshig dang sdom pa tshul bzhin du bsrung dgos / de la rgyud sde nas bshad pa'i dbang bskur ba legs par thob dgos / de la thun mong ba'i lam sems can thams cad mar shes / drin dran / drin gzo ba / yid 'ong gi byams pa / sdug bsngal dang bral bar 'dod pa'i snying rje / lhag bsam / de la brten nas byang chub kyi mchog tu sems bskyed pa rnams sngon du 'gro dgos / de la 'khor ba spyi dang bye brag gi nyes dmigs legs par bsams nas / thar pa don gnyer gyi blo bskyed pa sngon du 'gro dgos / de la sdug bsngal gyi rgyu sdig pa spong / bde ba'i rgyu dge ba sgrub pa sngon du 'gro dgos / de la 'chi ba dran pa sngon du 'gro dgos / de la dal 'byor rnyed dka' bsam pa sngon du 'gro dgos zhes gsung ngo / / 'di dag dbus phyogs su 'gro dus rje rin po che'i gsung ji lta ba bzhin bkod pa lags / / / dngul chu'i bcud len gyi man ngag ! na mo gu ru / dngul chu rjen par za pa'i thabs na| rang mkha' 'gro ma dkar mo skra gyen du 'khyil ba / spyan gsum bgrad pa / sku la rus pa'i rgyan gyis brgyan pa bsgoms nas / / oM badzra tri tri dngul ngar gsang / mtshal ngar zhi / dngul dug nyal nyal swA hA / sngags 'di gsum brgya re bzlas nas dngul chu bzhi nam re nang re bzhin chang bzang po bre phyed yan gyis phul nas zos na / ting nge 'dzin 'phel / stobs che / lo brgya lon na yang so brje / skra dkar na ga por 'gro / lo bcu drug lon pa lta bu'i gzhon nur 'gyur / tshe nyi zla dang mnyam par 'gyur / rtsal seng ge dang mnyam / stobs glang po che dang mnyam / bteg ni ra rab kyang theg snyam pa'i nyams skye / mchog tu rma bya'i sgong dug / rgya gar gyi dbyig dug / rgya nag gi sbyar dug / dug rigs thams cad kyi gnyen por 'gro / gag lhog gzer gsum / gnyan dang / bzhi brgya rtsa bzhi'i nad rnams dang / khyad par sha lus rgyas par byad / mchog tu 'grogs pa'i grogs lags so / / 'di'i rgyud pa ni / ye shes mkha' 'gro

ma / kha che'i paN+Dita dz+nyA na sid+ha / ma hA ka ra dzi / bla ma rdo rje gdan pa / lo ts+tsha ba grags pa 'bum / nyi ma seng ge / khro lo / chos dpal bzang po / bya bral chos rje @# / / des grags pa 'byung gnas la'o / / ! / / chab shog / ! bstan pa rin po'i che'i sbyin bdag chen mo byang sems ma'i spyan sngar zhu ba / thugs dad pa chen po kun nas bslangs nas| dpal gsang ba 'dus pa'i sku / gser srang phyed gnang bas thugs la btags / sbyin pa dam pa 'di la brten nas sbyin pa'i bdag mo sku tshe thams cad du rin po che'i dbu rgyan / snyan rgyan / mgul rgyan / mu tig gi se mo do dang / rin po che'i do shal / phyag gdub / zhabs gdub dang rin po che'i ska rags la sogs pa lha dang mi'i rgyan khyad par du 'phags pa dang ldan par gyur cig / myur du mtshan dang dpe byad bzang po'i rgyan gyis spras pa'i sangs rgyas kyi sku blta bas chog mi shes pa thob par gyur cig / sbyin pa'i bdag mo yab yum gnyis kyang gnas skabs dal 'byor gyi mi lus thob nas myur du sangs rgyas par gyur cig / / ces pa'i smon lam btab cing rgyun du smon lam 'debs par zhu / ri mo gzigs pa'i rten mtshon ja sbyor gcig phul / drung lo chen po'i gsung bris rten dang bcas gnang ba 'phrod pas thugs la btags / mkhar la sogs chos ldan gyi mdzad pa rnams la thugs rtsol che dgos / bkra shis lhun po nas zhus / 'di yang snga mo'i dus su rje 'di nyid kyis mdzad pa'o / / ! / / 'phags pa dkon mchog brtsegs pa nas 'byung ba'i zhing sbyong ba'i smon lam ! phyogs bcu na bzhugs pa'i sangs rgyas dang byang chub sems dpa' thams cad bdag la sgongs su gsol / bdag gis 'di ltar bsgrubs pa'i dge ba'i rtsa ba 'dis mtshon nas / dus gsum du bsags pa'i dge ba'i rtsa ba rnams kyi mthu dang / nus pa la brten nas bdag sems can thams cad kyi don du mngon par rdzogs par sangs rgyas par gyur cig / bdag mngon par rdzogs par sangs rgyas pa'i sangs rgyas kyi zhing de / bcom ldan 'das 'od dpag med kyi zhing khams bde ba can lta bur gyur cig / bdag sangs rgyas pa'i zhing der ngan song gsum gyi ming yang med par gyur cig / zhing der skyes pa'i sems can rnams shi 'phos nas ngan song gsum dang lha ma yin gyi ris su nam yang mi skye bar gyur cig / zhing der skyes pa'i sems can thams cad lus gser gyi mdog lta bu phun sum tshogs pa thob par gyur cig / zhing der skyes pa'i sems can thams cad skad cig re re la sangs rgyas

kyi zhing bye ba khrag khrig brgya stong du 'gro ba'i rdzu 'phrul la dbang ba'i pha rol tu phyin pa thob par gyur cig / zhing der skyes pa'i sems can thams cad bskal pa bye ba khrag khrig brgya stong du mar tshe rabs dran pa thob par gyur cig / zhing der skyes pa'i sems can thams cad 'jig rten gyi khams bye ba khrag khrig mthong ba'i lha'i mig rnam par dag pa thob par gyur cig / zhing der skyes pa'i sems can thams cad sangs rgyas kyi zhing bye @# / / ba khrag khrig brgya stong du dam pa'i chos cig car nyan pa'i lha'i rna ba thob par gyur cig / zhing der skyes pa'i sems can thams cad phyogs bcu'i sems can rnams kyi sems kyi sbyod pa ji lta pa bzhi rig pa'i pha rol gyi sems shes pa thob par gyur cig / zhing der skyes pa'i sems can thams cad rang gi lus la yongs su 'dzin pa'i 'du shes skad cig tsam yang mi skye bar gyur cig / zhing der skyes pa'i sems can thams cad mi gnas pa'i mya ngan las 'das pa ma thob kyi bar du yang dag pa nyid du nges pa la gnas par gyur cig / zhing der skyes pa'i nyan thos kyi 'khor grangs med pa rnams kyang zag pa zad pa thob par rgyur cig zhing der bdag gis sangs rgyas kyi zhing bye ba khrag khrig brgya stong gi tshad dang ldan pa'i 'od phun sum tshogs pa thob par gyur cig / zhing der skyes pa'i sems can rnams smon lam gyi dbang ma gtogs pa tshe lo dpag tu med pa thub par gyur cig / zhing der mi dge pa bcu'i m-ing tsam yang med par gyur cig / phyogs bcu'i sangs rgyas rnams kyis bdag gi sangs rgyas kyi zhing de'i bstod pa dang bsngags pa dang grags pa brjod par gyur cig / de'i tshe bdag gi ming thos nas sems rab tu dad ba'i sems can de dag 'chi ba'i tshe bdag dge slong gi dge 'dun dang bcas pa mngon sum du mthong bar gyur cig / de'i tshe bdag gi ming thos nas sangs rgyas kyi zhing der skye bar smon pa'i sems can de dag sangs rgyas kyi zhing der skye bar gyur cig / zhing der skyes pa'i sems can thams cad skyes bu chen po'i mtshan sum cu rtsa gnyis dang ldan par gyur cig / zhing der skyes pa'i byang sems thams cad smon lam gyi dbang ma gtogs par skye ba gcig gis thogs pa sha stag tu gyur cig / zhing der skyes pa'i sems can thams cad nyin re bzhin sangs rgyas kyi zhing rnams su phyin nas bde ba'i longs spyod kun gyis sangs rgyas rnams la bsnyen bkur byed par gyur cig / zhing der rin po che dang me tog la sogs pa bsams ma thag tu ji ltar 'dod pa bzhin du 'byung par gyur cig / zhing der skyes

pa'i sems can thams cad rnam pa thams cad mkhyen pa nyid dang ldan pa'i chos kyi gtam byed pa dang mi 'bral bar gyur cig / zhing der skyes pa'i byang sems thams cad sangs rgyas kyi zhing der 'dug bzhin du phyogs bcu'i rgyal ba rnams la mchod pa'i sprin phung bsam gyis mi khyab pa 'bul zhing / sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das de dag gis thugs brtse pa chen pos mchod pa de dag bzhes par gyur cig / zhing der skyes pa'i sems can thams cad sred med kyi bu'i stobs dang / rdo rje ltar mkhregs pa'i lus dang mthu stobs phun sum tshogs pa thob par gyur cig / sangs rgyas kyi zhing de'i gzi brjid dang / kha dog dang / 'byor pa phun sum tshogs pa @# / / sems can thams cad kyis lha'i mig gis mthong bar gyur cig / zhing der dge ba'i rtsa ba chung ba des kyang / byang chub kyi shing dpag tshad stong dang drug brgya tsam du mngon par mtho ba mthod bar gyur cig / zhing der lung nod pa dang kha ton byed pa'i byang sems de dag kun kyang so so yang dag par rig pa bzhi dang / smon gnas shes pa dang / spobs pa mtha' yas pa thob par gyur cig / zhing der skyes pa'i sems can thams cad phyogs bcu'i sangs rgyas kyi zhing thams cad me long gi dkyil 'khor la byad bzhin gyi gzugs brnyan gsal ba bzhin 'od gsal pa mthong bar gyur cig / zhing der sa dang bar snang la rin po che sna tshogs las grub pa'i spos phor nas bdugs pos dri zhim po rtag tu 'byung bar gyur cig / zhing der me tog dri rab tu zhim pa'i phreng ba dang / rol mo'i sgra yid du 'ong ba rtag tu 'byung bar gyur cig / bdag gi 'od kyis ' jig rten gyi khams kyi sems can thams cad 'od gsal bar gyur nas lha dang mi las lhag pa'i bde ba phun sum tshogs pa dang ldan par gyur cig / phyogs bcu'i byang sems rnams kyis bdag gi ming thos pa tsam la brten nas byang chub kyi snying po'i bar du gzungs phun sum tshogs pa thob par gyur cig / bdag sangs rgyas pa'i tshe bdag gi ming tsam thos nas rab tu dang ba bskyed pa'i bud med de dag tshe ba rjes nas nam yang bud med du mi skye bar skyes pa'i dbang po dang ldan par gyur cig / bdag gi ming tsam thos pa'i sems can de dag kun kyang byang chub ma thob bar du tshangs par spyod pa la gnas pa dang mi 'bral bar gyur cig / bdag sangs rgyas pa'i tshe bdag gi ming thos nas yan lag lngas phyag 'tshal ba de la
