yang lha dang bcas pa'i 'jig rten gyis bkur sti dang rim gro byed par gyur cig / zhing der sems can rnams skyes ma thag tu dge slong dgra

bcom pa bsam gtan gsum pa la snyoms par zhugs pa lta bu'i bde ba thob par gyur cig / zhing der skyes pa'i byang sems rnams la chos gos phun sum tshogs pa bsams ma thag tu 'byung zhing / sangs rgyas kyi zhing gi yon tan gyi bkod pa thams cad ji ltar 'dod pa bzhin du rin po che'i shing las 'byung bar gyur cig / bdag sangs rgyas pa'i tshe zhing khams gzhan na gnas pa'i byang chub sems dpa' rnams kyis bdag gi ming thos ma thag tu shin tu rnam par phye ba zhes bya ba'i ting nge 'dzin thob nas / de la gnas bzhin du sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das grangs ma mchis pa mngon sum du mthong bar gyur cig / bdag gi ming thos pa'i sems can de dag thams cad byang chub ma thob kyi bar du rigs bzang zhing dbang po tshang ba dang / byang sems kyi spyod pa la dga' ba dang / mchog tu dga' ba'i dge ba'i rtsa ba dang ldan par gyur cig / zhing der skyes @# / / pa'i sems can thams cad dam pa'i chos nyan par 'dod pa'i sems bskyed ma thag tu dam pa'i chos thos par gyur cig / zhing khams gzhan du skyes pa'i byang sems rnams kyis bdag gi ming thos pa tsam gyis bla na med pa yang dag par rdzogs pa'i byang chub las phyir mi ldog par gyur cig / mdor na 'jig rten 'dren pa'i dbang po rgyal ba 'od dpag med kyis sngon slob pa lam gyi gnas skabs su smon lam rlabs po che ji snyed cig btab cing legs par grub pa de bzhin du bdag cag rnams kyis kyang bde blag tu grub nas sems can thams cad smin grol gyi lam la myur du 'god nus par gyur cig / dkon mchog brtsegs pa las 'byung ba bzhin du cung zad cig bsdus nas dge slong dge 'dun grub pa dpal bzang pos theg chen pho brang du sbyar ba'o / / ! / / smon lam chen mo'i dus su mdzad pa'i smon lam mdor bsdus / ! sangs rgyas dang byang chub sems dpa' thams cad bdag la dgongs su gsol / sangs rgyas sras dang bcas pa rnams kyi byin rlabs dang / bdag gis dus gsum du bsags pa'i dge ba rnams kyi mthu la brten nas / bdag tshe rabs thams cad du thabs la mkhas pas rigs rus cho 'brang phun sum tshogs shing sngags spyod pa'i dbang po rnon por skyes ma thag tu tshe rabs dran pa dang / gzhon nu la rab tu byung nas tshul khrims rnam dag srung nus par gyur cig / thabs shes khyad par can gyis bstan pa dang sems can la phan pa rgya chen po khyad par du 'phags pa gong nas gong du sgrub nus par gyur cig / tshogs gnyis rlabs po che rdzogs nas sangs rgyas kyi zhing thams cad du mngon par rdzogs par sangs rgyas nas mya

ngan las 'da' ba'i tshul yang mi ston par / nyi ma re re bzhin phyogs bcu rab 'byams na bzhugs pa'i sangs rgyas thams cad kyi mdzad pa dang mnyam par sems can dpag tu med pa smin grol gyi lam la 'god nus par gyur cig / ces pa'i smon lam 'di rje thams cad mkhyen pa dge 'dun grub pa dpal bzang po'i zhal snga nas kyis rta lo'i smon lam chen mo'i dus su sbyar ba'o / / ! / / byams chen bzhengs pa'i smon lam mdor bsdus / ! byams pa'i sku gzugs phul byung bzheng ba la / / mthun rkyen sgrub par byed pa'i lus can rnams / / rgyal ba byams pa mgon po'i zhabs drung du / / theg mchog chos kyi dpal la spyod par shog / nam zhig rdo rje'i gdan gyi ri bo'i spor / / byams mgon nyin byed dbang po shar pa'i tshe / / bdag gi blo gros padmo kha bye nas / / skal bzang bung ba'i tshogs rnams tshi mas byed shog / de tshe rgyal ba byams pa rab tu dgyes / / phyag g.yas bdag gi mgo la bzhag bzhin du / / bla med byang chub mchog tu lung bstan nas / / 'gro kun don du sangs @# / / rgyas myur thob shog / byang chub sgrub pa'i tshe rabs kun tu yang / / dus gsum rgyal ba sras bcas thams cad kyi / / rlabs chen spyod pa ji snyed mchis pa kun / / gcig tu bsdus nas tshul bzhin 'doms par shog / legs bshad ri mo bkra ba'i lung gi gos / / rnam dpyod gser gyi yu ba la brten cing / / bslab gsum nor bu'i tog gis rab mtshan pa'i / / bstan pa'i rgyal mtshan phyogs bcur 'dzugs par shog / phan bde'i 'byung gnas bstan pa dar zhing rgyas / / bstan 'dzin skyes bu thams cad sku khams bzang / / lus can kun la bde skyid 'byung ba'i gnas / / bkra shis lhun po rtag tu rgyas gyur cig / rtag tu byams pa rnam gsum goms pa'i mthus / / bdud sde byams pa'i dpung gis 'joms pa dang / / 'gro kun byams pa'i stobs kyis skyong mjad pa'i / / rgyal ba byams pa mgon po'i bkra shis shog ces pa rje thams cad mkhyen pa dge 'dun grub kyis mdzad pa'o / / ! / / snyan ngag rgyun chags kyi smon lam / ! oM bde legs su gyur cig / rab brtan dad pa rgya mtsho'i gos can shin tu yangs pa'i ngos la rnam dag tshul khrims zla ba nor bu'i rdo leb dkar po gcal du bkram pa'i 'og gzhi brtan por rnam dkar las kyi mtho ris bzo bos dal 'byor rin chen rtsig pa rgya chen rab brtsegs rnam thar sgo bzhi grub mtha' rnam bzhi'i them skas dang ldan snying rje'i ka ba brtan pos gzhan phan gdung chen legs par bteg pa'i yid kyi

tshoms chen mkhyen rab nyi zla'i snang ba gsal bar 'char ba'i mngon par shes pa'i skar khud lung dang rigs pa'i rin chen dra mig rab mdzes blo bzang bden bzhi sgrog pa'i dril chen lhag bsam dkar ba'i rnga yab dang 'grogs man ngag nor bu'i do shal do shal phyed pa mdzes bar 'phyang ba'i tshogs gnyis ba ga ma mthon po dang ldan 'phags nor bdun gyis legs par gtams pa'i blo yi bad mdzod dman pa min par dal gyis rgyu ba'i rnam dpyod mdzes ma ting 'dzin lang tsho rab rgyas legs bshad 'dzum dkar ston mkhas dang 'grogs blo chen rgyal sras kun dang thabs gcig nyid du mi 'jigs seng ge'i khri la theg chen chos kyi dga' bde'i dpal la rtag tu dgyes par rol pa'i chos kyi rgyal po'i pho brang khang brtsegs yid 'phrog gang der tshad med byams pa'i dpung gis 'jigs rung bdud dang lha min mu stegs byed sogs nag po'i rtsa lag sde dar bcas pa'i g.yul las rnam par rgyal bas lha rnams dga' ba'i dga' ston rgyal mtshan mthon po gnam du sgreng ba'i spro dga' rgya cher gsar du sbel ba'i chos kyi rnga chen srid gsum g.yo ba'i sgra dbyangs zab mo ci yang sgreg pa dang bcas skyabs gsum dge legs dbang gi rgyal po 'dun pa'i rgyal mtshan rtse mor lan gcig min par mchod pas @# / / legs par grub pa'i phan bde'i dpal 'byor bzang po mtha' dag 'gro la yid bzhin stsol ba'i mdzad pa lhun grub rgyun chags 'jug pa nyid kyi snyan pa'i ba dan dkar po 'bum phrag phyogs bcur rol pa'i grags pa rgya chen lus can kun gyi rna ba'i lam nas bde bar son pas yid kyi khyim du rtag par dge legs spel gyur cig / 'di yang rje nyid kyis mdzad pa'o / / mang+ga laM / / bsod grags dpe

gu ru zhi ba'i sgom bzlas nyams su len pa'i tshul ni / rang gu ru drag po'am rta mgrin gang rung gi skur bsgoms pa'i mdun gyi nam mkhar rang bzhin stong pa'i ngang las paM las sna tshogs padma'i sdong po yangs shing rgya che ba / de'i steng du seng ges bteg pa'i rin po che'i khri'i steng du nyi ma dang zla ba'i gdan la gu ru dus gsum sangs rgyas sku mdog dkar la dmar ba'i mdangs chags pa / zhal 'dzum bag dang bcas pa / spyan gnyis zhi ma khro'i tshul du hur gyis gzigs pa / rab tu byung ba dge slong rdo rje 'dzin pa'i cha byad can snam sbyar dang chos gos sku la gsol ba / phyag g.yas rdo rje dang / g.yon mnyam gzhag gi steng na thod pa bdud rtsis gang ba 'dzin cing / mchan khung na kha TwAM ga bsnams pa / dbu la paN zhwa dmar po gsol ba / zhabs rdo rje skyil krung gis bzhugs pa / de'i 'khor du rig 'dzin dpa' bo mkha' 'gro chos skyong srung ma'i @# / / tshogs bsam gyis mi khyab pas bskor ba / de'i spyi bor oM / mgrin par AH thugs kar hUM / rang gi thugs ka'i hUM las 'od zer 'phros pas u rgyan gyi gnas nas bsgoms pa dang 'dra ba'i ye shes pa 'khor dang bcas pa spyan drangs / dzaH hUM baM hoH gnyis su med par gyur / mchod gtor rnams bla med ltar byin gyis brlabs / oM badzra gu ru sa pa ri wA ra ar+g+haM nas shap+ta'i bar dang / rU pa nas spar+sha'i bar gyis dbul / oM AH hUM gis nang mchod phul la bzlas pa bya ba ni / mdun bskyed kyi thugs kar zla ba'i steng du rdo rje rtse lnga pa lte ba la hUM gis mtshan pa'i mtha' skor du oM AH hUM badzra gu ru padma sid+d+hi hUM zhes pa'i sngags kyis bskor bar bsgoms nas / mdun bskyed kyi thugs ka'i sngags 'phreng sa bon dang bcas pa la phog pas thugs rgyud bskul nas mchog thun mong gi dngos grub stsol bar bsams la bzlas pa mang du bya'o / / mthar bla ma'i gnas gsum gyi yi ge gsum las 'od zer dkar dmar mthing gsum rim pa bzhin dang cig car byung / rang gi gnas gsum du rim pa ltar dang cig car thim pa las lus ngag yid gsum so so gang / thams cad kyi sdig sgrib dag bum pa / gsang ba / shes rab ye shes / dbang bzhi pa rnams thob / rdo rje gsum gyi dngos grub kyang thob par bsam mo / / gtor ma dbul na / ljags hUM las skyes pa'i rdo rje dmar po rtse gcig pa 'od kyi sbu gu can gyis gtor ma'i bcud thams cad drangs te gsol bar bsams la / sngags kyi mthar ba liM ta pratIts+tsha hUM swA hA zhes pa btags la dbul / mchod pa

dang nang mchod kyang phul / hUM / ma bcos spros bral bla ma chos kyi sku / / bde chen longs spyod bla ma chos kyi rje / / pad sdong las 'khrungs bla ma sprul pa'i sku / / sku gsum rdo rje 'chang la spyi bos 'dud / / ces pas bstod do / / gu ru zhi ba'i sgom bzlas 'di yang rje bla ma'i gsung las byung ba dge legs 'phel / / / / ! bla ma dang lhag pa'i lha dbyer ma mchis pa'i zhabs la phyag 'tshal lo / / bla ma drag po'i thugs sgrub gter kha gong ma'i thugs kyi sgrub thabs mdor bsdus pa'i tshul ni 'di yin te / skyabs 'gro sems bskyed tshad med bzhi sgom pa sngon du btang / swa b+hA wa sa stong par sbyangs / stong pa'i ngang las oM las rin po che'i gzhal med khang gru bzhi sgo bzhi rta babs dang bcas shing phyi rol srung ba'i 'khor lo chen po brgyad dang bcas pas bskor ba'i dbus su chos 'byung gru gsum mthing nag nang dgra bgegs kyi khrag zhag gi rgya mtshos gang ba'i steng du paM las sna tshogs padma / raM las nyi ma'i dkyil 'khor gyi gdan la ru tra pho mo bsnol ba'i @# / / steng du hUM las byung ba'i gnam lcags kyi rdo rje rtse dgu pa hUM gis mtshan pa / de las 'od zer dpag tu med pa 'phros / dgra bgegs log 'dren gdug pa can thams cad tshar bcad / tshur 'dus thim pa yongs su gyur pa las / rang nyid bcom ldan 'das padma drag po sku mdog dmar po zhal gcig phyag gnyis g.yas gnam lcags kyi rdo rje rtse dgu pa nam mkha' la 'phyar zhing / g.yon pas lcags kyi sdig pa nag po mgo dgu r+wa bco brgyad pa sdig mdzub dang bcas pas 'dzin pa / zhal rab tu gdangs shing 'bar ba'i mche ba rnon po bzhi gtsigs pa / dmar la zlum pa'i spyan gsum sdang mig tu bgrad cing smin ma'i mtshams nas bskal pa'i glog stong 'gyu ba shangs nas drag po'i 'thor rlung 'tshub cing zhal nas hUM dang phaT kyi sgra 'brug ltar sgrog pa / smin ma dang sma ra dmar ser 'bar zhing dbu skra kham ser gyen du brdzes pa / thod skam lnga'i dbu rgyan dang rin po che'i rtse phran gyis brgyan cing thod rlon lnga bcu'i do shal can / rus pa'i rgyan drug gis brgyan cing klu chen po brgyad kyis phyag zhabs mdzes pa / glang po che'i ko ba dang zhing chen gyi g.yang gzhis stod g.yogs shing / stag gi pags pa'i sham thabs can / sku la khrag gi thig le dang zhag gi zo ris dang thal chen gyi tshom bus brgyan cing / gar dgu'i nyams dang ldan pa / zhabs g.yas bskum zhing g.yon brkyang pa'i stabs kyis ye shes kyi me rab tu 'bar ba'i dbus na bzhugs pa / dbu'i

gtsug na nam mkha' lding nag po lcags kyi mchu sder dang me'i gshog pa can / gshog pa'i gseb nas gnam lcags kyi thog ser 'bab pa / de'i spyi gtsug tu gu ru padma sku mdog mthing nag phyag g.yas kha TwAM ga dang g.yon thod khrag 'dzin pa / zhabs rdo rje skyil krung gis bzhugs pa / rang gi spyi bor 'khor lo ser po rtsibs bzhi'i dbus su sku'i lha 'jam dpal ser po g.yas ral gri dang g.yon sdigs mdzub 'chang ba / mgrin par padma 'dab ma bzhi pa'i dbus su gsung gi lha rta mgrin dmar po g.yas dbyug pa dang / g.yon sdigs mdzub mdzad pa / thugs kar ye shes kyi mchod rten seng khri bang rim bum pa bre 'khor lo tog dang bcas pa'i bum pa'i nang du thugs kyi lha phyag rdor mthing nag g.yas rdo rje dang g.yon sdigs mdzub brkyang pa / lte bar chos 'byung dmar po'i dbus su padma 'dab ma bzhi pa la dbus su rdo rje phag mo dmar mo gri gug dang thod khrag 'dzin pa / 'dab ma bzhi la rigs bzhi'i mkha' 'gros bskor ba / gsang gnas su sna tshogs rdo rje'i lte bar 'phrin las kyi khro bo yak+Sha me dbal sku mdog smug nag shin tu khros pa / g.yas me'i tho ba dang g.yon lcags kyu 'dzin pa / rang gi spyi bor sku rdo rje'i ngo bo oM dkar po / mgrin par gsung rdo rje'i ngo bo AH dmar po / thugs kar thugs ka'i lha phyag rdor gyi thugs kar nyi gdan la thugs rdo rje'i ngo bo hUM sngon po / thugs ka'i hUM las 'od 'phros pas rang bzhin gyi gnas nas bsgoms pa dang 'dra ba'i ye shes pa spyan drangs / dzaH hUM paM hoH gnyis su med par gyur / slar yang thugs ka'i hUM las 'od 'phros / rigs lnga 'khor bcas spyan drangs / de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyis mngon par @# / / dbang skur du gsol / zhes gsol ba btab pas de rnams kyis oM sarba ta thA ga ta a b+hiShe ka ta sa ma ya shri ye hUM / zhes dbang bskur / lus gang / dri ma dag / chu lhag ma spyi gtsug tu gnas pa yongs su gyur pa las sangs rgyas snang ba mtha' yas kyis dbu brgyan par gyur / mchod pa bla med bzhin bsangs sbyangs byin gyis brlabs nas / oM gu ru padma kro d+ha rA dza sa ba ri wA ra ar+g+haM pra tI ts+tsha ye swA hA / de bzhin du shap+ta'i bar du sbyar la phyi'i mchod pa dang / hUM / gdod nas rnam dag bdud rtsi'i sman / / ye shes lnga rdzogs a mr-i ta / / dug lnga sel ba'i bdud rtsi mchog / bcom ldan 'khor dang bcas la dbul / / X sngags kyi mthar / pany+tsa a mr-i ta kha raM khA hi / sman dbul lo / / gdug pa'i

dgra bgegs tshogs rnams dang / / dug lnga'i nyon mongs dbyings su bsgral / / sha khrag phung po bdud rtsir gyur / / bcom ldan 'khor dang bcas la dbul / / X sarba big+hA na sha truM kha khA / khA hi khA hi / bsgral mchod do / / X sngags kyi mthar oMH AH hUM btags la nang mchod dbul / rang snang thabs dang shes rab ni / / rdo rje padma mnyam par sbyor / / bde stong lhan cig skyes pa'i dngos / / bcom ldan 'khor dang bcas la dbul / / zhes gsang ba dang de kho na nyid kyi mchod pas kyang mchod la / lhun grub sgrib bral bde chen chos kyi sku / / dbang po'i gzhu ltar dwangs pa longs spyod rdzogs / / khro rgyal gdug pa 'dul mdzad sprul pa'i sku / / sku gsum dbyer med khyod la phyag 'tshal lo / / zhes bstod de bzlas pa bya ba'i tshul ni / thugs kyi lha phyag na rdo rje'i thugs kar nyi ma'i dkyil 'khor gyi steng du rdo rje sngon po rtse lnga pa lte ba la hUM yig dmar la sngo ba'i mdangs can gyi mthar bzla bya'i sngags phreng kha dog dmar po gzugs yi ge dbu can gyi rnam pa can gyis bskor ba / de las bskal pa 'jig pa'i me'i tsha tsha lta bu'i 'od zer lus kyi nang thams cad khyab par 'phros / nad gdon dgra bgegs sdig sgrib thams cad sbyangs / 'od zer ba spu'i sgo nas phyir 'phros / snang srid thams cad ye shes kyi me 'bar ba'i klong dkyil gcig tu gyur pas dgra bgegs gdug pa can thams cad bya sgro mes bsregs pa bzhin du gzhob thul gyis bsregs shing tshar bcad par bsams la / oM AH hUM ar tsig nir tsig na mo b+ha ga wa te / a ya ma du ru tsa sha na / oM badzra ga ru Da hUM / oM badzra yak+Sha hUM / oM badzra rak+Sha hUM / gnod byed 'byung po'i snying la mA ra ya hUM phaT / ces mang du bzla'o / / mdun bskyed la gtor ma 'bul tshul sogs ni spyi dang mtshungs / / / / ! na mo gu ru / gtor ma la brten pa'i rjes gnang mdor bsdus bya bar 'dod na / gtor ma phyag len bzhin du bshams / gong du bshad pa ltar padma drag por bskyed pa nas bzlas pa'i bar rdzogs par byas la / slob mas khrus byas maN+Dal phul / kun mkhyen ye shes phung po can / / zhes sogs lan gsum gyis gsol ba gdab / spyi dang bye brag gi chos bshad / dkon mchog gsum la bdag skyabs mchi / / zhes sogs kyis sdom pa gzung / bla ma dang gtor ma gnyis ka slob ma'i ngor padma drag por gsal btab bsgom du gzhug de nas sku'i rjes gnang ni / dus gsum sangs rgyas thams cad kyi /

/ sku yi rdo rje slob dpon gyis / / bdag la padma drag po yi / / sku yi rjes gnang stsal du gsol / / zhes gsol ba gdab / sna tshogs padma dang nyi ma @# / / dang ru tra pho mo spyi bo bsnol ba'i steng du hUM dmar la sngo ba'i mdangs chags pa yongs su gyur pa las slob ma padma drag por mngon rtogs bzhin du bskyed / lus la lha rnams dgod / gnas gsum byin gyis brlab / rang gi thugs ka'i hUM gi 'od zer gyis rang bzhin gyis gnas nas bsgoms pa dang 'dra ba'i padma drag po la rig 'dzin brgyud pa'i bla ma rnams dang sangs rgyas byang sems dpa' bo mkha' 'gro chos skyong srung ma'i tshogs kyis bskor ba spyan drangs / sprin gyi phung po gtibs pa bzhin du byon / slob ma'i lus la char bzhin du babs nas gnyis su med par thim par bsam / gu ru padma kro d+ha rA dza sa pa ri wA ra sa mA dzaH zhes drag tu brjod / rol mo'i sgra bya'o / / gsung gyi rjes gnang ni / gsung gi rdo rje slob dpon gyis / / zhes 'don pa spos la gsol ba gdab / bla ma padma drag po'i skur gsal ba'i thugs ka nas oM AH hUM ar tsig / ces sogs kyi / sngags phreng kha dog dmar po byung / bla ma'i shangs bug g.yas pa nas 'thon / slob ma'i sna bug g.yon par zhugs / thugs kar thugs rdo rje phyag rdor gyi thugs kar nyi ma'i steng du hUM yig gi mtha' skor du gnas pa las 'od zer dus mtha'i me 'od tsam 'phros / dgra bgegs gdug pa can rnams tshar bcad par bsams la sngags kyi rjes zlos lan gsum bya'o / / de nas / bcom ldan bdag la stsal lags kyi / / bdag la brtse bar mdzad du gsol / / zhes gsol ba btab pas / bla mas me tog spyi bor bzhag nas / bcom ldan 'di la stsal lags kyi / / 'di la nye bar mdzad du gsol / / zhes brjod do / / thugs kyi rjes gnang ni / thugs kyi rdo rje slob dpon zhes bsgyur la gsol ba btab pas / bla ma padma drag por gsal ba'i thugs ka'i hUM yig dmar la sngo ba'i mdangs chags pa las thugs gnyis su med pa'i ye shes kyi rang bzhin gnam lcags kyi rdo rje me rab tu 'bar ba nam mkha'i khams gang ba byung / slob ma'i snying ga'i hUM yig la thim pas padma drag po'i thugs dang slob ma'i sems ro gcig tu gyur par bsam / de nas / bcom ldan 'das la stsal lags kyi / / bdag la nye bar mdzad du gsol / / zhes gsol ba btab la / gtor ma padma drag po'i skur bskyed pa slob ma'i spyi bor bzhag / bcom ldan 'di la stsal lags kyi / /

'di la 'go bar mdzad du gsol / / dus 'di nyid nas bzung nas su / / byang chub snying por mchis kyi bar / / lhag pa'i lha ni mdzad du gsol / / rkyen ngan bar chad thams cad sol / / bgegs dang log 'dren rdul du rlog / mchog dang thun mong dngos grub stsol / / oM AH hUM ar tsig ces sogs brjod nas slob ma'i lus la thim pas slob ma'i lus ngag yid gsum dang padma drag po'i sku gsung thugs dbyer mi phyed par gyur / mjug yon dbul ba dang tshogs kyi 'khor lo sogs kyang bya'o / / padma drag po'i mngon rtogs rjes gnang dang bcas pa 'di yang rje btsun thams cad mkhyen pas dpal ldan 'bras spungs kyi dga' ldan pho brang du mdzad pa lags so / / / / ! padma yang gsang khros pa'i sgrub thabs phrin las bzhi'i bang mdzod ces bya ba / rje btsun dpal ldan bla ma dam pa'i zhabs kyi madmor gus pas phyag 'tshal lo / / ji snyed shes bya'i snang ba kun 'char pha mtha' yas pa'i bde chen gnas de rgyal ba rnams kyi chos kyi sku / / @# / / srid gsum 'byung po kun gyi mgo bor khros pa'i gar mdzad gar dbang ma dang gnyis med sbyor de longs spyod rdzogs / / yid 'ong mdzes pa'i chu skyes las 'khrungs mtsho las skyes pa'i rdo rje zhes grags dus gsum sangs rgyas sprul pa'i sku / / sku gsum dbyer med zhabs kyi padmo spyi bor bsten no bdag gi snying la nam yang 'bral ba med gyur cig / padma gsung gi lha tshogs las / / yang gsang khros pa sgrub pa'i thabs / / rgyud dang dam pa'i phyag len bzhin / / go sla'i ngag gis 'dir bshad bya / / 'dir padma dbang chen yang gsang khros pa'i phrin las kyi rim pa 'chad pa la gsum / gang du bsgrub pa'i gnas kyi mtshan nyid / sgrub pa po rten gyi gang zag gi mtshan nyid / des nyams su blang bar bya ba'i sgrub thabs kyi rnam gzhag go / dang po ni rgyud las / dur khrod ri brag dmar po la / / nub ri mtho zhing shar ri dma' / / nags tshal stug po nub tu bltas / / nam mkha' padma 'dab brgyad 'dra / / nyi zla gza' skar 'od 'bar zhing / / chu phran ri brag kun 'dud par / / zhes gsungs pa ltar / mtshan nyid dang ldan zhing yid dang mthun pa'i gnas su bya'o / / gnyis pa ni / rgyud las / dbang bgrod nod dam ldan slob dpon bkur / / brtson 'grus ldan pas rtse gcig bsgrub / / ces gsungs pa ltar gyi sgrub pa pos / tsha tsha sbyin gtong mdo sde gdon / / 'dus byas dge rtsa nus tshad bya / / zhes gsungs pa ltar gyi phyi'i sngon 'gro rnams legs par bsgrubs

te nyams su blang ngo / / gsum pa la thog mar bya ba'i rim pa / bar du bya ba'i rim pa / tha mar bya ba'i rim pa'o / / dang po la thog mar sngon 'gro gtor ma bya ba'i tshul ni / skyabs 'gro sems bskyed tshad med bzhi sngon du 'gro bas / rang skad cig gis dpal rta mgrin sku mdog dmar po zhal gcig phyag gnyis kyi phyag g.yas seng ldeng gi dbyug pa 'phyar zhing / g.yon thugs kar sdigs mdzub mdzad pa / dur khrod kyi chas brgyad kyis brgyan cing gar gyi nyams dgu dang ldan par gyur par bsgoms la / sngon 'gro gtor ma phyag len bzhin bshams pa la / raM yaM khaM rat+na b+hany+dza oM AH hUM / zhes pas gtor ma zag pa med pa'i ye shes kyi bdud rtsir byin gyis brlabs la / rang gi thugs ka'i hrIH las 'od 'phros / phyogs skyong zhing skyong klu la sogs pa rnams spyan drangs / skad cig gis 'od gsal du bcug pa las padma dbang chen gyi lha'i skur gyur pa'i mgron rnams kyi ljags hUM las skyes pa'i rdo rje rtse gcig pa dmar po 'od kyi sbu gu can du gyur pas gtor ma'i bcud thams cad drangs te gsol bar bsams la / a kA ro mu khaM sogs kyi sngags lan gsum gyis gtor ma bsngos la mchod cing nang mchod kyang phul nas / rnal 'byor pa bdag cag padma dbang chen gyi sgrub pa nyams su len pa'i bar chad thams cad zhi bar mdzod cig / ces 'phrin las bcol / mgron rnams rang gnas su gshegs par bsam mo / / de nas mtshams bcad cing srung 'khor bya ba ni / rang padma dbang chen du gsal ba'i thugs kar padma dmar po 'dab ma brgyad pa'i lte bar nyi ma'i dkyil 'khor la gnas pa'i hrIH dmar nag las dus mtha'i me lta bu'i 'od zer dpag tu med pa phyogs bcur 'phros pa'i sna la dpal rta mgrin gyi lha'i tshogs nam mkha' gang ba spros pas bgegs dang log par 'dren pa thams cad phyi'i rgya mtsho'i pha rol du bskrad / slar 'dus pa las steng 'og phyogs mtshams thams cad du khro bo'i gur bar mtshams med par gnas pa / @# / / de'i phyi rol tu rdo rje'i ra ba rim pa gsum / de'i phyi rol tu me dang rlung dang chu'i ra ba rim pa gsum gyis bskor te bgegs rnams kyis lta ba tsam yang mi nus par gyur par bsams la / rol mo dbyangs dang bcas pas / hUM| dpal chen mi bzad dkyil 'khor nas / / bar ba'i khro bo me dpung 'bar / / gdug pa'i mtshon cha sna tshogs bsnams / / bgegs dang log 'dren rdul du rlog / dbang chen me dpung dmar nag 'bar / / bskal pa dus mtha'i me lta bu / / dbang drag mtshon cha brag ltar gtams / / gang la bab

kyang gcod cing sgrol / / dbang chen khro bo mi bzad rngam / / srid pa'i ye shes 'khor lo 'khrigs / / dbang chen mtshams las gang 'da' ba / / rdul phran bzhin du rlag par gyis / oM raM kro d+ha rak+Sha badzra dzwa la raM tik+Sha b+hi sha dzwa la raM phaT phaT / raM raM zhes mtshams gcad do / / de nas mchod pa / nang mchod / sman rag gtor ma dang bcas phyag len bzhin bshams la / mchod pa byin gyis brlab pa ni / mchod pa rnams la raM kro d+ha'i sngags kyis bgegs bskrad / swa b+hA was stong par sbyangs / stong pa'i ngang las a las byung ba'i thod pa yangs shing rgya che ba rnams kyi nang du rang rang gi ming yig dang po thig les brgyan pa zhu ba las byung ba'i mchod yon / zhabs bsil / me tog bdug spos / mar me / dri / zhal zas / rol mo la sogs pa rnams rang bzhin stong pa / rnam pa mchod rdzas / byed las dbang po drug gi spyod yul du zag med kyi bde ba khyad par can skyed par gyur par bsams pa / oMr+g+haM AH hUM / de bzhin du shap+ta'i bar dang / rU pa nas / spar+sha'i bar du sbyar la rang rang gi sngags dang phyag rgyas byin gyis brlab / nang mchod byin gyis brlab pa ni / sngar ltar bsangs sbyangs / raM yaM khaM zhes brjod pas raM las ye shes kyi mes bsregs / yaM las rlung gis gtor / khaM las chus bskrus te mi dmigs par gyur / stong pa'i ngang las thod pa dum bu gcig pa phyi dkar la nang dmar ba'i nang du 'khor lo rtsibs bzhi pa lte ba dang bcas pa / lte bar padma dmar po 'dab ma brgyad pa / shar du nyi ma / lhor rin po che / nub tu zla ba / byang du rdo rje rgya gram / de dag gi steng du b+h+rUM aM dzriM khaM hUM las sha lnga dang / laM maM paM taM baM las bdud rtsi lnga / de rnams yongs su gyur pa las rigs lnga yab yum du gyur pa rnams snyoms par zhugs pa'i byang chub kyi sems kyi 'od zer gyis 'phags pa mchod / sems can gyi don byas / snod bcud thams cad bsdus nas rigs lnga yab yum la thim / de dag 'od du zhu bas bdud rtsi dkar po dri ma med pa'i rgya mtshor gyur pa'i steng du zla gdan la ye shes lnga'i bdag nyid oM dkar pos mtshan pa / oM AH hUM lan gsum brjod / de nas ye shes kyi bdud rtsi dbab par 'dod na / rang gi lag pa g.yon pa'i mtheb srin gnyis a dang ma las nyi ma dang zla bar gyur / bdud rtsi'i rgya mtsho'i steng du padma 'dab ma bzhi pa'i lte bar las kyi rtsa mgrin sku mdog dmar nag

g.yas thugs kar padma dang / g.yon rdo rje rgya gram bsnol stabs su 'dzin pa la gsang ba'i yum mi pham dkar mo lcags kyu 'dzin pa / khro gnyer can ser mo zhags pa 'dzin pa / ral gcig ma dmar mo lcags sgrog 'dzin pa / ro langs ma ljang gu dril bu 'dzin pa rnams kyis mdun @# / / rgyab dang g.yas g.yon nas sku la 'khril ba / rta mgrin gyi dbu'i gtsug na rta mgo ljang gu'i steng du yi ge hrIH dmar po de nyid rang gi mtheb srin gyis nyi zla gnyis kyi bar du bzung ba las 'od zer 'phros / 'og min nas rgyal ba yab yum sbyan drangs / snyoms par zhugs pa'i byang chub kyi sems rta mgrin yab yum gyi sbyor mtshams nas babs pas ye shes kyi bdud rtsi'i rgya mtshor gyur par bsams la / oM sarba pany+tsa a mr-i te hUM / zhes pa'i 'jam bsnyen byas te bsgrub bo / / sman phud dang gtor ma nang mchod ltar byin gyis brlab cing bsgrub bo / / rak+ta byin gyis brlab pa ni / sngar ltar bsangs sbyangs / stong pa'i ngang las a las thod pa stong gsum dang mnyam pa'i nang du ma las nyi ma'i dkyil 'khor gyi steng du rang gi thugs ka'i hrIH las raM yig dmar po 'phros / 'od du zhu ba las rak+ta'i rgya mtsho rba klong bsnol mar 'khrug pa tshil chen gyi dar chags pa / rang bzhin stong pa nyid / rnam pa rak+ta / ngo bo yum gyi byang chub kyi sems thams cad kyi 'byung gnas su gyur par bsams la / oM ma hA padma rak+ta hUM / zhes bzlas pas byin gyis brlab bo / / de nas tshogs zhing mchod pa ni / oM badzra sa ma ya hUM dzaH rang gi thugs ka'i hrIMH las 'od zer 'phros pas bla ma dang gnyis su med pa'i yang gsang khros pa khrag 'thung lha dgu'i dkyil 'khor sangs rgyas dang byang chub sems dpa'i tshogs dang bcas pa mdun gyi nam mkhar spyan drangs / 'od zer rang gi snying ga'i hrIH la thim / hUM| dpal chen khro bo mi bzad pa / / rta mchog dpal la phyag 'tshal lo / / khro mo yum la phyag 'tshal lo / / sprul pa'i sku la phyag 'tshal lo / / sgo ma bzhi la phyag 'tshal lo / / zhes phyag bya / rang gi thugs ka'i hrIH las byung ba'i mchod pa'i lha mo rnams kyis mchod par gyur par bsams la / hrIH badzra kro d+ha ha ya grI ba sa pa ri wA ra ar+g+haM pra tIts+tsha ye swA hA / de bzhin du shap+ta 'i bar du sbyar la phyi'i mchod pa dang / oM sarba pany+tsa a mr-i ta la kha raM khA hi / oM ma hA padma rak+ta a mr-i ta la kha raM khA hi / oM dz+nyA na sa ma ti pu dza te AH hUM /

zhes pa rnams kyis sman rag ting nge 'dzin dang bcas pas mchod / hUM| bdag cag ma rig nyon mongs sems can gyis / / bag med tshul gyi dam las 'gal gyur te / / padma dbang chen dkyil 'khor lha tshogs kyi / / thugs dang 'gal ba'i las ni ci bgyis pa / / thugs rje che mnga' khyed la bzod par gsol / / bzod par bzhes nas tshangs pa'i dngos grub stsol / / zhes sdig pa bshags pa dang / dkon mchog gsum la bdag skyabs mchi / / zhes pa nas / 'gro la phan phyir sangs rgyas 'grub par shog / ces pa'i bar gyis sems bskyed nas lam la slob par dam bca' zhing / sems can thams cad bde ba dang ldan par gyur cig sdug bsngal dang bral bar gyur cig sdug bsngal med pa'i bde ba dang mi 'bral bar gyur cig nye ring chags sdang gnyis dang bral ba'i btang snyoms la yun ring du gnas par gyur cig ces tshad med bzhi bsgom / de nas tshogs zhing rnams kyis bdag dang gnas mchod rdzas dang bcas pa byin gyis brlabs par bsams nas byin dbab pa ni / hUM| yi dam lha dang dkon mchog gsum gyi dngos / / rtsa brgyud bla ma mi mngon dbyings nas bzhengs / / dur khrod gsang ba dbang drag dkyil 'khor du / / thod pa rin @# / / chen las grub gzhal yas khang / / gnam lcags ur mo'i gzer chen ta la la / / sprul pa'i lcang lo mang po'i kha bad can / / gsang ba'i me ri dmar nag 'tshub mar 'bar / / mi ro thod phreng keng rus sogs kyis brgyan / / rak+ta'i rgya mtsho rba rlabs chil li li / / rus chen tshogs kyi phung po khral la la / / khrag dang zhag gi 'bab chu zu lu lu / / sha chen tshil chen dri ngad thul lu lu / / tsit+ta gsar rnying rgyan mchog ye re re / / dbang chen khrag 'thung rgyal po 'khor dang bcas / / rgyud sde brgyad kyi lha tshogs mang po dang / / ma mo mkha' 'gro'i tshogs dang bcas pa rnams / / gnas mchog 'di ru byin gyis brlab tu gsol / / sgrub mchog bdag la dbang zhig skur du gsol / / bgegs dang log 'dren bar chad bsal du gsol / / mchog dang thun mong dngos grub stsal du gsol / / grub pa'i rtags mtshan myur du bstan du gsol / / chos nyid zhi ba'i tshul gyis don mdzad pa'i / / bcom ldan zhi ba'i lha tshogs dbyings nas bzhengs / / khro bo'i tshul gyis gdug pa 'dul mdzad pa'i / / 'bar ba khro bo'i lha tshogs dbyings nas bzhengs / / skye med chos kyi dbyings nas sku bzhengs pa / / 'jam dpal sku yi lha tshogs dbyings nas bzhengs / / khams gsum dbang du sdud pa'i las mdzad pa'i

/ / padma gsung gi lha tshogs dbyings nas bzhengs / / dus gsum bde gshegs rnams kyi las mdzad pa'i / yang dag thugs kyi lha tshogs dbyings nas bzhengs / / dug lnga gtan 'joms ye shes lnga sbyor ba'i / / bdud rtsi yon tan lha tshogs dbyings nas bzhengs / / gdug pa'i tshogs rnams ma lus tshar gcod pa'i / / phur pa phrin las lha tshogs dbyings nas bzhengs / / thabs dang shes rab gnyis med dgyes rol ba'i / / ma mo rbod gtong lha tshogs dbyings nas bzhengs / / bstan la gnod pa'i dgra bgegs tshar gcod pa'i / / dmod pa drag sngags lha tshogs dbyings nas bzhengs / / legs nyes stangs 'dzin dam tshig rjes gcod pa'i / / 'jig rten mchod bstod lha tshogs dbyings nas bzhengs / / rtsi shing thams cad ye nas sman dang bcud / / snang srid thams cad ye nas byang chub sems / / stong gsum thams cad ye nas gzhal yas khang / / rgyud drug thams cad ye nas rgyal ba'i sku / / sgra dbyangs thams cad drag po'i sngags kyi tshig / gnas mchog 'di ru byin gyis brlab tu gsol / / zhes sogs sbyar la byin dbab / de nas / oM badzra aM ku sha dzaH zhes sogs brjod la tshogs zhing rang la thim pas byin gyis brlabs par bsam mo / / de rnams kyis ni bsod nams kyi tshogs bsags pa ste / 'dzam bu gling pa'i mngal skyes khams drug ldan gyis rang nyid 'chi ba'i sngon rol du skyes nas myong 'gyur gyi bsod nams kyi las 'du byas pa dang chos mthun no / / de nas ye shes kyi tshogs bsags pa ni / snang srid 'khor 'das kyis bsdus pa'i chos thams cad sgyu ma dang chu zla bzhin du rang bzhin gyis grub pa rdul tsam yang med pa'i stong pa nyid du gyur par bsams la / swa b+hA wa'i sngags brjod cing / stong nyid snying rje dbyer med kyi byang chub kyi sems la yun ring du mnyam par gzhag go / de ni las bsags pa'i 'og tu phung sogs rim gyis thim ste / 'chi ba 'od gsal mngon du byas pa dang rnam pa mthun no / / de rnams ni @# / / thog mar bya ba'i rim pa'o / / gnyis pa bar du bya ba'i rim pa la / gzhi rgyu'i ting nge 'dzin gsal gdab pa dang / ting nge 'dzin gyi dkyil 'khor bskyed pa / ye shes pa dgug gzhug bya ba / dkyil 'khor mchod pa'i tshul lo / / dang po ni / de ltar snang ba thams cad bsdus pa'i stong pa'i ngang las rang gi sems ye shes lnga'i bdag nyid can gyi hUM yig gi rnam par nam mkhar gnas par gyur par bsams te / de ni 'chi ba 'od gsal las lugs ldog tu bar do'i lus grub pa dang rnam pa mthun par bsgom pa'o

/ / gnyis pa la / dang po sbyor ba'i ting nge 'dzin dang / dkyil 'khor rgyal mchog gi ting nge 'dzin gnyis las / dang po la'ang / thog mar rten gzhal yas khang bskyed pa ni / rang gi sems hUM yig tu gnas pa las e sngo skya / yaM dud kha / raM dmar po / khaM dmar nag suM ser po / keM dkar po rnams rim pa ltar chad de steng nas steng du brtsegs par gyur / e agne maN+Da la / e las nam mkha'i dkyil 'khor sngo skya gru gsum / yaM karma rak+Sha maN+Da la / yaM las rlung gi dkyil 'khor zla gaM dud kha / raM dzwa la maN+Da la / raM las me'i dkyil 'khor dmar po gru gsum pa / khaM rak+ta maN+Da la / khaM las khrag gi rgya mtsho dmar nag zlum po / suM suk+She maN+Da la / suM las sa'i dkyil 'khor ser po gru bzhi pa / keM maN+Da la / keM las keng rus kyi ri rab gru bzhi dkar po / de rnams steng nas steng du brtsegs pa| de dag kyang phyi 'byung ba lnga / nang ye shes lnga / gsang ba yum lnga'i mkha' klong rnam par dag pa'i bdag nyid do / / b+h+rUM bi sha bi shud+d+he dz+nyA na tsakra maN+Da la hUM / ri rab kyi steng du b+h+rUM yig yongs su gyur pa las gzhal yas khang gru bzhi sgo bzhi rta babs bzhi dang bcas pa / phyi nas rim pa bzhin du dmar dkar ser ljang nag pa'i rtsig pa rim pa lnga dang ldan pa / de'i steng du rin po che'i pha gu ser po dra ba dang dra ba phyed pas brgyan pa / steng na rin po che'i mda' yab dang pu shus mdzes pa / rtsig pa'i 'gram nas 'dod yon gyi snam bu dmar pos bskor ba la 'dod yon gyi lha mo bcu gnyis kyis mchod rdzas sna tshogs thogs nas bcom ldan 'das la mchod pa / nang thod skam gyi ka ba brgyad kyis bteg cing / pad ma'i gdung bzhis mig mang ris su phub pa'i dbus phyur bur gyur pa'i steng du padma'i tog gis mdzes pa / sgo bzhi so so'i 'gram du ka ba bzhi bzhis bteg pa'i rta babs snam bu bcu gcig dang ldan pa'i rtse mor chos kyi 'khor lo / g.yas g.yon du ri dwags pho mo dang bcas pa / gzhan yang gdugs dang rgyal mtshan dang 'phan dang me tog gi phreng ba dang zla ba rlung gis bskyod pa dang / rnga yab nor bu'i yu ba can la sogs pas brgyan pa'i gzhal yas khang gi nang gi steng dang 'og gi sa gzhi thams cad shar dkar / lho ser / nub dmar / byang ljang ba / dbus dmar nag gru gsum zla gam dmar po gsum dang bcas pa / de'i phyi rol nas thod pa'i phreng ba dkar po dang gzhal yas khang gi nang thams

cad kyang thod pa skam rlon gyi rtsig pas bskor ba / gzhal yas khang gi phyi rol tu rdo rje'i ra ba dang / ye shes kyi me rab tu 'bar bas kun nas bskor ba'i pho brang chen po'i nang du 'khor lo rtsibs bzhi pa'i lte bar gru gsum dmar nag gi steng du paM padma maN+Da la / paM las sna tshogs padma'i lte bar atsan+d+ra @# / / maN+Da la / a las zla ba'i dkyil 'khor / de'i steng du ma sUr+ya maN+Da la / ma las nyi ma'i dkyil 'khor gyi steng du ru tra baM / ru tra pho mo byi chings su bsnol ba'i gdan / phyogs bzhi'i rtsibs kyi steng du ba baM / shar du dri za pho mo / ya ma baM| lhor grul bum pho mo / nA ga baM / nub tu klu pho mo / yak+Sha baM / byang du gnod sbyin pho mo byi chings su bsnol ba'i gdan / sgo bzhir zla ba'i gdan dang bcas par gyur / gdan dbus ma'i steng du rang gi sems hUM yig gi rnam par gnas pa de nyid babs pa yongs su gyur pa las hrIH dmar nag dang / maM sngon po 'od zer dpag tu med pa 'phro bar gyur par bsam ste / gzhi dus la bar do pha ma'i khu khrag gi dbus su nying mtshams sbyar ba dang chos mthun pa'o / / s+pha ra Na phaT / yi ge de gnyis las 'od zer 'phros / 'phags pa mchod / sems can gyi don byas / padma dbang chen gyi go 'phang la bkod / saM ha ra Na hUM / slar 'dus / tiTHa badzra brtan par byas / hrIH badzra kro d+ha hya gr-i wa hu lu hu lu hUM phaT / hrIH dmar po de yongs su gyur pa las rang padma dbang chen yang gsang khros pa sku mdog dmar po zhal gsum phyag drug zhabs bzhi pa / rtsa zhal dmar po / g.yas zhal dkar po / g.yon zhal ljang gu dbu gtsug na rta mgo ljang nag rngog ma dmar po / phrom phrom ser po / zhur dkar po / rta skad 'tsher zhing / zhal re re la dmar la zlum pa'i spyan gsum gsum dang ldan zhing mche ba rnon po bzhi bzhi gtsigs pa / smin ma dang sma ra dus mtha'i me ltar 'bar zhing dbu skra kham nag gyen du brdzes pa / phyag dang po gnyis kyis padma dang ban d+ha / bar pa gnyis kyis lcags kyu dang zhags pa / tha ma gnyis kyis be con dang ral gri bsnams shing / zhing chen gyi g.yang gzhi dang glang po che'i ko bas stod g.yogs pa / stag gi pags pa'i sham thabs can / thod skam lnga'i dbu rgyan dang / thod pa tshal bus dpung pa brgyan cing / thod rlom lnga bcu tshar gsum gyi do shal can / sbrul rigs bzhi dang rin po che'i rgyan gyis brgyan cing / khrag

gi thig le dang / zhag gi sor ris dang / thal chen gyi tshom bus brgyan pa / gar gyi nyams dgu dang ldan zhing / khams gsum las rnam par rgyal ba'i khyung gshog can / zhabs bzhi g.yas bskum zhing g.yon brkyang pa'i stabs kyis ye shes kyi me rab tu 'bar ba'i dbus na bzhugs pa / oM ma hA kro d+hi shwa rI hUM phaT / maM sngo nag de yongs su gyur pa las yum padma gar gyi dbang phyug ma sku mdog mthing nag zhal gcig phyag gnyis ma spyan gsum sdang mig tu lta ba / zhal rab tu bgrad cing mche ba rnam par gtsigs pa / dbu skra ral pa kham nag mun pa ltar gtibs shing / phyag g.yas dgra bgegs kyi tsit+ta thogs nas yab la 'khyud cing / g.yon thod pa khrag gis bkang ba yab kyi zhal du stob pa / thod skam lnga'i dbu rgyan dang / thod rlon lnga bcu'i do shal can / g.yon phyogs nas yab kyi sku la 'khril ba / de nas sku gsung thugs byin gyis brlab pa ni / yab yum gnyis kyi spyi bor zla ba'i steng du oM dkar po / mgrin par padma dmar po 'dab ma brgyad pa'i lte bar AH dmar po / thugs kar nyi ma'i dkyil 'khor gyi steng du hUM sngon po rnams bsams te / oM AH hUM zhes brjod do / / de nas ye @# / / shes lnga'i bdag nyid can gyi he ru ka lngas dbang bskur ba ni / rang gi spyi bor thod pa'i khang bu lnga'i nang du spyi gtsug tu hUM sngon po / mtshog steng du oM dkar po / rna ltag g.yas su swA ser po / ltag par AH dmar po / rna ltag g.yon du hA ljang khu / de rnams yongs su gyur pa las hUM badzra he ru ka a b+hi Shiny+tsa hUM zhes brjod pas badzra he ru ka sngon po rdo rje dang dril bu 'dzin pa / bud+d+ha he ru ka dkar po 'khor lo dang dril bu 'dzin pa / rat+na he ru ka ser po rin po che dang dril bu 'dzin pa / padma he ru ka dmar po padma dang dril bu 'dzin pa / karma he ru ka ljang gu ral gri dang dril bu 'dzin pa / thams cad kyang phyag rgya drug gi rgyas btab cing / dur khrod kyi chas brgyad dang ldan pas dbu brgyan par gyur par bsam mo / / gnyis pa ni yab kyi gsang gnas mi dmigs pa'i ngang las hUM las byung ba'i rdo rje sngon po rtse lnga pa bu ga phaT kyis bkag pa / yum gyi gsang gnas mi dmigs pa'i ngang las / AH las byung ba'i padma dmar po 'dab ma brgyad pa bu ga phaT kyis bkag pa / yab yum snyoms par zhugs pa'i dga' ba'i sgras sangs rgyas thams cad spyan drangs pa yab kyi zhal du zhugs / thugs kar 'od

du zhu ba rdo rje'i lam nas yum gyi padmar babs pa'i byang chub kyi sems kyi thig le de nyid hUM hUM hUM hUM dzaH hUM baM hoH ste yi ge brgyad po 'od zer gyi phung po dang bcas par gyur / de rnams yum gyi padma las spros te phyogs bzhi'i rtsibs kyi gdan gyi steng dang / sgo bzhi'i nang gi gdan gyi steng du 'khod pa yongs su gyur pa las sprul pa'i khro bo bzhi dang sgo ma bzhir gyur pa ni / badzra kro d+ha shwa ra hUM phaT / shar rtsibs kyi gdan gyi steng du rdo rje dbang chen sku mdog dkar po zhal gcig phyag gnyis kyi phyag g.yas rdo rje dang g.yon dbyug tho bsnams pa / rat+na kro d+ha shwa ra hUM phaT / lho rtsibs kyi gdan gyi steng du rin chen dbang chen sku mdog sngon po g.yas rin po che dang g.yon lcags kyu 'dzin pa / padma kro d+ha shwa ra hUM phaT / nub rtsibs kyi gdan gyi steng du padma dbang chen sku mdog dmar po g.yas padma dang g.yon zhags pa 'dzin pa / karma kro d+ha shwa ra hUM phaT / byang rtsibs kyi gdan gyi steng du las kyi dbang chen sku mdog ljang gu g.yas ral gri dang g.yon rtse gsum bsnams pa / thams cad kyang zhal so so la dmar la zlum pa'i spyan gsum gsum dang ldan zhing / zhal rab tu gdangs nas mche ba rnam par gtsigs pa / dbu skra kham ser gyen du brdzes pa la sbrul gyis bcings shing dpal gyi chas brgyad dang ldan pa / zhabs g.yas bskum zhing g.yon brkyang pa'i gar stabs kyis ye shes kyi me rab tu 'bar ba'i klong dkyil na bzhugs par gyur / oM badzra s+pho Ta baM aM gu sha dzaH shar sgor lcags kyu ma dkar mo khrag gi ral pa can / zhal gcig phyag gnyis kyi phyag g.yas lcags kyu 'dzin pa / oM badzra pA sha hUM / lho sgor zhags pa ma ser mo g.yu'i ral pa can g.yas zhags pa 'dzin pa / oM badzra s+pho Ta baM / nub sgor lcags sgrog ma dmar mo mthing gi ral pa can g.yas lcags sgrog 'dzin pa / oM badzra g+haN+Da hoH byang sgor dril bu ma ljang gu gser gyi ral pa can g.yas dril bu 'dzin pa / thams cad kyang g.yon snying 'dzin cing mche ba rnam par gtsigs pa'i @# / / zhal can / dur khrod kyi chas brgyad kyis brgyan cing / zhabs g.yas bskum zhing g.yon brkyang ba'i stabs kyis ye shes kyi me rab tu 'bar ba'i dbus na bzhugs par bsams la / hUM| chos nyid nam mkha'i klong yangs nas / / chos rnams sna tshogs rang shar ba / / rang bzhin med de chu zla 'dra / / thugs rje chen pos kun la khyab / / snying po ye shes hUM gi dbyibs / / chen po lnga yi snying po la / /

'byung ba lnga yi dwangs ma chags / / ye shes 'bar ba'i gzhal yas khang / / chos kyi dbyings kyi gnas chen po / / 'khor lo dbang chen pho brang ldan / / phyi nang med par yongs su gsal / / gdan gding sku bskyed dbang bskur zhing / / byin gyis brlab pa rab tu bya / / yab yum gnyis med sbyor ba las / / sprul pa'i dkyil 'khor rab tu ston / / zhes brjod la / rten brten pa'i dkyil 'khor thams cad bde stong dbyer med kyi ye shes kyi gzung rnam / snang stong tshogs pa nam mkha'i 'ja' tshon lta bur yid ngor gsal btab la 'char du gzhug go / gsum pa ni / lha thams cad kyi spyi bor oM dkar po / mgrin par AH dmar po / thugs kar hUM sngon po / bdag nyid kyi thugs ka'i hrIH las 'od zer 'phros pas 'og min gyi gnas nas yang gsang khros pa khrag 'thung lha dgu'i dkyil 'khor skad cig gis spyan drangs / badzra sa ma ya hUM dzaH hUM| chos kyi dbyings nas sku bzhengs pa / / dbang chen khros pa'i rgyal po bzhengs / / dbus nyid ye shes gzhal yas nas / / padma rta mchog gshegs su gsol / / yum chen khro mo gshegs su gsol / phyogs bzhi 'khor lo'i rtsibs steng nas / / sprul pa'i khro bo gshegs su gsol / / sgo bzhi gnas kyi gzhal yas nas / / sgo ma rnam bzhi gshegs su gsol / / e hye hi b+hag wan ma hA kA ru Ni ka badzra d+hA tu sa pa ri wA ra dzaH hUM baM hoH dam tshig pa so so dang gnyis su med par gyur / sa ma ya hoH hUM| dam tshig chen po'i dkyil 'khor 'dir / / ye shes dbang chen dkyil 'khor mchog / pho brang dam tshig dkyil 'khor 'dir / / dgyes bzhin brtan par bzhugs su gsol / / sa ma ya stwaM / zhes ye shes pa spyan drangs / dam tshig pa dang gnyis su med par bstim / bzhugs su gsol nas dkyil 'khor gyi lha la phyag 'tshal ba ni / hUM| dpal chen khro bo mi bzad pa / / zhes pa nas / sgo srung bzhi la phyag 'tshal lo / / zhes pa'i bar brjod la / a ti pu hoH pra ti dza hoH zhes phyag bya / bzhi pa la / mchod bstod bzlas pa dang bcas pa ji ltar bya ba'i tshul dang / dngos grub blang ba'i tshul dang / longs spyod tshogs kyi mchod pa bya ba'i tshul gsum las / dang po la mchod bstod bzlas pa gsum gyi / mchod pa la yang phyi nang gi mchod pa gnyis las / phyi'i mchod pa ni / rang gi snying ga'i sa bon las byung ba'i lha mo mchod rdzas thogs pa dpag tu med pas mchod par bsams la / hUM| gnyis med bde chen

dbyings las byung / / zag med bde ster mchod yon 'di / / padma dbang chen dkyil 'khor la / / bdag nyid dad pas 'bul lags kyi / / thugs rjes dgongs la bzhes su gsol / / oM na maH sarba ta thA ga ta ar+g+haM pU dza me g+ha sa mu dra s+pha ra Na sa ma ya shri ye hUM / de bzhin du mchod yon gyi gnas su zhabs bsil dang / ar+g+haM gyi gnas su pA dyaM sogs bcug ste / shap+ta 'i bar du sbyar te dbul / gnyis pa nang gi mchod pa la bdud rtsi @# / / sman gyi mchod pa / gsang ba rak+ta'i mchod pa / zab pa sbyor sgrol gyi mchod pa / dam rdzas gtor ma'i mchod pa / dug lnga dam rdzas kyi mchod pa / 'dod yon lnga'i mchod pa rnams las / bdud rtsi sman gyi mchod pa ni / mchod pa'i lha mo nam mkha'i khams gang ba rnams kyis thod pa'i nang nas zag med kyi bdud rtsis mchod par / bsams la / thog mar rtsa brgyud kyi bla ma rnams la 'bul ba ni / hUM / rang byung gdod nas rnam par dag / rtsa brgyad stong las sbyar ba'i sman / / ye shes lnga rdzogs grub pa'i rdzas / / 'chi med bdud rtsi ra sa yin / / dam rdzas mchog gi mchod pa 'di / / rtsa brgyud bla ma'i tshogs rnams la / / bdag gis dad pas 'bul lags kyi / / bzhes te 'phrul gyi dngos grub stsol / / chos sku snang ba mtha' yas zhal du sarba pany+tsa a mr-i ta la kha raM khA hi / longs sku padma dbang chen zhal du sarba pany+tsa a mr-i ta la kha raM khA hi / sprul sku padma 'byung gnas zhal du sarba pany+tsa a mr-i ta la kha raM khA hi / dpal ldan grub thob mdar char zhal du X / bo dong pa brtson 'grus rdo rje'i zhal du X / gnyan chen bsod nams brtan pa'i zhal X / mkhan chen chos rgyal chen po'i zhal X / kun mkhyen dpal ldan seng ge'i X / mkhas grub rin chen dpal bzang X / gru ston kun dga' bzang po'i X / dran mchog don yod rgyal mtshan zhal du X / grub mchog kun dga' rgyal mtshan zhal du X / drin can rtsa ba'i bla ma'i zhal du sarba pany+tsa a mr-i ta la kha raM khA hi / zhes lag pa g.yon pa'i mtheb srin gyis bdud rtsi smin phrag gi thad nas gtor la mchod / de nas dkyil 'khor gyi lha rnams la 'bul ba ni / bdud rtsi snying ga'i thad nas 'thor zhing / hUM| rang byung gdod nas rnam par dag / khro rgyal padma dbang chen la / / X hriH badzra kro d+ha ha ya grI wa sarba pany+tsa a mr-i ta la kha raM khA hi / yum chen padma gar dbang la / /

X ma hA kro d+hi shwa rI sarba pany+tsa a mr-i ta la kha raM khA hi / sprul pa'i khro bo bzhi rnams la / / X badzra kro d+ha shwa ra sogs / sgo srung chen mo bzhi rnams la / / bdag gis dad pas 'bul lags kyi / / bzhes nas 'phrul gyi dngos grub stsol / / badzra aM ku sha dzaH sogs kyi mthar / sarba pany+tsa a mr-i ta la kha raM khA hi / de nas rang nyid kyis dngos grub kyi tshul du bdud rtsi blang ba ni / dkyil 'khor pa'i lha rnams kyi gnas gsum nas oM AH hUM gi yi ge gsum byung ba 'od dkar dmar mthing gsum gyi rnam par zhu bas bdud rtsi la thim pa mtheb srin gyis rang gi lce thog tu bzhag pas dkyil 'khor pa'i lha thams cad kyi sku gsung thugs kyi dngos grub thob par bsams la / hUM| ye shes khro bo dbang chen gyi / / sku gsung thugs kyi dngos grub mchog / rnal 'byor lus ngag yid la thim / / gnyis med gyur nas brtan pa che / / oM AH hUM kA ya wa ka tsit+ta sid+d+hi pha la ya zhes brjod / slar yang / hUM| rang byung rnam dag grub sman 'di / / rnal 'byor bdag cag gus pa yis / / padma dbang chen dkyil 'khor la / / mchod par 'bul lo kha raM khA hi / zhes pas dkyil 'khor pa'i lha la sman phud rkyang pa nyid kyang dbul / gsang ba rak+ta'i mchod pa ni / yangs shing rgya che ba'i thod pa'i nang rnams nas rak+ta'i rgya mtsho phul bar bsam zhing / rak+ta dmar gyi mchod pa 'di / / padma dbang chen dkyil 'khor la / mchod par 'bul lo kha raM khA hi / hrIH badzra kro d+ha ha ya grI wa @# / / sa pa ri wA ra ma hA rak+ta la kha raM khA hi / zab pa sbyor sgrol gyi mchod pa la / thog mar sbyor ba'i mchod pa ni / 'dod yon gyi lha mo gzugs dang lang tsho phun sum tshogs pa nam mkha'i khams gang ba dkyil 'khor ba'i lha rnams la phul bas de rnams dang snyoms par zhugs pa las bde stong dbyer med kyi ting nge 'dzin gyis dgyes pa skyed par bsams te / gsang ba thabs dang shes rab las / / padma nor bu mnyam sbyor bas / / dgyes pa chen po'i bde chen dang / / byang chub sems kyi mchod pa 'di / / padma dbang chen dkyil 'khor la / / mchod par 'bul lo bzhes su gsol / / zhes brjod / sgrol ba'i mchod pa ni / rang gi thugs ka'i sa bon gyi 'od zer gyis dgra bgegs thams cad mdun du bkug par gyur / hUM| sprul pa'i khro bo 'bar ba yis / / 'khor ba'i nyon mongs rgya dral nas / / dug lnga dbyings su bsgral bar bya

/ / rang gi thugs ka'i sa bon gyi 'od zer las byung ba'i las byed kyi khro bo rnams kyis dgra bgegs rnams skad cig gis bsgral bar gyur / a mu ka mA ra ya phaT / ces brjod la dgra bgegs kyi sha khrag gi phung po dkyil 'khor ba'i lha rnams kyis gsol bar bsams la / hUM| zhing gyur thams cad rang bzhin bsgral / / sha khrag srog dbugs mchod pa 'di / / padma dbang chen dkyil 'khor la / / mchod par 'bul lo bzhes su gsol / / hrIH padma ta krid ha ya grI wa sarba big+h+nAn sha truM kha raM khA hi / zhes dbul / dam rdzas gtor ma'i mchod pa ni / gtor ma ngo bo zag pa med pa'i ye shes kyi bdud rtsi la rnam pa dgra bgegs bsgral ba'i sha khrag gi phung po / byed las zag pa med pa'i bde ba khyad par can ster bar sngar bshad pa ltar byin gyis brlabs nas / dkyil 'khor pa'i lha thams cad kyi ljags hUM las skyes pa'i rdo rje rtse gcig pa dmar po 'od zer gyi sbu gu can du gyur pas gtor ma'i bcud thams cad drangs te gsol bar bsam zhing / khyad par 'dod yon mchod pa'i mchog / sha khrag rkang rus gtor ma yis / / khro rgyal dbang chen thugs dam bskang / / yum chen khro mo'i thugs dam bskang / / sprul pa'i khro bo'i thugs dam bskang / / sgo ma bzhi yi thugs dam bskang / / zhes brjod la / hrIH badzra kro d+ha sogs sngags rnams kyi mthar ma hA ba liM ta la kha raM khA hi zhes btags la dbul / 'dod yon drug gi mchod pa ni / 'dod yon gyi lha mo drug gis dkyil 'khor gyi lha la mchod par bsams la / gzugs kyi lha mo sku mdog dkar / / gzugs kyi longs spyod sna tshogs 'dzin / / dbang chen khro bo'i spyan la 'bul / / bzhes nas dngos grub stsal du gsol / / sgra yi lha mo sku mdog sngo / / sgra yi longs spyod sna tshogs 'dzin / / dbang chen khro bo'i snyan la 'bul / / X dri yi X / / ser X / / shangs la X / / ro yi X / / dmar X / / ljags X / / reg bya'i lha mo sku mdog ljang / / reg bya'i X / / dbang chen khro bo'i sku la 'bul / / X chos dbyings lha mo sku mdog dkar / / phyag na chos kyi 'byung gnas 'dzin / / dbang chen khro bo'i thugs la 'bul / / bzhes nas dngos grub stsal du gsol / / dug lnga dam rdzas kyi mchod pa ni / dgra bgegs kyi sha khrag rus pa nang khrol mkhris pa dang bcas pa phul bas dug alnga'i dri ma thams cad dag nas sku gsung thugs yon tan @# / / phrin

las dang bcas pa'i dngos grub thob par bsams la / hUM| sha khrag rus pa nang khrol mkhris / / <ALLO>dod chags zhe sdang gti mug dang / / nga rgyal phrag dog mchod par 'bul / / sku gsung thugs dang yon tan dang / / phrin las dngos por bzhes su gsol / / zhes 'bul / de nas bstod pa bya ba ni / rol mo dbyangs dang bcas pas / hrIH rang bzhin chos kyi sku las rang byung ba / / dmar nag gru gsum dbang gi dkyil 'khor nas / / padma 'khyil ba dbang chen khro bo'i sku / / thugs rje thabs kyis sprul skur bzhengs su gsol / / bdud pho bdud mo byi chings bsnol ba'i khri / / chags med padma nyi zla'i gdan steng na / / dus gsum dbang sgyur ye shes lha yi lha / / dbang chen phrag thung ha ya grI ba'i sku / / sku mdog dmar nag zhal gsum phyag drug pa / / zhabs bzhi brkyang bskum rngam 'gying brjid pa'i sku / / spyan gsum zhal bgrad dbang gi mche ba gtsigs / / smin ma smra ra ag tshom me ltar 'bar / / dbu skra kham nag ral pa gyen du 'bar / / spyi gtsug rta mgo ljang gu zil gnon rngam / / rngog ma dmar po dbang gi rta skad 'tsher / / g.yas dkar g.yon ljang dbus dmar rngam sgra sgrog / sku stod zhing lpags glang chen ko rlon gsol / / sku smad stag gi sham thabs bdud dpung 'dul / / thod rlon tshar gsum phreng bas rgyan du mdzes / / sbrul chen rigs bzhis sku brgyan phyag zhabs spras / / dang po padma ban d+has dbang du sdud / / bar pa lcags kyu zhags pas dmigs pa 'gugs / / tha ma be con ral gris dgra bgegs sgrol / / dbang drag me dpung klong dkyil rin chen spras / / sku la dur khrod chas brgyad rdzogs par ldan / / dbang chen gdug pa'i spyan rtsa zlog pa yis / / snang srid dregs pa thams cad dbang du sdud / / shangs nas rlung nag 'tshub pa'i bskal pa 'byung / / snang srid kun 'thor mthu chen drag rtsal 'dul / / snyan nas bskal pa'i 'brug stong di ri ri / / srid pa'i che btsan thams cad zil gyis gnon / / tshems las drag po'i thog chen phab pa yis / / sdang dgra gnod bgegs thal ba'i rdul du rlogs / / zhal nas rak+ta'i rgya mtsho 'khrug cing 'khyil / / bstan pa bshig pa'i dgra la skyi thang phob / / khro rgyal dbang gi rta skad tsher re re / / thugs rjes dbang chen che btsan dbang du sdud / / padma dbang chen khrag 'thung mi bzad pa / / khyod kyi dbang drag phrin las dus la bab / / sdang dgra gnod byed thal ba rdul du rlogs / / hrIH khro

rgyal dbang chen sku yi g.yon phyogs na / / khro mo padma gar gyi dbang phyug ma / / sku mdog mthing nag zhal gcig phyag gnyis ma / / spyan gsum zhal bgrad dbang gi mche ba gtsigs / / dbu skra ral pa nag po mun ltar gtibs / / sku la dur khrod chas brgyad legs par brgyan / / phyag g.yas tsit+ta thogs nas yab la 'khyud / / phyag g.yon dung chen dmar 'khyil gtso la stob / / khro mo kun gyi dbang phyug chen mo khyod / / rngam pa'i nga ros thams cad zil gyis gnon / / spyan nas khrag 'dzag zhal nas mi ro 'drul / / snyan nas 'brug sgrog shangs nas rlung nag 'tshub / / khyod kyi dbang drag phrin las dus la bab / / sdang dgra gnod byed thal ba rdul du rlogs / / hrIH yab yum thabs dang shes rab @# / / rol pa las / / thugs kyi sprul pa dbang chen khro bo'i sku / / shar phyogs 'khor lo 'bar ba'i rtsibs steng na / / dri za pho mo bsnol ba'i gdan steng na / / rdo rje dbang chen dkar po khro bo'i sku / / zhal gcig phyag gnyis dur khrod chas brgyad rdzogs / / spyan gsum zhal bgrad mche gtsigs mi ro za / / dbu skra kham nag gyen brdzes sbrul gyis bcings / / phyag g.yas rdo rjes dgra bgegs mgo lus gshog / phyag g.yon dbyug thos myos shing brgyal bar byed / / me dpung klong na 'gying zhing gar stabs tshul / / rngam pa'i nga ro 'brug stong di ri ri / / thugs kyi sprul pas stong gsum khyab par byed / / khyod kyi dbang drag phrin las dus la bab / / sdang dgra gnod byed thal ba rdul du rlogs / / hrIH yab yum thabs dang shes rab rol pa las / / thugs kyi X / / lho phyogs X / / grul bum X / / rin chen dbang chen mthing nag khro bo'i sku / / zhal gcig phyag gnyis dur khrod chas brgyad rdzogs / / spyan gsum X / / dbu skra X / / phyag g.yas rin chen dbyu gus dgos 'dod skong / / phyag g.yon lcags kyus bla 'gugs tsit+ta 'byin / / me dpung la sogs pa'i tshig 'og ma kun la 'gre / de nas rkang pa dang po gnyis 'dra ba la / nub phyogs X / / klu dbang X / / padma dbang chen dmar smug X / / rkang pa gsum pa 'gre / phyag g.yas padmas che btsan dbang du sdud / / phyag g.yon zhags pas lus dang yan lag 'ching / / byang phyogs X / / gnod sbyin X / / phrin las dbang chen ljang dmar X / / phyag g.yas ral gris rtsa dang srog dbugs gcod / / phyag g.yon kha TwAM rtse gsum dug gsum sgrol / / hrIH shar phyogs dung

gi sgo khyud nas / / bud med dkar mo 'jigs tshul can / / khrag gi ral pa shar ra ra / / phyag na lcags kyus dgra snying 'byin / / rings par khug cig aM ku sha / lho phyogs gser X / / ser mo X / / g.yu yi ral pa shar ra ra / / phyag na zhags pas bla tshe 'gugs / / chings shig sdoms shig pA sha hUM / / nub phyogs zangs kyi sgo khyud nas / / dmar mo X / / mthing gi X / / phyag na lcags sgrog tshe srog bstim / / rten la bstim zhig s+pho Ta baM / / byang phyogs g.yu yi sgo khyud nas / / ljang gu X / / phyag na dril bus brgyal bar byed / / myos par gyis shig g+haN+Da hoH / / zhes bstod cing bskul lo / / 'dir 'phro nyid du gying lnga gza' gdong gi skul gsungs pa ni 'og nyid du bris pa'o / / bzlas pa bya ba'i tshul ni / rang gtso bo'i nga rgyal la gnas pa'i thugs kar padma dmar po 'dab ma brgyad pa'i lte bar hrIH dmar po 'dab ma la sngags kyis bskor ba de las 'od zer dus mtha'i me lta bu drag cing rtsub la 'bar zhing 'khyil ba phyogs bcur 'phros pas de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad la phyi nang gsang gsum gyi mchod pa phul / sku gsung thugs kyi dngos grub thams cad bsdus nas rang la thim / sems can thams cad kyi sdig sgrib sbyangs / dpal rta mgrin gyi go 'phang la bkod / bar du gcod pa'i dgra bgegs thams cad bya sgro mes bsregs pa bzhin du thal ba'i rdul phran tsam yang ma lus par bsregs par bsams la / / hrIH badzra kro d+ha ha ya grI wa hu lu hu lu hUM phaT / ces 'dzab ci nus bzla / yum dang 'khor rnams kyi bzlas pa bya tshul ni / lha rang rang gi thugs kar padma 'dab ma brgyad pa'i lte bar @# / / rang rang gi sngags kyis bskor ba la dmigs pa sngar bzhin gtad la / oM ma hA kro d+hi shwa rI hUM phaT / yum gyi dang / oM badzra kro d+ha shwa ra hUM phaT / oM rat+na kro d+ha shwa ra hUM phaT / oM padma kro d+ha shwa ra hUM phaT / oM karma kro d+ha shwa ra hUM phaT / ces khro bo bzhi dang / oM badzra aM ku sha dzaH oM badzra pA sha hUM / oM badzra s+pho Ta baM / oM badzra g+haN+Da ho / zhes sgo ma bzhi'i sngags rnams bzla'o / / bzlas pa'i mthar yi ge brgya pas lhag chad kha bkang zhing / mchod pa bsdus pa nang mchod sman rag dang bcas pas kyang mchod la / padma rigs kyi khro rgyal mchog / dbang chen padma he ru ka / mi bzad khro bo rta mchog dpal / / dbang

drag stobs chen rngam brjid gtum / / sku mdog dmar nag brjid cing 'gying / / dbu gsum rnam thar gsum yang ston / / phyag drug rgyud drug rtsad nas gcod / / zhabs bzhis 'khor ba'i chos bzhi sgrol / / dur khrod chas brgyad sku la rdzogs / / rta mgo ljang gu rta skad 'tsher / / me dpung 'bar ba'i klong na bzhugs / / rngam pa'i nga ro 'brug stong sgrog / dregs pa pho mo dbang du sdud / / dbang chen sku la phyag 'tshal lo / / zhes 'dzab bstod bya / spros pa la mi dga' na gong du'ang bstod pa 'di nyid bya / de ltar bsnyen pa byas pa las 'grub pa'i mtshan ma ni / rgyud las / sku nyid dngos su mthong ba 'am / / slob dpon nyi zla mgo la 'char / / rdzas la me 'bar 'od 'phro zhing / / sgrub khang g.yo 'gyur sgra chen 'byung / / padma'i sdong por 'dug pa dang / / snang srid me tog padmas khengs / / sangs rgyas nyag gcig chos nyan pa / / rmi lam mngon sum phyi nang gsang / / mthong nas dngos grub dam rdzas blang / / drag po'i las rnams kun la sbyar / / zhes gsungs pas / mtshan ma de dag gang yang rung ba rnyed nas las sbyor la 'jug gi gzhan du mi rung ste / mtshan ma ma mthong las rtsom pa / / 'ja' tshon sbar zin don med yin / / zhes gsungs pa ltar ro / / gnyis pa dngos grub blang ba'i tshul ni / hUMH khro rgyal rngam chen rta mchog dpal / / dpal gyi sku gsung thugs mchog las / / mchog gi dngos grub ye shes dbyig / dus 'dir bdag la stsal du gsol / / zhes pas dngos grub blang / dus gsum longs spyod tshogs kyi mchod pa bya ba'i tshul ni / tshogs kyi yo byad rnams bsangs sbyangs byin gyis brlab pa nang mchod dang gtor ma ltar byas la / mgron spyan drangs pa ni / rang gi thugs ka'i sa bon las 'od zer 'phros pas / rang bzhin gyi gnas nas yang gsang khros pa lha dgu'i dkyil 'khor la rtsa brgyud kyi bla ma / yi dam dkyil 'khor gyi lha tshogs / gnas gsum mkha' 'gro / chos skyong srung ma / yul lha gzhi bdag gi tshogs dang bcas pas bskor ba skad cig gis spyan drangs / hUM / rang bzhin rnam dag ngang nyid las / sprul pa'i khro bo mi bzad pa / / padma dbang chen dkyil 'khor lha / / longs spyod tshogs la gshegs su gsol / / e hye hi b+ha ga wan mahA kA ru Ni ka badzra d+hA tu sa pa ri wA ra badzra sa ma ya dzaH zhes spyan drangs la mdun gyi nam mkhar bzhugs par bsams te / padma ka ma la ye stwaM / zhes gdan phul / de

nas tshogs kyi mchod pa bya ba la gsum las / dang po bstod de 'bul ba ni / 'dod yon gyi lha mo rnams kyis spyan drangs pa'i ye shes pa'i mgron rnams la 'dod pa'i yon tan lnga dang ldan pa'i tshogs kyi mchod pa nam mkha'i khams gang bas mchod par gyur par bsams la / hUMH mdzes sdug gzugs kyi mchod pa 'di / / padma dbang chen spyan la @# / / 'bul / / spyan gyi thugs dam skongs gyur cig / gzugs kyi mchod pa bzhes su gsol / / snyan pa sgra yi mchod pa 'di / / padma dbang chen snyan la 'bul / / snyan gyi thugs dam skongs gyur cig / sgra yi mchod pa bzhes su gsol / / dri zhim ngad kyi mchod pa 'di / / padma dbang chen shangs la 'bul / / shangs kyi thugs dam skongs gyur cig / dri yi mchod pa bzhes su gsol / / zhal zas ro yi mchod pa 'di / / padma dbang chen ljags la 'bul / / ljags kyi thugs dam skongs gyur cig / ro yi mchod pa bzhes su gsol / / 'jam pa reg bya'i mchod pa 'di / / padma dbang chen sku la 'bul / / sku yi thugs dam skongs gyur cig / reg bya'i mchod pa bzhes su gsol / / zhes dbul / gnyis pa bshags te 'bul ba ni / sngar ltar tshogs kyi mchod pa phul nas / rang gi dam tshig nyams chag thams cad dag par bsams te / hUM / bdag cag ma rig nyon mongs sems can gyi / / zhes sogs kyis bshags pa byas pas nyams chag ma lus par dag par bsam mo / / gsum pa bstabs te 'bul ba ni / rang gi thugs ka'i sa bon gyi 'od zer gyis dgra bgegs thams cad mdun du bkug par gyur / hUM / sprul pa'i khro bo 'bar ba yis / / 'khor ba'i nyon mongs rgya dral nas / / dug lnga dbyings su bsgral bar bya / / rang gi thugs ka'i sa bon gyi 'od zer las byung ba'i las byed kyi khro bo phur bu me 'bar ba thogs pa rnams kyis dgra bgegs rnams skad cig gis bsgral bar gyur / a mu ka mA ra ya phaT / ces brjod la tshogs de nyid dgra bgegs bsgral ba'i sha khrag gi phung por bsams la / hUMH zhing gyur thams cad dbyings su bsgral / / sha khrag srog dbugs mchod pa 'di / / padma dbang chen dkyil 'khor la / / mchod par 'bul lo bzhes su gsol / / hrIH padmAn+ta krita hya gr-i wa sa pa ri wA ra sarba big+h+nAn sha truM ga na tsakra pU dza la kha raM khA hi / / zhes zhal du bstabs pas dgra bgegs kyi sha khrag ma lus par gsol bas rgyud bde ba chen pos tshim par bsam mo / / de nas tshogs la sgrub pa po

rnams longs spyod pa'i tshul ni / las kyi rdo rjes / gzigs shig mdzes ldan dam pa'i chos / / 'di la the tshom byar mi rung / / bram ze khyi dang gdol pa phag / rang bzhin gcig tu dgongs te rol / / zhes brjod la drang zhing / rnal 'byor pa rnams kyis / bde bar gshegs pa'i chos kyi mchog / 'dod chags dri ma med pa 'di / / gzung 'dzin rnam par spangs pa yi / / de bzhin nyid la bdag phyag 'tshal / / a la la hoH zhes blangs te / lha'i rnal 'byor gyi ngang nas nang gi sbyin sreg gi tshul du longs spyad / de nas tshogs lhag ma rnams bsdus pa la rang gi ya rkan 'od dpag med dang / ma rkan gos dkar mor bsams te / de gnyis snyoms par zhugs pa'i byang chub kyi sems kyis gtor bas bdud rtsi'i rgya mtsho chen por gyur par bsams te / nang mchod kyi kha phrus bran la / hrIH dmar nag gru gsum dbang gi dkyil 'khor nas / / bcom ldan padma dbang chen dang / / yum chen gar gyi dbang phyug ma / / lhag ma'i tshogs kyis bskor ba ni / / bde gshegs khyung dang gza' gdong dang / / ma mo sde brgyad 'khor dang bcas / / bod khams skyong ba'i bstan ma sogs / / lhag ma'i mchod pa 'di bzhes la / / rnal 'byor bcol ba'i phrin las mdzod / / lhag ma'i tshogs la kha raM khA hi / / zhes pas @# / / tshogs kyi lhag ma bsngo / tha mar bya ba'i rim pa la / bka' sdod la gtor ma 'bul ba / gtor ma phyi rol tu gshegs shing bstan ma bskyang ba / nye bar bsdu zhing bzod par gsol nas shis brjod pa'i tshul lo / / dang po la chos skyong lcam sring la gtor ma 'bul tshul ni / mchod gtor rnams phyag len bzhin du bshams te byin gyis brlabs la / chos skyong 'khor bcas skyed pa ni / swab+hA wa sa stong par sbyangs / stong pa'i ngang las rang gi mdun du rta khrag dang mi khrag gi rgya mtsho chen po dmar la dwangs pa rba klong gru gsum bsnol mar 'khrug pa'i dbus su zangs kyi ri gru bzhi pa'i steng du padma nyi ma rta ro mi ro brtsegs pa'i gdan la / praM dang zangs gri las skyes pa'i gnod sbyin chen po sku mdog dmar po / zhal gcig phyag gnyis pa / phyag g.yas 'bar ba dang bcas pa'i zangs kyi ral gri nam mkha' la 'phyar bas dam nyams kyi srog rtsa gcod cing / g.yon mda' gzhu dang dgra bgegs kyi glo snying thugs kar 'dzin pa'i mchan khung g.yon na bse'i ru mtshon dmar po bsnams pa / zhal rab tu gdangs shing mche ba rnon po bzhi gtsigs nas ljags rnam par bskyod pa / spyan gsum dang ldan zhing

khro gnyer shin tu bsdus pa / smin ma dang sma ra dus mtha'i me ltar rab tu 'bar zhing dbu skra kham ser ltag par bcings pa / mi mgo skam po lnga'i dbu rgyan dang / khrag 'dzag pa'i mgo bo rlon pa lnga bcu'i do shal can / sku la zangs kyi beg rtse dang dar gyi ral gu dmar pos brgyan cing / zhabs la sag lham dmar po gsol ba / sgeg pa dpa' ba mi sdug pa'i gzugs can g.yas bskum zhing g.yon brkyang pa'i gar stabs gyis ye shes kyi me 'bar ba'i klong dkyil na bzhugs pa / de'i g.yon du maM las rig pa'i lha mo gdong dmar ma sku mdog sngo nag gdong pa bse / so dung / smin ma g.yu / me'i ral pa la mchong dang mu men gyis brgyan cing / gser gyi rna rgyan 'phyang ba / gcer mo spyan dang zhal bgrad cing / g.yas zangs kyi ral gri dgra la 'phyar zhing / g.yon lcags kyi phur bu bgegs la 'debs pa / dred mo mi zan la zhon pa / gtso bo'i g.yas su praM las las mkhan srog bdag dmar po zhal gcig phyag gnyis g.yas mdung dmar 'phyar zhing g.yon btsan gyi zhags pa dgra la 'debs pa / bse khrab dang bse rmog gyon zhing lce spyang smyon pa la zhon pa / mtshan mo rgyu zhing dgra bgegs la 'o dod 'bod pa / gtso 'khor gsum gyi shar du mi dmar khra ma / lhor ri tsi mi dmar / nub tu kro d+hi mi dmar / byang du srog bdag ko shang / shar lhor aM kri mi dmar / lho nub tu ro kri mi dmar / nub byang tu haM shang mi dmar / byang shar du srog bdag thal ba ste / gri thogs brgyad dang bshan pa nyi shu rtsa gcig po thams cad kyang sku mdog dmar po / g.yas zangs kyi ral gri 'phyar zhing / g.yon la la rgyu ma'i lag dog byed pa / la la glo snying mchin pa 'brad pa / la la snying khrag klad pa bldag pa / la la sha khrag spar gyis 'debs pa / la la rus pa rkang mar 'cha' ba / la la pags pa dmar bshus byed pa / la la sha gdan dmar po 'dings pa / thams cad kyang dgra bo'i srog len pa / mi lpags kyi g.yang gzhi dang ba glang gi ko ba rlon pa gyon pa / gzhan yang btsan dmar stong / bdud @# / / dang gnod sbyin srin po sum stong / ma mo 'bum sde / the'u rang stong la sogs pa dam can rgya mtsho'i dmag tshogs dpag tu med pas bskor ba'i gtso 'khor thams cad kyi spyi bor oM / mgrin par AH thugs kar hUM / rang gi thugs ka'i hUM las 'od zer 'phros pas byang shar ma ru tse'i dur khrod brag dmar po mchong lding gi pho brang nas gnod sbyin dregs pa

lcam sring 'khor dang bcas pa skad cig gis spyan drangs / kyai| yul gcig mya ngam 'das pa bdun gyi pha rol na| |mda' na khrag mtsho phu na zangs brag brtsegs / / mi ro rta ro mang po gcal du bkram / / mi khrag rta khrag du ma mtsho ru 'khyil / / 'khor yug zangs ri'i 'phreng bas kun nas bskor / / bse mkhar smug po mchong gi ba gam can / / thod pa brtsegs pa'i gzhal yas chen po nas / / chos skyong dregs pa lcam sring gshegs su gsol / / 'khor tshogs bshan pa'i tshogs kyang gshegs su gsol / / zhing bcu'i dam nyams dgra bo gdul ba dang / / rnal 'byor bdag gis las bcol bsgrub pa'i phyir / / da lta nyid du gnas 'dir gshegs su gsol / / da lta nyid du gnas 'dir gshegs nas kyang / / rings pa'i tshul gyis mchod gtor 'di bzhes la / / nag po'i phyogs dang gang la dmigs pa yi / / gnod byed dgra bgegs thal ba'i rdul du rlogs / / rak+mo pra Na At+ma sa pa ri wA ra a kar+Sha ya dzaH dzaH hUM baM hoH dam tshig pa dang gnyis su med par gyur / padma ka ma la ye stwaM / chos nyid zhi ba'i ngang las ma g.yos kyang / / ma rungs gdul phyir drag po'i skur bstan nas / / mthu stobs phun tshogs bstan ba srung mdzad pa'i / / sgrol gying bshan pa dmar po la phyag 'tshal / / bka' yi 'khor gnas ye shes srung ma'i tshogs / / rnal 'byor 'dod pa'i bde ster gsang ba'i yum / / las byed bshan pa gtum po sde lnga dang / / ma mo the rang tshogs la gus pas 'dud / / ces phyag bya / oM rak+mo pra Na At+ma sa pa ri wA ra ar+g+haM pra tI ts+tsha ye swA hA / de bzhin du shap+ta 'i bar du sbyar la mchod pa dbul / oM AH hUM mthar btags la nang mchod phul te / rang yi dam du gsal gsal ba'i thugs ka'i sa bon las 'od zer 'phros / chos skyong lcam sring gi thugs kar nyi ma'i steng du rang rang gi sngags phreng gis bskor ba la phog pas thugs rgyud bskul / rang dbang med par bka' nyan cing ci 'dod pa'i las bsgrub par bsams la / oM pra Na Ang+ma k+Shi ru pu ru Sha lo hi ta sarba sha truM mA ra ya hUM phaT / ces pa yab kyi sngags dang / oM rak+mo ya ma tsit+ta dzwa la raM pra ti de wi hUM srog la ya ma dzaH sarba sha truM mA ra ya rbad phaT / ces yum gyi sngags ci mang bzlas pa'i mthar / chos skyong 'khor dang bcas pa'i ljags hUM las skyes pa'i rdo rje rtse gcig pa dmar po 'od kyi sbu gu can du gyur pas gtor ma'i bcud thams cad drangs

te gsol bar bsams la / oM rak+mo pra Na At+ma sa pa ri wA ra sarba big+h+nAn sha truM i daM ba liM ta kha kha khA hi khA hi / zhes pa lan bdun gyis gtor ma dbul / slar yang mchod pa dang nang mchod phul nas / kye rgya gar yul gyi dgra lha / ma ru tse'i gnas srung / li yul chos kyi srung ma / ma hA de wa'i bka' nyan / gshin rje'i gshed kyi bka' sdod / yab gnod sbyin zangs kyi ral pa can dang / @# / / yum srin mo khrag gi ral pa can gyi sras gnod sbyin chen po zangs kyi beg tse can / sring mo srid pa'i lha mo gdong dmar ma / 'khor srog gcod bshan pa'i tshogs dang bcas pa khyed rnams kyis sha khrag dmar gyi gtor ma 'di bzhes la| sangs rgyas kyi bstan pa srungs / dkon mchog gi dbu 'phang bstod / bla ma'i sku tshe srings / rnal 'byor pa bdag gis sangs rgyas ma thob kyi bar du 'gal rkyen thams cad sol / mthun rkyen thams cad sgrubs / gnod byed dgra bgegs thams cad drag po'i chad pas skad cig nyid la thal ba'i rdul phran bzhin du brlag par mdzod cig ces bka' bsgo / 'og nas 'bul ba ltar gyi bskang rdzas rnams bsang sbyangs byas la / rang rang gi ming yig dang po thig les brgyan pa zhu ba las byung ba'i gnod sbyin lcam sring mnyes par byed pa'i dam rdzas spyan gzigs mchod pa'i bye brag bsam gyis mi khyab pa zhig gnod sbyin lcam sring 'khor dang bcas pa'i spyan lam du 'byung zhing rgyas par gyur cig ces brjod la / oM sarba bid pu ra pu ra sogs kyi nam mkha' mdzod kyi sngags dang phyag rgyas byin gyis brlabs la 'bul ba ni / kye| dus gsum rgyal ba'i bstan srung mthu rtsal can / / srog bdag dmar po 'khor bcas spyan lam du / / nam mkha' gang ba'i dam rdzas spyan gzigs tshogs / / 'byung zhing rgyas la thugs dam skongs gyur cig / ra dmar khrag chang mchod yon mtsho ltar 'khyil / / dbang po lnga yi me tog ri ltar spungs / / sha chen tshil chen dud pa sprin ltar 'khrigs / / zhun chen sgron me nyi ltar 'bar ba 'dis / / gnod sbyin dregs pa lcam sring thugs dam bskang / / las mkhan srog bdag dmar po'i thugs dam bskang / / gri thogs bshan pa'i tshogs kyi thugs dam bskang / / 'khor tshogs dam can rgya mtsho'i thugs dam bskang / / 'khor dang bcas pa'i thugs dam bskongs gyur nas / / rnal 'byor dpon slob nyams chags sos gyur cig / mi mthun rkyen dang bar gcod zlog pa dang / / mthun pa'i dngos grub ma lus stsal du gsol / / gser zhun 'khyil 'dra mkhris pa'i dri chab dang / / dgra bgegs sha khrag spungs pa'i

zhal zas dang / / snyan brjid rol mo'i sgra yis stong gsum khyab / / ro brgya ldan pa'i gser skyems dam pa 'dis / / X rno sdug ra g.yo sha rgyas dal gyis 'gro / / mdzes pa'i spu ldan mtshams sprin phung po bzhin / / 'ja' tshon ltar bkra dar gyi rgyan cha can / / spyan gzigs bse yi ra skyes kham pa 'dis / / X zhol g.yag kham pa rnams ni ngar 'jo byed / / mdzes ldan rta mchog rnams ni glog bzhin 'gyu / / dur bya srin bya'i gar gyis mkha' lam khyab / / bse khra dam nyams klad la lding ba 'dis / / X sra zhing brtan pa rdo rje'i go khrab dang / / rno ngar mi bzad sna tshogs mtshon cha dang / / dur bya'i sgros rgyan dar dmar g.yo bas mdzes / / dgra bgegs snying la thog ltar rgyug pa 'dis / / X sha khrag gtor ma'i tshogs kyis sa gzhi gang / / phyi nang 'dod yon tshogs kyis bar snang gang / / rgyal srid rin chen bdun gyis nam mkha' gang / / dngos bshams yid kyis sprul pa'i mchod sprin 'dis / / X sems nyid rang bzhin mkha' ltar rnam dag kyang / / glo bur nyon mongs sprin gyis g.yogs @# / / pa'i mthus / / nongs par gang gyur bshags dang bshags yul dang / / bshags bya dmigs med ngang du dag par bgyi / / sgrol gying srog bdag dmar po 'khor bcas kyis / / gnod byed dgra bgegs thams cad tshar chod la / / yid bzhin nor dang dpag bsam shing bzhin du / / mchog dang thun mong dngos grub char du phob / / ces thugs dam bskangs nas gtor ma byang shar gyi gtor stegs khar bskyal te / byang shar ma ru tse yi dur khrod nas / / mchong dmar brag la brten pa'i gnas bcas pa / / sgrol gying chen po srog bdag dmar po dang / / srog bdud chen mo bse yi lan phran can / / lcam sring khyed kyi bka' las mi 'da' ba'i / / las mkhan srog bdag dmar po 'khor dang bcas / / sgrol byed bshan pa gri thogs brgyad po dang / rol bshan nyi shu rtsa gcig 'khor dang bcas / / bdud dang gnod sbyin srin po sum stong dang / / btsan dmar stong gi dmag tshogs 'khor dang bcas / / ma mo 'bum dang the'u rang stong la sogs / / ston pa'i bka' nyan bstan srung rgya mtsho'i tshogs / / 'dir gshegs rgyan gyi gtor ma 'di bzhes shig / dgra sha khrag gi mchod pa 'di bzhes shig / gtsang ma phud kyi gser skyems 'di bzhes shig / ra dmar khrag chang mchod yon 'di bzhes shig / sngar bcol legs pa'i gtang rag gnyan po gtong / / da 'chol legs pa'i gsol 'debs rten du 'bul / / rgyal ba'i bstan dang

bstan 'dzin gces par skyongs / / rnal 'byor bdag gi gnas lus longs spyod dang / / 'khor dang yo byad bzhon pa la sogs pa / / bcol lo ltos so srung ma mthu rtsal can / / nyin gsum bya ra rgyang nas ma g.yel cig / mtshan gsum mel tshe drung nas ma g.yel cig / rtag tu sgrub pa'i stongs grogs ma g.yel cig / bla mas bcol ba'i phrin las ma g.yel cig / sdang ba'i dgra la mngon pa'i rtags ston la / / rnal 'byor bdag gi mgon skyabs dpung gnyen mdzod / / bla ma'i sku dgra bstan pa'i spyi dgra dang / / rnal 'byor sgos dgra sems can yongs la 'tshe / / ma nyes log par lta ba'i dgra dang bgegs / / dpal mgon khyod kyis sgrol la bstan pa srungs / / zhes spyi bstabs bya'o / / gying lnga gza' gdong lcam dral la gtor ma 'bul ba'i tshul ni / gtor ma phyag len bzhin bshams / sngar ltar byin gyis brlab pa'am / yang na sngags drug phyag rgya drug gis byin gyis brlabs te / rang gi thugs ka'i sa bon las 'od zer 'phros pas / yang gsang khros pa'i dkyil 'khor nas bka' sdod gying lnga gza' gdong 'khor bcas spyan drangs / hUM| padma dbang chen dkyil 'khor nas / / chos kyi dbyings las ma g.yos kyang / / bstan pa gnyan po srung ba dang / / dgra bgegs thal bar rlog pa dang / / rnal 'byor las bcol bsgrub pa'i phyir / / srog gcod dregs pa gying lnga dang / / gza' gdong lcam dral 'khor dang bcas / / sngon gyi dam las ma 'da' bar / / rings pa'i tshul gyis da tshur spyon / / e hye hi / badzra sa ma ya dzaH zhes spyan drangs te / rang gi mdun du bzhugs par mos la / mgron rnams kyi ljags hUM las skyes pa'i rdo rje rtse gcig pa 'od kyi sbu gu can du gyur pas gtor ma'i bcud thams cad drangs te gsol bar bsams la / oM a kA ro mu khaM zhes @# / / sogs lan bdun gyis gtor ma bsngos la / mchod pa nang mchod sman rag dang bcas pas kyang mchod nas bstod cing bskul ba ni / hrIH bcom ldan padma he ru ka / dbang chen thugs kyi sprul pa ni / / srog bdag 'od kyi rgyal po byung / / skyes mchog 'od kyi mi bo che / / sku la seng ge'i slog pa gsol / / dbu la byi le dkar po bcings / / nam mkha' 'ja' yi ska rags can / / chibs su seng ge dkar mo chibs / / lcags kyi sder mos dgra snying 'byin / / g.yas pa ral gris dgra sogs gcod / / g.yon pa 'od kyi zhags pa 'phen / / dgra bo'i tshe srog don snying phyung / bskul lo drag tu dgra srog chod / /

shar gyi dkar po dam tshig can / / rta ru dkar po ngang ring zhon / sku la dar dkar ral gu gsol / / dbu la dung gi cod paN can / / phyag na shel gyi zangs gri thogs / / phyag g.yon zhags pa dgra la 'debs / / tshangs pa dung gi thor tshugs can / / dgra bo'i lto phrol khong snying phyung / / lho yi dge bsnyen dam tshig can / / sku la za 'og sngo khra gsol / dbu la bse man 'gying thod bcings / / rta ni kham pa lag dkar zhon / / g.yas pa bse yi rdo rje thogs / / g.yon pa tsit+ta dmar po thogs / / gying chen rdo rje gshogs rgod rtsal / / dgra bo'i snying phyung srog rtsa chod / / nub kyi bdud nag dam tshig can / / sku la lcags kyi zhun khrab gsol / / dbu la bdud zhwa lding nag gsol / / chibs su bdud rta nag po chibs / / phyag g.yas bdud kyi khram shing bsnams / / phyag g.yon zhags pa nag po 'debs / / nag po gsod byed bdud kyi bu / / dgra yi tshe srog khram la thob / / byang gi srog bdag dam tshig can / / sku la bse khrab dmar po gsol / / dbu la bse rmog zangs ring gsol / / chibs su bse yi ra skyes chibs / / phyag g.yas zangs kyi gri rings bsnams / / g.yon pa zhags pa dgra la 'debs / / bse rog srog gcod lag dmar 'gying / / dgra bo'i mdangs phrogs srog rtsa chod / / dam nyams ma gtang sho ra re / hrIH padma'i rgyal po rta mchog dpal / / khro rgyal khrag 'thung he ru ka / thugs kyi sprul pa mi bzad pa / skyi thang chu 'khyag mnga' bdag khyod / / khyab 'jug chen po ra hu la / / byi ta se ta sgra gcan 'dzin / / drang srong chen po kun tu rgyu / / gza' rgod chen po skyi thang bdag / dud kha mgo dgu mig gis khengs / / ro smad sbrul gyis rgya mtsho 'khrug / phyag g.yas skyi thang 'khor lo bsnams / / phyag g.yon chu srin zhags pa 'phen / / dgra yul lo thog rdul du rlogs / / hUM| phyogs bzhi nam mkha'i klong dkyil na / / ngan sngags bdag mo skyi thang phob / / shar gyi stag srin drag srin zer ba'ang 'dug zor ba gdong / / lho yi baM srin dred mo gdong / / nub kyi kong srin ba glang gdong / / byang gi 'brog srin chu srin gdong / / ngan sngags bdag mo khyed bzhi ni / / g.yas pa zor ba g.yon nad rkyal / / skyi thang chu rgod mnga' bdag ma / / dgra bo'i lo thog sna ma la / / chu rgod 'khyag pa'i skyi thang phob / / dgra

yul thal ba'i rdul du rlogs / / ces bskul lo / / gnyis pa gtor ma phyi rol du gshegs shing bstan ma skyong ba'i tshul ni / 'jig rten dang 'jig rten las 'das pa'i gtor ma dang / bstan ma bcu gnyis kyi gtor ma phyag len bzhin bshams byin gyis brlabs / phyi rol tu khyer / de'ang zer du byed na / da ni @# / / gshegs so sha ra ra / / zhes sogs kyis gtor sgo dbye ba'ang byed / de bzhin min na rig 'dzin spyi skul dang / dkon mchog gi spyi skul sogs byas nas gtor ma spyi ltar bskyangs / khyad par bstan ma bskyang ba ni / rang gi thugs ka'i hrIH las 'od 'phros / bod khams skyong ba'i bstan ma bcu gnyis la yul lha gzhi bdag gis bskor ba spyan drangs / oM ma ma / me me / la la / le le / ta ta / te te / sring 'gro ma A kar+Sha ya dzaH zhes pas spyan drangs / dar dkar gyi gur 'ja' 'od 'khyil ba'i nang du bzhugs par bsams la / gying lnga gza' gdong gi skabs ltar gtor ma bsngos shing mchod nas gser skyems sbran rol mo dang bcas pas / oM| bdag nyid chen mo rdo rje kun grags ma / / dpal ldan lha ri rdo rje g.ya' ma skyong / / gangs kyi yum chen rdo rje kun tu bzang / / 'brog chen 'khor 'dul rdo rje bgegs kyi gtso / / bdud mo chen mo khyed bzhi yang / / sngon gyi thugs dam rjes dgongs la / / bran g.yog mang po'i 'khor dang bcas / / lhab lhub mang po'i rgyan dang bcas / / sil snyan rol mo'i sgra dang bcas / / 'dir spyon mthun pa'i dam rdzas bzhes / / bcol ba'i phrin las grub par mdzod / / gangs dkar sha med rdo rje spyan gcig ma / / mkha' rag khyung btsun rdo rje dpal gyi yum / / gser chen mkha' lding rdo rje klu mo dang / / rma ri rab 'byams rdo rje grags mo rgyal / / gnod sbyin chen mo khyed bzhi yang / / X kong btsun de mo rdo rje bod khams skyong / / btsan la lo ro rdo rje sman gcig ma / / sman btsun ug chos rdo rje g.yas mo sil / / g.yu yi dril bu rdo rje gzugs legs ma / / sman mo chen mo khyed bzhi yang / / zhes pa nas / bcol ba'i phrin las grub par mdzod / / ces pa'i bar sbyar la gtor ma g.ya' dang gangs mthong ba'i sar bskyal / de nas kyang sbros pa la dga' na dbang po rab 'bring tha ma'i rta bro dag kyang bya'o / / gsum pa nye bar bsdu zhing bzod par gsol nas shis pa brjod pa'i tshul nye bar bsdu ba ni / gzhal yas khang gdan dang bcas pa 'khor gyi lha rnams

la thim / 'khor gyi lha rnams yum la thim / yum yab la / yab thugs ka'i pad 'dab hrIH dang bcas pa la / thugs ka'i pad 'dab kyang hrIH la thim zhing / hrIH yang je phra je phrar gyur te mthar mi dmigs par bsams la / de kho na nyid kyi rtogs pa'i lta ba'i steng du re zhig mnyam par gzhag slar yang de las chu las nya ldang ba'i tshul du gtso bo zhal gcig phyag gnyis pa'am / zhal phyag yongs su rdzogs par langs pa'i gnas lngar bya khyung gi phyag rgya bcas la / spyi bor oM hya gr-i ba / mgrin par b+han+d+ha hrIH snying gar padma b+han+d+ha hrIH lte bar tsan+da rag sha hrIH gsang gnas su hu lu hu lu hUM b+h+yo hUM / zhes sngags rnams 'od zer gyi phung po can du bsgoms la lus bsrung / slar yang mchod bstod bsdus pa zhig byas las / oM padma sa twa sa ma ya zhes sogs snang ba mtha' yas kyi yi ge brgya pa lan gsum brjod de / ma 'byor pa dang nyams pa dang / zhes sogs kyis bzod par gsol zhing lhag chad kha bskang la thun mtshams su snod thams cad gzhal yas khang dang / bcud thams cad dpal rta mgrin gyi lha tshogs su mos pa dang / bza' btung rnams kyang ye shes kyi bdud rtsir byin gyis brlabs la nang gi sbyin sreg gi tshul du longs spyad / mthar / phun sum tshogs pa mnga' ba gser gyi ri bo 'dra / / zhes sogs kyi bkra shis kyang rgyas par bya'o / / gang zhig yid la dran pa tsam gyis @# / / bdud sde ma lus skrag cing 'dar / / mtshan tsam rna bar lhung ba yis kyang srid gsum bgegs dpung 'byer zhing 'bros / / snying nas skyabs su bzung ba'i mod la 'chi med go 'phang bde blag stsol / / lhag pa'i lha de bsnyen cing sgrub rnams kwa ye mchog tu skal ba bzang / / yang gsang khros pa padma gar gyi gtso / / gsang don yid bzhin rgya mtsho'i 'jug ngogs nas / / dngos grub gnyis kyi nor bu len 'dod na / / sgrub thabs gru chen 'di la brten par byos / / 'dir 'bad las byung rnam dkar nyi 'od kyis / / nag phyogs bdud sde'i mun pa drungs phyung nas / / sku gsum 'dab brgya'i tshal du gegs med par / / gzhan phan sbrang rtsi'i ro la spyod gyur cig / ces padma dbang chen yang gsang khros pa'i
